      { "There's a %fish%-catching contest at the docks this %timeofday% — a fat purse of %currency% to the winner and a year of bragging to go with it. I haven't fished in years. I'm in.", roles={"sailor","citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={coast=2, city=1} },
      { "Over-tuned the %enchant% on a merchant's cloak and now the poor soul glows whenever he lies. Ruinous for a haggler. I'll fix it. Eventually. It's a LITTLE funny.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Bandits 'tax' the %route% past the mile-stone now, polite as you please, and hand you a receipt for the robbery. You almost have to admire the paperwork. Almost.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={road=2} },
      { "My %companion% found the safe ford across the %zone% river when my own eyes would've drowned us both. Pride sinks men out here. A clever beast keeps them afloat.", roles={"adventurer","farmer"}, moods={"warm","wry"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      { "Went into the deep halls of %instance% for %item% in my day and came out with a limp and a healthy respect for locked doors. The folk who opened them are still down there.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Roof's leaking over the whole common room in this %weather%. I've pots out catching it like a tinker's orchestra. Come in, mind the drips, the %drink%'s still dry.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { "A tauron bent an iron bar at the %event% trials and a gnome challenged him to a thinking contest in revenge. It ended a draw and they're friends now. The square's the better for it.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Quiet %timeofday% on the gate, the %weather% keeping trouble home. I'd almost rather a brawl. A quiet shift leaves a guard too long alone with his own thoughts.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Swear I saw %rare% off the %route% at dawn — it watched me, then walked into the mist like it owned the morning. Believe me or don't. I know what wonder does to a face.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      { "Lost a whole %season%'s savings at cards in the %shop% to the same grinning friend as always. Better to lose your coin to a friend than a stranger, I say. Deal me in again.", roles={"drunkard","citizen"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A barn cat woke the whole household before the fire took hold this %season%. We lost the barn and nothing more. Feed the beasts first, friends. They've earned it twice over.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Flood washed the %route% bridge clean away and stranded a season's worth of travelers on the wrong bank, all crammed in one inn. Worst week, best company I ever kept.", roles={"adventurer","innkeeper"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={road=2} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged one-liners (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { "The %profession% guild raised dues again. Same %item% I've made for thirty %season%, now with twice the stamped paper. Some wars are fought with ledgers.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The old %shop% sold to a goblin who means to 'modernize.' Enjoy the one quiet corner of the %city% while it lasts, friends. The surcharge is coming.", roles={"citizen","innkeeper"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Spare an old soldier a copper and I'll spare you a tale of %zone% worth ten times the coin. The full purses never have time for the tales. Their loss.", roles={"drunkard","soldier"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "Left three coppers loose at the top of my purse for the urchin eyeing it. I was that child once. You pay the kindness forward where it lands.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "They've raised the %route% bridge toll again and called it a war tax. My cart of %tradegood% barely clears a profit. So we travel in company and split it.", roles={"farmer","vendor"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={road=2} },
      { "My %companion% won't go near the old mill and growls at the dark inside. So I don't go near the old mill. I've lived this long trusting a frightened beast.", roles={"farmer","adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={rural=2, wilderness=1} },
      { "A noble's throwing a grand ball for the %event% — half the %city% invited, the other half catering. We're catering. We'll know every secret by midnight.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Forty %season% on this corner and I've never once raised a price on a widow or an urchin. They're neighbors, not marks. The busy stall proves me right.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The survivors tell the quiet tales. The loud heroes are mostly names on stones in %zone%. I'll take a coward's long life over a hero's short song any %timeofday%.", roles={"adventurer","drunkard"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Saw a man who shook like a leaf the whole march hold the line when it broke. That's the only courage there is — afraid, and doing the thing regardless.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={battlefield=1, city=1} },
      { "The two warriors who duel outside the bank every dawn were sharing a %drink% at dusk. Sworn enemies, my foot. This %city% loves a good public lie.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Mucked out a stable of war-%mount%s after the %zone% campaign for honest %gold%. No glory in it, but the beasts were better company than the nobles ever were.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "The light goes long and gold this %timeofday% of the %season% and it always finds the someone I lost. Grief and a sunset keep the same hours, it seems.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={rural=1, city=1} },
