      { "Earned the title '%title%' in %zone% a lifetime ago. These days it mostly earns me a free %drink% off old soldiers, and that's plenty.", roles={"soldier","drunkard"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Watched a %class% loose a %spell% over the harbor at dusk for no reason but the beauty of it. The %weather% lit up gold. Magic isn't always for war.", roles={"mage","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={coast=1, city=1} },
      { "My old warhound's gone grey at the muzzle, same as me. We earned our quiet by the %zone% road and we're spending it on this porch. No regrets.", roles={"soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "The %bg% recruiters promise honor and a %pvptitle% to any fool with a strong arm. I had a strong arm once. The honor never paid for the limp.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={city=1, battlefield=1} },
      { "Held a frozen ridge in %zone% through a whole %season% of %weather%. We burned the wagons to stay warm. I still can't watch a fire without remembering.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={battlefield=1, road=1} },
      { "A goblin's selling 'genuine %mount% whistles' by the bank. Blow it and a swamp %critter% turns up instead. Sold out by noon. The chaos is the product.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Spent the whole %event% teaching my %companion% the festival %emote%. It refused with dignity. I respect it more for that, honestly.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The lighthouse lamp went dark two nights and the whole coast held its breath. Old keeper's just ill, thank the tides. We've lit it for him till he mends.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","kindly"}, areas={coast=2} },
      { "A %race% gambler bet a fine %mount% in %city% on a hand he couldn't win. He couldn't win it. I ride to work in style now and he walks. Lesson, that.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={city=1} },
      { "Out in %zone% the stars come so thick you forget the %city% exists. The road takes your comfort and pays you back in sky. I've made peace with the trade.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={wilderness=2, road=1} },
      { "An old soldier in the tavern can name every man he lost in %zone% and not one he killed. That's how you can tell a true veteran from a boastful one.", roles={"soldier","drunkard"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "Hauled a wounded stranger off the %route% on my own back to the next inn. Never learned the name. Some debts you pay forward to folk you'll never meet.", roles={"adventurer","innkeeper"}, moods={"kindly","weary"}, areas={road=2} },
      { "The %instance% under %zone% has ceilings you can't see the top of. We went in for %item% and came out with a respect for the old builders we never lost.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={road=1, wilderness=1} },
      { "Drums on the far ridge again all %timeofday%. The enemy doesn't mean for us to sleep before %zone%. Doesn't matter. A man can fear in rhythm same as silence.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
