      { "Carved a %toy% for the innkeeper's daughter. Took an evening, cost me nothing, bought me a year of free stew. Best deal I ever struck.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","wry"}, areas={rural=2, city=1} },
      -- Farmers & rural folk
      { "Frost spared the %season% crop this year. I'll not say it loud, but I had a quiet word of thanks with the Earth Mother all the same.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","kindly"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "A %monster% came out the treeline and took two of my hens. Set the dogs and a lantern. It'll think twice tomorrow.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={rural=2, wilderness=1} },
      { "Hauling %tradegood% to market down the %route% before dawn. Pray the bridge still stands after that %weather%.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","nervous"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { "The miller's thumb is on the scale again, same as his father's was. Some %profession% are just inherited sins.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={"rural"} },
      -- Sailors & the coast
      { "Tide's right and the wind's kind. We make for %zone% on the turn, and I'll not hear a word about the %weather%.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Hauled in a %fish% this morning bigger than the cabin boy. Sold it dockside before the gulls could argue.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"boastful","cheerful"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Lighthouse keeper hasn't come down for the %event% in forty years. Says the lamp can't mind itself. Lonely faith, that.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Foreign ship's paying in %currency% for every barrel of %tradegood% on the dock. Somebody up the chain is getting rich. Not us.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"bitter","greedy"}, areas={coast=2} },
      -- Nobles, urchins, the streets
      { "My family's crest has hung over this %city% for nine generations. Lately it mostly hangs over the tax rolls.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Spare a copper, kind sir? No? Then spare a tale of %zone% instead. The full purses never have time for those.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { "We run the rooftops better than the watch runs the streets. Know every gutter and gap in the %city%, we do.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Funded the new orphanage wing this %season%. Don't print it. A name's worth more for the deeds you keep quiet.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"kindly","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Drunkards & tavern philosophers
      { "What %season% is it? No, don't tell me. If I don't know, I can't have missed anything. Another %drink%, friend.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      { "I've fought %boss%, I've sailed past %zone%, I've kissed a %race% princess. Believe what you like. The %drink%'s real, that's enough.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Citizens, weather, ambience (lighter tags)
      { "The criers say %weather%'s coming off the mountains by %timeofday%. The washing's already in. We learn fast in this %city%.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Watched the lamplighters race the dusk down the long street. The %city%'s at its softest in that grey hour.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Every %season% the same swallows nest over the smithy. The blacksmith pretends to mind. He's named them, the old softie.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Heard a %class% telling children about %boss% in the square. Half of it was lies. All of it was wonderful.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A traveling %profession% set up by the well selling charms against %monster% attacks. We've no %monster% for fifty leagues. Selling well, though.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { "The %event% banners are up across the %city% already. Whole quarter smells of %food% and woodsmoke. My favorite time.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Capital-city life & ambiance
      "The city wakes the same way every morning: bells, then bread, then the auctioneers, then the complaining. I love it.",
      "Rain on the cobbles, smoke from the chimneys, lamplight in the windows. The city's at its prettiest when it's grey.",
      "Commons is loud today. Three auctioneers shouting over each other and not one of them selling anything I need.",
      "Stood in the bank line for twenty minutes behind someone reorganizing forty bags. Send patience.",
      { "The blacksmith's apprentice dropped a whole rack of swords. The clang echoed three districts over.", roles={"craftsman"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Saw a %class% help an old woman carry her groceries across the square. The Light's in the small things too.", moods={"kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Tavern's out of the good ale already. It's not even noon. Rough crowd today.", roles={"innkeeper","drunkard"}, areas={"city","rural"} },
      "Someone painted a mustache on the founder's statue overnight. The guards are 'investigating' between laughs.",
      { "A traveling merchant set up by the fountain selling 'genuine artifacts.' They're rocks. Nice rocks, though.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The lamplighters are making their rounds. Dusk in the city always feels like a held breath.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Heard two nobles arguing over who has the bigger estate. Neither noticed the pickpocket between them.", roles={"noble","urchin"}, moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Beggar by the gate has better stories than most adventurers. Spare him a copper if you pass.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The city criers have the same news as yesterday. Slow week for villainy, apparently.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      "I just like sitting in the tavern and listening to other people's adventures. Cheaper than having my own.",
      { "Rumor in the market: a noble's wedding next week. Half the city's invited, the other half is catering.", moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      "A child asked me if I'd ever seen a real dragon. I said yes. Made their whole week.",
      "Bought %food% from a street cart. Didn't ask what's in it. Some city mysteries are better left alone.",
      { "Two old veterans arguing about a war that ended before I was born. I bought them both %drink%.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","kindly"} },
      "The street musician outside the inn only knows one song, but he plays it with his whole heart.",
      { "City guard stopped me to ask directions. To his own barracks. New recruit, bless him.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The watch doubled the patrols near the bank. Either trouble's brewing or someone important's visiting.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A guard recited the entire city ordinance to a drunk who just wanted to find the privy. Justice.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "They post the wanted notices by the gate. Same three rogues every week. Practically celebrities now.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The city tailor does the finest stitching in the kingdom. Pricey, but you'll never look like a peasant again.", roles={"vendor","craftsman"}, moods={"boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Innkeeper set my hearthstone and then asked if I wanted the usual. I have a usual now. I've arrived.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The stablemaster knows every pet in the city by name. Mine she calls 'the troublemaker.' Accurate.", moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Flight master's gryphons are restless today. Storm coming, he reckons, and he's never wrong.", areas={"city"} },
      { "Stood in the forge watching the blacksmith work for an hour. There's poetry in good steelwork.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Fruit vendor gave me an extra apple 'for the road.' Small kindness, big city, good day.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Faction-neutral hubs (Dalaran, Shattrath, Booty Bay)
      "Dalaran floats over Crystalsong today. Best view in Northrend, if you don't mind the cold.",
      "The Legerdemain Lounge has a fire going and someone playing piano. Perfect place to wait out a blizzard.",
      "Antonidas Memorial fountain is full of coins from a hundred wishes. Mages wish big, apparently.",
      { "Watched an apprentice mage misfire a portal and end up in the sewers. We've all been there.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      "The streets of Dalaran are neutral ground. Doesn't stop the glaring, though.",
      "Lower City in Shattrath is a melting pot. Heard six languages before I finished my soup.",
      "The Aldor and Scryers still won't share a tavern. Old grudges die hard in Shattrath.",
      "A naaru's light fills the Terrace of Light. Whatever your faith, it's hard not to feel it.",
      "Refugees still arrive in Shattrath daily. The Sha'tar take them all in. Every one.",
      { "Booty Bay never closes. Goblins don't sleep when there's a copper to be made.", roles={"sailor"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "A goblin in Booty Bay sold me a map to buried treasure. The treasure was another map. Well played.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "The Salty Sailor Tavern is rowdy tonight. Two duels and a marriage already, and it's not even dark.", roles={"sailor","innkeeper"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Steamwheedle goblins are neutral, sure. Neutral about everything except your gold.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={"coast"} },
      "Northrend wind cuts right through Dalaran's streets. Thank the Light for that lounge fireplace.",
      -- War, the wider world, rumor
      { "Word from the front: the Lich King's grip on the north hasn't loosened. Pray for our soldiers in Icecrown.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"} },
      { "They say the dragons gather in Wyrmrest. When dragons hold council, the rest of us should worry.", moods={"nervous","gossipy"} },
      { "Heard the Argent Crusade is recruiting at the city gates. Noble cause, terrible retirement plan.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A traveler from Northrend says the Scourge is quieter lately. Quiet Scourge is the scary kind.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous"} },
      { "The Cenarion Circle warns the Emerald Dream is troubled. Druids look tired. That's never good.", moods={"solemn"} },
      { "Tirion Fordring's name on every soldier's lips heading north. If anyone can end this, it's him.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave"} },
      { "They say the King hasn't slept in days. Heavy is the head, and all that.", moods={"gossipy","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Heard the Stockades had a breakout. Probably just a drunk who wandered in the wrong door again.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The harbor's foggy today. Half the dock workers swear they saw a ghost ship. Half are just hungover.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Politics in the capital again. Everyone's got an opinion, nobody's got a solution.", moods={"bitter"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "They say peace talks failed again. The diplomats go home, the soldiers stay in the field. Same as always.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","bitter"} },
      { "Two faction banners flying over the same contested town by week's end. Bet the goblins are selling both.", moods={"wry"}, areas={battlefield=2, rural=1} },
      { "Saw an Alliance and a Horde soldier nod at each other in neutral Dalaran. War's complicated, ain't it?", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn"} },
      "Heard a human and an orc came to blows in Booty Bay. The goblin bartender charged them both for the broken table.",
      { "Did you all hear about the guild leader from Vanquished who vanished with the whole treasury?", moods={"gossipy"} },
      { "A hooded figure's been buying every candle in the city for three days. Cult, or just bad at planning a party.", moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "They say there's a door in the canals that wasn't there last week. Nobody's opened it. Yet.", moods={"gossipy","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Rumor of a secret tavern beneath the city that only serves those who know the password. I do not know the password.", moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Someone's leaving fresh flowers at the unmarked grave in the cemetery every dawn. No one's caught them.", moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={"city"}, cooldown=20 },
      -- Festivals & holidays
      "Brewfest decorations are going up in the cities already. My liver is filing a formal complaint.",
      "The Darkmoon Faire's back. I've already lost my month's gold to a goblin and a ring toss.",
      "Hallow's End bonfire in the square tonight. Bring a costume, leave with candy and a headache.",
      "Winter Veil lights are up across the city. Greatfather Winter had better bring me that mount this year.",
      "Lunar Festival fireworks over the city. The elders are handing out Coins of Ancestry. Grab a fistful.",
      "Pilgrim's Bounty feast in the city square. The tables go on forever. So does the line.",
      "Love is in the Air and the city's drowning in pink. I've been handed nine perfumes and zero proposals.",
      "Children's Week. The orphans are touring the city and every single one waved at me. My heart.",
      "Midsummer flames lit in every capital tonight. Dancing till dawn, win or lose the bonfire war.",
      "Noblegarden eggs hidden all over the city and grown adults are SPRINTING for them. No shame. None.",
      "Day of the Dead shrines went up in the cemetery. Marigolds everywhere. The dead are remembered well here.",
      -- Faith, the elements, quiet moments
      { "Lit a candle in the Cathedral for a friend who didn't come back from the north. The Light keeps them now.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Knelt at the moonwell and felt the day's weight lift a little. Elune's mercy is real, whatever you believe.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"} },
      { "The shaman say the elements are restless lately. I'm no shaman, but even I can feel the air's gone strange.", moods={"nervous","solemn"} },
      { "Sat in the silence of the Terrace of Light until the naaru's glow felt like an answer. Maybe it was.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"} },
      { "Saw a knight teaching a farmboy to hold a sword properly. Everyone starts somewhere.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"kindly"} },
      { "An old mage feeds the city pigeons every morning at the fountain. Says they're better company than apprentices.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The orphanage matron walked a line of children through the city. They waved at every guard. Every one waved back.", moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A blind old man asked me to describe the sunset over the harbor. Best ten minutes of my whole week.", moods={"kindly","dreamy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Gave my cloak to a shivering kid by the gate. The cold's worth it. I've got a warm inn to walk to.", moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      "A stranger returned my dropped coin purse, full. Faith in folk: restored, at least till the auction house.",
      { "The tavern keeper remembered my late friend's usual order and poured it without a word. Kindness has a long memory.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Bards, music, small wonders
      "A bard just made up a song about my last %instance% run. Got the details wrong but the chorus slaps.",
      "Street drummers set up in the square and within minutes half the city was dancing. Magic, the ordinary kind.",
      "An old troll played a flute carved from a raptor bone. Loveliest, eeriest sound I've ever heard.",
      "Saw a painter capture the whole harbor at sunset in twenty quick strokes. Bought it on the spot.",
      "The opera house reopened. Tickets sold out in an hour. The dragon's not even in this production. Probably.",
      "Two bards in the same tavern turned a song into a sing-off. The crowd picked sides. It got beautifully out of hand.",
      { "The inn cat has claimed the warmest chair by the fire and the entire city respects its authority.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A stranger paid my tab and vanished before I could thank him. Pay it forward, the bartender said. So I will.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Races rubbing shoulders
      "A dwarf told me his beard was older than my entire bloodline. He wasn't wrong and he knew it.",
      "Watched a tauren gently move out of a gnome's way in the bank. Big folk, bigger hearts.",
      "A draenei diplomat tried to explain the Light to a Forsaken. Long conversation. Surprisingly polite.",
      "A night elf rolled her eyes at a human's 'ancient' family history. Ten thousand years is a long time to gloat.",
      "A blood elf and a high elf passed in Dalaran without a word. Family reunions are awkward.",
      "Every city's got its own smell. Orgrimmar's smoke, Ironforge's ale, Darnassus's flowers. Home is whichever's closest.",
      "Crossed half of Azeroth this week and the friendliest face was a goblin who overcharged me with a smile.",
      -- Mounts, pets, the little chaos
      "Some noble paraded his new mechanostrider through the square. It backfired. The crowd loved it.",
      "A little girl asked to pet my war mount. The mount that has killed dragons now lives for ear scratches.",
      "Someone's pet sporebat is loose in the auction house and honestly it's improving the place.",
      "Saw a goblin propose with a ring he 'definitely didn't' lift from the auction house. She said yes anyway.",
      "A gnome ran past me in the street yelling 'IT'S SUPPOSED TO DO THAT.' Nothing was supposed to do that.",
      "A dwarf and a gnome arguing engineering in the street drew a bigger crowd than the actual parade.",
      "Rumor says someone slew Onyxia again last night. Her head's hanging in the city gate. Again. Poor girl.",
      -- The road, the traveler's life
      { "Met a fellow traveler in the inn. Swapped stories till the candles burned out. That's the real endgame.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"warm"} },
      "Some nights the city feels too big and lonely. Then a stranger shares a joke and it's home again.",
      "A rainstorm rolled into the harbor and the whole city ducked into the taverns. Crowded, cozy, perfect.",
      "I've slain dragons and saved villages, but I still can't navigate the bank line without an existential crisis.",
      "Funny how the safest I ever feel is standing in a crowded city square doing absolutely nothing important.",
      "A whole life happens in these streets between dungeon runs. Weddings, funerals, arguments over fish prices. The real epic.",
      { "The city's loud and crowded and overpriced and somehow it's the only place that ever feels like coming home.", moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"}, weight=2 },
      "Watched the gates close for the night from the top of the wall. Whole city tucked in safe behind stone. Sleep easy.",
      "Whatever banner flies over it, a city is just people trying to get home before dark. Easy to forget that.",
      { "Long day. Found a quiet bench, a warm drink, and a good view of the city lights. That'll do. That'll do just fine.", moods={"weary","warm"}, areas={"city"}, weight=2 },
      -- A light sprinkle of in-character grouping calls (RP-flavored, not spam)
      { "A %role% by the gate is gathering brave souls for a delve into %instance%. Glory promised, survival not guaranteed.", roles={"adventurer"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Anyone in the city up for a wander to %zone%? Tired of these crowded streets.", roles={"adventurer"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "%role% sitting in the tavern, bored, will travel for adventure. Whisper me.", roles={"adventurer"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Heading out of the city to %zone% at sundown. Walking the long way for the scenery. Join if you like.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Anyone want to escort a nervous %class% through %zone%? First time out of the city.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Quiet night in the city. A %role% looking for a chat and maybe a quick delve. Either's fine.", roles={"adventurer"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Word's gone round the tavern that %instance% has stirred again. They're asking for a %role% and a steady blade.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"gossipy"} },
      { "A caravan's forming at the gate, bound through %zone%. They want a %class% or two for the rough stretches.", roles={"adventurer"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      -- Street-vendor & guard cries (in-character flavor)
      { "Fresh apples, ripe melons, honeyed dates! Best produce in the city, ask anyone, mostly my cousin!", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Sharpening blades by the smithy gate, two copper a sword, keen as a widow's tongue!", roles={"vendor","craftsman"}, moods={"gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Hot pies! Meat pies, fruit pies, mystery pies! The mystery ones are half price and twice the adventure!", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Candles, lanterns, lamp oil! Don't let the night catch you dark, friends!", roles={"vendor"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Bandages and salves, battle-tested! If they didn't work I'd be out of business AND blood!", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Maps! Real maps! Get where you're going before the goblins sell you a fake one!", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Charms and trinkets, lucky every one! Worked for me, and look how I turned out! ...don't look too hard.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Fine cloth, dyed in the city's own vats! Wear color like you mean it!", roles={"vendor","craftsman"}, moods={"boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Cold ale, warm bread, a place by the fire! The inn's door is open, traveler!", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city","rural"} },
      { "Songs for a copper, stories for a silver, the truth for a gold piece I haven't got!", moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Repairing armor by the bank! Dents hammered, straps mended, dignity not included!", roles={"craftsman","vendor"}, moods={"gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Spices from across the sea! Make your trail rations taste like something other than regret!", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Pet food, pet toys, pet everything! Spoil the only companion who never asks for a cut of the loot!", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Keep it moving by the gates, folks, the caravan needs the road. Plenty of city to stand around in.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "No dueling in the bank line. I don't care who started it. Take it to the ring like civilized warriors.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Curfew bell's rung. Honest folk to their beds, the rest of you to wherever you sleep. Move along.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Lost a child? Check the fountain. They always end up at the fountain. Every time. Like little homing pigeons.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Mind the wet cobbles by the harbor. Lost a recruit to a comedic slip just this morning. He's fine. His pride isn't.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Move it along, citizen. Yes, you, admiring the statue for the fortieth time. It'll still be bronze tomorrow.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Overheard half-conversations (the "..." flavor)
      "...so I told the auctioneer, that's not a deal, that's a robbery with extra steps...",
      "...and THEN the gryphon wouldn't land, so I'm just circling the city going 'down, DOWN, you feathered menace'...",
      "...swear on my beard the fish was THIS big before it got away...",
      "...no, see, the trick to the bank is you go at dawn, before the whole city wakes up...",
      "...she said yes! At the moonwell, with the bard and everything! I'm getting MARRIED...",
      "...third time I've been turned into a sheep this week, I'm starting to take it personally...",
      { "...best stew in the city, hands down, don't let the harbor folk tell you otherwise...", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "...you didn't hear it from me, but the noble in the blue cloak owes half the market money...", moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Closers
      "The city wakes the same way every morning and I wouldn't trade a single bell of it.",
      "A capital is a promise that tomorrow there'll still be a market, a bell, a warm inn. Worth fighting for, that promise.",
      "Spent the whole day just being a person in a city full of people. No quests, no loot, no dragons. Best day in ages.",
      "Some come to the city for the bank, some for the auction house, some for the war. I come for the bread. No regrets.",
      { "Last call at the inn, lamps going dim, the city settling into sleep. Goodnight, capital. Same time tomorrow.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Lines using the expanded placeholders (%city% %race% %profession% %boss% %mount% etc.)
      "Word from %city% is a %race% finally put %boss% down for good. The taverns will be loud tonight.",
      "Anyone in %city% leveling %profession%? I'll trade mats for a few crafts, paying fair.",
      "Saw a %race% %class% ride past on %mount%. Stopped half the street just to stare.",
      "They say %rare% was spotted out in %zone% again. Every hunter in %city% is already saddling up.",
      "Just hit revered with %rep%. The grind was long but the rewards are finally worth it.",
      "Some %class% in %city% is selling %item% for %gold%. Either a fortune or a fool, can't tell which.",
      "Half of %city% started to %emote% when the news came in. You love to see it.",
      "Fresh %level% today and proud of it. Onward to the next.",
      "Don't step into %instance% on %difficulty% without %consumable% in your pack. Learned that the hard way.",
      "Watched a %race% land %spell% perfectly at the last second. Clutch doesn't begin to cover it.",
      "Earned the title '%pvptitle%' this week. Wearing it everywhere, even to the bank.",
      "LFM %instance% %difficulty%, link %gearscore% gearscore and a %role% spec, summons from %city%.",
      -- Ambient flavor: events, seasons, time of day, shops, routes, tales, weather
      "%event% has %city% packed wall to wall. Couldn't get a table at %shop% to save my life.",
      "Nothing beats %timeofday% in %zone% when there's %weather% rolling in.",
      "%season% always makes me restless. Half a mind to take %route% and just see where it goes.",
      "Stopped at %shop% for a pint and ended up hearing the whole tale of %tale%. Worth the detour.",
      "Took %route% at %timeofday% and the view was unreal. Recommend it to anyone passing through.",
      "The old-timers at %shop% still argue about %tale% like it happened yesterday.",
      "%weather% over %zone% this %timeofday%. Beautiful and miserable in equal measure.",
      "They're decorating %city% for %event% already. The %season% air and the lanterns... it's a good time to be alive.",
      "A %race% %class% just strolled through %city% with %item% on their back like it was nothing. Some people have all the luck.",
      "Watched a %class% drop %spell% in the middle of the square just to show off. Half of %city% stopped to %emote%.",
      "Word is someone finally tracked down %rare% out in %zone%. Took them a %season% of camping, but they got it.",
      "Saw a %race% ride past on %mount% today and the whole street went quiet. Some things you just have to %emote% at.",
      "Anyone running %instance% %difficulty% tonight? I'll heal, I'll tank, I'll carry your bags — just get me out of %city%.",
      "Hit exalted with %rep% this %timeofday%. Took half a lifetime and more %gold% in repairs than I'll admit.",
      "Some %level% %class% asked me how to get to %zone%. Friend, you are very far from where you ought to be.",
      { "The %profession% trainer in %city% says %consumable% is selling for %gold% a stack now. Highway robbery.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"gruff","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      "Met a veteran who earned the title '%pvptitle%' the hard way. Bought him a round at %shop% and just listened.",
      "Someone soloed %boss% at %gearscore% gearscore and won't stop talking about it. Honestly? Fair enough.",
      "%weather% rolling in over %zone% at %timeofday%. The caravans on %route% are going to have a miserable night.",
      { "Old sailor at %shop% swears he saw %rare% from the deck off %zone%. Three drinks deep, mind you.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"coast"} },
      "Anyone got %consumable% to spare before the %instance% run? I'll trade %gold% or a favor, your call.",
      -- == Coast & sailors (expansion) ==
      { "Tide's coming in early. Pull the nets or lose them, lads, the sea doesn't wait on slow hands.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"gruff"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Hauled in a %fish% the size of my arm this morning. Sold it before it stopped flopping.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"boastful","greedy"}, areas={coast=3, rural=1} },
      { "Storm's stacking up black on the horizon. I've sailed enough to know: that one's got teeth.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Spent the whole tide mending nets while the others drank. Somebody's got to keep us fishing.", roles={"sailor","craftsman"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Gulls are screaming over the docks again. Means the shoals are running. Means coin, if we're quick.", roles={"sailor","vendor"}, moods={"cheerful","greedy"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Watched the harbor pilots bring a battered galleon in through the fog. Steady hands, those two.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Lost a good man overboard off the cape last season. The sea keeps what it takes. Pour one out.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"solemn","bitter"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Tide's out, flats are wide, and there's clams enough for a week if your back can stand the bending.", roles={"sailor","farmer"}, moods={"weary","cheerful"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Press a copper into the old sailor's palm and he'll read the weather from the gulls. Never wrong, the salt.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "First mate says we sail with the dawn tide whatever the sky does. I'd sooner sail in %weather% than cross him.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","weary"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Calm seas, full hold, and the harbor lights ahead. There's no finer feeling, none.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "The lighthouse keeper hasn't let the lamp go dark in forty years. Half the fleet owes that old soul their lives.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Salt cod, salt cod, fresh-dried and cheap by the barrel! Feeds a crew through a long crossing!", roles={"vendor","sailor"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Caught nothing but boots and a foul mood all morning. The %fish% are laughing at me, I swear it.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Don't whistle on the deck and don't name the day's catch. Bad luck, both. The sea's superstitious, so I am too.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","gruff"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { "Captain promised us shares of the cargo and paid us in promises. Last voyage I take with that one.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"bitter","gruff"}, areas={coast=3} },
      "The harbor smells of tar and brine and frying fish, and I wouldn't swap it for any perfume in the city.",
      -- == Rural, farms & harvest (expansion) ==
      { "Harvest's in early this year. Barn's full, cellar's stocked, and the %season% can do its worst.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Lost half a field to crows. Set up a scarecrow that frightens me more than the birds, frankly.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "The cow got into the turnips again. I'd be angrier if she didn't look so pleased about it.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Up before the cockerel, abed after the candles. Farming's no trade for a man who loves his sleep.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","gruff"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Rain's held off three weeks now. Whisper a prayer to whatever you favor, the wheat's gone to dust.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"nervous","weary"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Sheared the flock, sold the wool to a city trader for half what it's worth. City folk rob the country blind.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","gruff"}, areas={rural=3, city=1} },
      { "New lambs this morning, three of them, all on their feet by noon. Light, but it does the heart good.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Mill's grinding day and night with the harvest in. You can smell fresh flour clear across the valley.", roles={"farmer","craftsman"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Sold a fat hog to the inn down the road and bought my girl a ribbon with the coin. Good market day.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={rural=3, road=1} },
      { "Wolf took two ewes off the high pasture last night. I'll sit up with a bow tonight, see if he's bold enough to return.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={rural=3, wilderness=1} },
      { "Whole village turns out for the harvest. Hard work, but there's ale and a fiddle when the last sheaf's in.", roles={"farmer","citizen"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Tax collector came round for the King's share. Took the fattest goose and called it our duty. Duty's expensive.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Apples are coming in red and sweet. Press the windfalls for cider and you'll thank me come %season%.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Fixed the fence, patched the roof, mended the gate. A farm's a list of small wars you never quite win.", roles={"farmer","craftsman"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Plough's stuck in clay heavy as sin and the ox won't pull. Some days the land just says no.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { "Smoke from the cottages, dogs in the lane, bread cooling on every sill. The village wakes slow and I love it for that.", roles={"farmer","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={rural=3} },
      "Nothing in any city smells half so good as a hayfield cut fresh under a high summer sun.",
      -- == Battlefield, war-camp & siege (expansion, faction-neutral) ==
      { "Quiet on the line tonight. Quiet's worse than the fighting. You start hearing things in the dark.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"nervous","weary"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Movement in the treeline -- everyone down, blades ready, nobody breathes till I say.", roles={"soldier","guard"}, moods={"brave","nervous"}, areas={battlefield=3, wilderness=2, road=1} },
      { "Drew the dawn watch again. Whole camp asleep behind me, and only this cold and me awake to keep it.", roles={"soldier","guard"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Rations down to hardtack and hope. War always runs out of bread before it runs out of orders.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Sharpen your blade, check your straps, write your letter home. We move at first light.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","brave"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Sappers worked through the night. Come morning that wall comes down and Light help whoever's behind it.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "First battle. My hands won't stop shaking. The old hands say that's the body being smarter than the heart.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","nervous"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Saw the green recruit freeze when the horns blew. Pulled him back by the collar. We all freeze once.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","kindly"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "I didn't sign up to die in the mud over a hill nobody can name. But here I stand in it all the same.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Banners up, drums going, the whole field roaring at once. Light forgive me, part of me lives for it.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","boastful"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Field surgeon's tent never goes dark. I bring him water and try not to look. Bravest soul in this camp, that one.", roles={"soldier","priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "We hold this ridge or we lose the valley behind it. So we hold the ridge. Simple as a sword's edge.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Scout came back white as chalk and wouldn't say what he saw past the river. So we don't cross the river.", roles={"soldier","guard"}, moods={"nervous","cowardly"}, areas={battlefield=3, wilderness=1} },
      { "Won the field, buried the lost, struck the camp. Victory weighs near as heavy as the other thing.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Truce on the front for the festival. Strange, hearing songs from both camps drift over the same dark field.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Powder's damp, ballista's seized, and the order says assault at dawn regardless. War's run by fools, always was.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","gruff"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "Some boast loud before the charge to keep the fear from showing. I just check my friend's straps and mine.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","kindly"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { "If the horns blow tonight I'm first over the wall. Tell them at home I didn't hang back. Tell them I went forward.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      -- == Wilderness, beasts & the open dark (expansion) ==
      { "Three days into the wilds and I've forgotten what a roof feels like. The stars are a fair trade, mostly.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={wilderness=3, road=1} },
      { "Something big paced the camp all night, just past the firelight. Come dawn, tracks bigger than my two hands.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","cowardly"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Tracked a %monster% half a day through the brush. It tracked me right back. We both went home empty.", roles={"adventurer","soldier"}, moods={"wry","brave"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Lost the trail at dusk and the dark came down like a lid. Spent the night up a tree, no shame in it.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"cowardly","nervous"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Out here you learn fast: read the weather, mind the water, never camp in a dry riverbed. The wilds teach hard.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Brought down a stag clean with one shot at sixty paces. Venison for a week and a tale for a month.", roles={"adventurer","farmer"}, moods={"boastful","brave"}, areas={wilderness=3, rural=1} },
      { "A %critter% wandered into my camp and stole my whole supper while I dozed. Out-adventured by a rabbit. Glorious.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "The old hunter says the deep wood has rules and the first is humility. I'm learning to keep my voice low.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Fog rolled in off the marsh so thick I lost my own hands. Sat tight and counted breaths till it lifted.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","cowardly"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Heard %monster% calling to each other across the ridge after dark. Built the fire higher and slept with one eye open.", roles={"adventurer","soldier"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Days in the wilds and not a soul to talk to but my %companion%. It's started answering, which worries me.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","dreamy"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Found a hot spring deep in the backcountry and soaked till my fingers wrinkled. The wilds owe me that much.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Greenhorn wanted to charge the cave alone for glory. Talked him out of it. The wilds don't hand out glory, just graves.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","kindly"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { "Set my snares at dusk, woke to two hares and a fat grouse. The wild provides for the patient. Mostly.", roles={"adventurer","farmer"}, moods={"cheerful","weary"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      "Out past the last farmstead the road just gives up and the wild takes over. That line in the dirt always makes me pause.",
      -- == Road, caravans & travelers (expansion) ==
      { "Walked since dawn and the inn's still a smudge on the hill. My feet have filed a formal complaint.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Caravan master pays two silver a day to guard the wagons through the pass. Cheap, given the bandit talk.", roles={"guard","adventurer"}, moods={"gruff","greedy"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Heard there's highwaymen working the crossroads again. Keep your purse close and your blade closer, friend.", roles={"adventurer","guard"}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Met a peddler on the road with a cart of wonders and a story for each. Half lies, all delightful.", roles={"vendor","adventurer"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "The wayside inn between the towns is no palace, but a dry bed and a hot bowl after a day's walk? Heaven.", roles={"innkeeper","adventurer"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Shared a fire with strangers at the milestone last night. Come morning we were friends. The road does that.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Took %route% to save my feet and regretted it the moment a wheel cracked in the ruts. Walking's slower but honest.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "A noble's carriage forced us into the ditch to pass. Didn't even slow. The road's wide enough for manners, surely.", roles={"citizen","farmer"}, moods={"bitter","gruff"}, areas={road=3, rural=1} },
      { "Driving cattle to the city market down the long road. Three days of dust and lowing. The beasts complain less than I do.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={road=3, rural=1} },
      { "Milestones, mileposts, and the same crow following my cart for a league. Lonely work, the carter's road.", roles={"vendor","craftsman"}, moods={"weary","dreamy"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Bridge toll's gone up again. A copper to cross a stream a child could wade. Robbery with a gate on it.", roles={"vendor","citizen"}, moods={"bitter","greedy","wry"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Rain caught us between towns with no inn for a league. Huddled under the cart and called it an adventure. Barely.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={road=3} },
      { "Pilgrims passed at dawn, singing low, bound for the shrine over the hills. Gave them bread and good road.", roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"kindly","solemn"}, areas={road=3} },
      "Every crossroads has a leaning signpost some joker's turned the wrong way. Half my wandering's been that joker's fault.",
      -- == More city texture (light touch, varied roles/moods) ==
      { "Counted the day's takings twice and they came up short twice. Some apprentice has light fingers. I'll find them.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","gruff"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "A young lord tipped me a whole gold for holding his horse. Didn't even blink. The rich don't feel coin like we do.", roles={"urchin","citizen"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Slept under the bridge again. Watchman pretends not to see me, leaves a heel of bread. There's kindness in this hard city.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"kindly","weary"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Lifted an apple, ran three streets, and the grocer just laughed and waved. Some days the city's gentle to a small thief.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Know every rooftop and gutter in this quarter. Up high, nobody bothers a street kid. The pigeons and me own the sky.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"dreamy","brave"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "The other urchins and I run messages for a copper apiece. Fast feet, sharp eyes, closed mouths. Best couriers in the city.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"boastful","cheerful"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "My lord expects the estate spotless before the gala and the staff halved by his economies. Nobility is a great deal of polishing.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "One does not simply walk the market. One is jostled, fleeced, and shouted at by a man selling 'genuine' relics. I rather enjoy it.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Inherited the title and the debts in the same breath. They never put the debts on the family crest, do they.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Hosted the season's finest gala and not one guest commented on the orchestra I paid a fortune for. Society is thankless.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","bitter"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "The old houses look down their noses at my new fortune. Let them. My cellar's deeper and my parties are better.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","greedy"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Gave the better part of my purse to the orphanage and felt richer for it than the gold ever made me.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "I'll not set foot outside the walls. Wilds, roads, all of it -- full of mud and monsters and men who haven't bathed. The city for me.", roles={"noble","citizen"}, moods={"cowardly","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Glassblower's at it again, and the whole street stops to watch the molten gold dance on the rod. Real magic, that.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Three orders behind, an apprentice who can't temper steel, and a noble screaming for his ceremonial sword by dusk. Craft life.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"weary","gruff"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Cut a gem so clean today the jeweler went quiet, then doubled my fee without my asking. Pride in the work pays twice.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"boastful","greedy"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "The cobbler down the lane's been mending the same beggar's boots for free for years. Quietly. He'd hate me telling you.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Light grant me patience: the collection plate's lighter each week and the queue at my door grows longer. Faith costs, friend.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"weary","kindly"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Blessed a soldier's blade this morning and a baby this afternoon. The Light doesn't pick favorites and neither do I.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"warm","solemn"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Some come to the temple for the Light and some for the warm bench and the quiet. The doors are open to both, always.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=2} },
      "A pickpocket lifted my purse, found it empty, and slipped me a copper out of pity. This city contains multitudes.",
      -- == Drunkard, tavern & wry mood (expansion) ==
      { "I came in for one drink. That was, I'm told, the day before yesterday. Time's a slippery thing in a good tavern.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      { "The barkeep cut me off, so I'm drinking the rainwater off the awning out of principle. Principle and necessity.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry","bitter"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Lost a drinking contest to a dwarf, a tauren, and a goblin in one night. Different beasts, same humbling. Worth it.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={city=2, coast=1} },
      { "Some %drink% in me and I'll tell you the meaning of life. It's this stool, this fire, and not being asked to leave yet.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Buried my coin under the floorboards so I'd stop spending it on ale. Then dug it up. For ale. I know myself, see.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Greatest swordsman in the realm, me. Ask anyone. ...don't ask while I'm sober, the answer changes.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      -- == Vendor & greed (expansion) ==
      { "Buy low, sell high, and never let the buyer see you smile. That's the whole of the trade, and I'm a master of it.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","boastful"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { "Doubled my prices for the festival crowd and they thanked me for the privilege. The %event% is the merchant's harvest.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","cheerful"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "A man tried to haggle me down to nothing, so I haggled him UP and he didn't even notice. Pure art, that was.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { "Quality costs, friend. You want the cheap one, the goblin two stalls down will sell you something that catches fire.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"gruff","greedy"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "Gave a starving kid a loaf off my own cart and lost a copper of profit. Worth every bite of it. Don't tell my partner.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=2} },
      -- == Brave / cowardly civilian texture ==
      { "Heard a scream from the alley and I went toward it, not away. Turned out a cat. But I'd have fought a dragon. Probably.", roles={"citizen","guard"}, moods={"brave","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "When the alarm bells ring I bar the door, douse the lamp, and hide in the cellar with the preserves. Heroics are for other folk.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cowardly","wry"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      { "Everyone ran from the runaway cart. I caught the reins. Don't know why. My knees gave out after. But I caught them.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"brave","nervous"}, areas={city=2} },
      { "I've fled three towns ahead of three different troubles and I'll flee a fourth if I must. A coward who keeps breathing, that's me.", roles={"citizen","adventurer"}, moods={"cowardly","wry"}, areas={road=2, city=1} },
      { "Stood my ground at the gate when the others scattered. Wasn't brave. Just too scared to turn my back. Held the line, though.", roles={"guard","soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={battlefield=2, city=1} },
      -- == Innkeeper & quiet warmth (expansion) ==
      { "Storm's driven half the road into my common room. Standing room only, fire roaring, and nobody minding the crowd. Best nights, these.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { "Keep a room ready for the soldier whose family waits each season for his return. Empty so far. I'll keep it ready.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { "A traveler couldn't pay, so he washed pots for his bed. Left a carving of my inn on the mantel. Worth more than the coin.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={road=2} },
      "A good inn is a lighthouse on land: a warm window in the dark that tells the weary they've nearly made it home.",
    },
    -- two-person back-and-forth (speakers alternate A / B)
    duos = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 5: tagged duos (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"There's a %fish%-catching contest down at the dock this %timeofday%.", "Prize?", "A fat purse of %currency% and a year's bragging rights.", "...I haven't fished since I was a boy.", "Neither have half of them. That's the fun. Grab a rod, lose with dignity, drink with the winners."}, roles={"sailor","citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={coast=2, city=1} },
      { chain={"My %enchant% on your cloak holding up?", "Too well. It glows when I lie. Do you know how INCONVENIENT that is for a merchant?", "...I may have over-tuned it.", "You think? I haggled this morning and lit up like a festival lantern. Undo it before I starve."}, roles={"mage","vendor"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Cards at the %shop% tonight. You in?", "Last time you cleaned me out of a whole %season%'s savings.", "And I'll do it again. That's the offer.", "...at least you're honest about the robbery. Deal me in. A man should lose his coin to a friend, not a stranger."}, roles={"citizen","drunkard"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Bandits on the %route% again past the mile-stone.", "Same crew? The ones who 'tax' travelers and hand out receipts?", "The very same. Polite as you like, robbing you blind.", "...you have to almost respect the paperwork. Almost. Travel armed and travel together. Their politeness has a knife behind it."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"Your %companion%'s a clever little thing.", "Smarter than me on a bad %timeofday%. Found the safe ford when I'd have drowned us both crossing the %zone% river.", "You'd trust a beast over your own eyes?", "Out here? Every time. Pride drowns men. A good %companion% keeps them dry. Feed yours first tonight, that's my advice."}, roles={"adventurer","farmer"}, moods={"warm","wry"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"You fought in the deep halls of %instance%, didn't you. In your day.", "Went in for %item%, came out with a limp and a healthy fear of locked doors.", "What's behind the locked doors?", "I never opened them. That's WHY I came out. The bold ones opened the doors. We buried what was left of them in %zone%."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"The %weather%'s the worst I've seen this %season%.", "Roof's leaking over the common room. I've pots out catching it like a tinker's orchestra.", "Need a hand?", "Need a roofer and a miracle. But a hand and a %drink% will do till the sky relents. Climb up, mind the wet thatch."}, roles={"innkeeper","craftsman"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"They're holding the %activity% trials in the square for the %event%.", "The strongman lift? The footrace?", "All of it. A tauron's already bent an iron bar and a gnome's challenged him to a thinking contest in revenge.", "...who's winning the thinking contest?", "The gnome, smugly. The tauron, by simply not caring. It's a draw and they've become friends. Beautiful."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Quiet %timeofday% at the gate.", "Too quiet. The %weather%'s kept the travelers home and the trouble with them.", "Enjoy it. Quiet shifts are a gift.", "Quiet shifts are when a man gets to thinking. I'd rather a brawl than an hour alone with my own head, truth be told."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Spotted %rare% off the %route% at dawn. I swear it.", "You and every traveler since my grandfather.", "No, truly — it watched me, then walked into the mist like it owned it.", "...you know what? I believe you. Not because it's likely. Because your face has gone the way faces go when a man's seen a wonder. Hold onto that."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged duos (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"The %profession% guild raised the dues AGAIN.", "Same work, less coin, more stamped paper. I joined to make %item%, not to feed clerks.", "Could go independent. Sell out of a cart.", "And lose the guild mark? No buyer in %city% trusts an unstamped blade. They've got us, and they know it."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"You hear the %shop% changed hands?", "The old owner finally sold? After forty %season%?", "Sold to a goblin. Says he'll 'modernize' it.", "...there goes the one quiet corner in this %city%. Drink it in now, friend. By spring it'll have a queue and a surcharge."}, roles={"citizen","innkeeper"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"What's the maddest thing you ever did for coin, back when?", "Guided a noble's hunting party through %zone% in the %weather%. They shot at every %critter% and hit nothing but my temper.", "Carried a sealed crate down the %route% and asked no questions. Best %gold% I ever made. Worst sleep I ever had.", "...what was in the crate?", "I asked no QUESTIONS, friend. That was the whole arrangement. Some coin you earn by not knowing."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={road=1, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"Spare a copper for an old soldier?", "I've a copper and a question, friend. Which %zone% did you serve?", "...the cold one. The northern campaign.", "Then keep your copper and take this seat instead. I served it too. Sit. We'll trade names the recruiters never bothered to remember."}, roles={"drunkard","soldier"}, moods={"weary","kindly"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { chain={"That urchin's been eyeing your coin purse the whole time we've talked.", "I know. I left three coppers loose at the top on purpose.", "...why?", "Because I was that child once, and a stranger once 'forgot' to guard his purse near me. You pay the kindness forward where it lands."}, roles={"citizen","urchin"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"They've raised the %route% toll at the bridge again.", "War tax, they're calling it. Everything's a war tax now.", "My cart of %tradegood% barely clears a profit after.", "Then we travel together, split the toll, and share a guard. The road's cheaper and safer in company. Always was."}, roles={"farmer","vendor"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"You actually saw %boss% with your own eyes?", "Close as I am to you. We didn't fight it — we HID, and prayed, and it passed.", "And you call that a tale worth telling?", "The survivors tell the quiet tales, friend. The loud heroes are mostly names on stones in %zone%. I'll take a coward's long life over a hero's short song."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Noble's throwing a grand ball for the %event%, they say.", "Half the %city% invited, the other half catering it.", "Which half are we?", "Catering, friend. Always catering. But the kitchen hears every secret the ballroom whispers. We'll know more than the guests by midnight."}, roles={"citizen","noble"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Forty %season% I've kept this stall on this corner.", "And you've never once raised your prices. The whole quarter knows it.", "Raise them on WHO? The urchins? The old widows? They're my neighbors, not my marks.", "...that's why the corner's always busy and the fancy stalls aren't. Folk pay loyalty back, eventually."}, roles={"vendor"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Caravan master wants us through %zone% by nightfall.", "Through there? After dark? With this cargo of %gem%?", "He's paying double and praying we don't meet what hunts that road.", "...double won't spend if we're dead. But the children need feeding. Aye, alright. Sharpen up and keep the lanterns low."}, roles={"adventurer","soldier"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"My %companion% won't go near the old mill anymore.", "Animals know things. What's at the mill?", "Nothing, last I looked. But the beast plants its feet and growls at the dark inside.", "...then we don't go in the mill. I've lived this long by trusting a frightened %companion% over my own brave nonsense. Walk on."}, roles={"farmer","adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={rural=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"You've that faraway look. The %season% getting to you?", "It's the %timeofday% the light goes long and gold. Reminds me of someone I lost.", "...want to talk on it?", "No. But sit a while and watch the light with me. Grief's lighter with a body beside it, even a quiet one."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged duos (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"You ever earn a real title, back in the day? A %pvptitle%, a %title%, anything?", "Earned '%title%' in %zone%. Bled for it. Now it just gets me a free %drink% from old soldiers.", "That's the best use of a title there is, friend.", "Aye. Glory fades. A free %drink% from someone who understands? That keeps."}, roles={"soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"That's a fine %mount% you've got tethered there.", "Won her off a %race% gambler in %city% who bet more than he had.", "Lucky.", "Skilled. There's a difference, and I'll thank you to remember it when you tell the tale."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Saw a %class% throw a %spell% in the square that lit the whole street blue.", "Showing off for the festival crowd, no doubt.", "Maybe. But a child near me gasped like she'd seen the Light itself.", "...then it wasn't showing off. It was a gift. Let the mages have their moment."}, roles={"citizen","mage"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"What was the worst posting you ever pulled, soldiering?", "Holding a frozen ridge in %zone% through a %season% of %weather%. We burned the wagons for warmth in the end.", "Did you hold it?", "We held it. Half of us came down the mountain. The ridge wasn't worth one of them. They never are.", "...to the ones who didn't come down, then.", "To them. Every %timeofday%, I lift one. Sit, lift one with me."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={battlefield=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Tide's wrong and the %weather%'s worse. We sail or we sit?", "We sit. I've buried enough crew to a captain's pride.", "The cargo of %tradegood% spoils if we wait.", "Cargo spoils. Men drown. One of those I can replace by morning. Drop anchor."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Heard you finally hit exalted with %rep%.", "A whole %season% of dailies for it. Got the %mount% at the end and a deep mistrust of quartermasters.", "Worth it?", "Ask me when my %mount% stops making the stablemaster cry with envy. ...so, yes. Worth it."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","boastful"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"The %event%'s got the whole %city% doing that silly %emote% in the square.", "The dance? My knees said no the moment the music started.", "Mine said no and I did it anyway. Now they're SHOUTING at me.", "...worth it, though?", "Every aching step. Help me to a stool and a %drink% and I'll tell you it was worth it again."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Tracks in the snow here are fresh. Big %monster%, came through at dusk.", "How big?", "Bigger than the campfire stories. Keep the %consumable% close and the blade closer.", "...I knew I should've taken the coast route.", "Too late for should-haves. Back to back, eyes up, and we'll laugh about it in %city% if we live."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { chain={"You enchanted my old blade with %enchant%. It hums now.", "It'll hold an edge through a whole %season% of fighting. Don't waste it.", "On what wouldn't I waste it?", "On tavern brawls and showing off. Good steel's for the work that matters. The rest you can do with your fists."}, roles={"mage","craftsman"}, moods={"gruff","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"First muster at dawn. They march us to %zone%.", "Your hands are shaking.", "I know. I can't make them stop.", "Don't try. Mine shook my first time too. You stay close, you watch my left, I watch your right, and the shaking won't matter. We just keep moving."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={battlefield=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Lighthouse lamp's been dark two nights running.", "The old keeper's not been seen. Somebody ought to climb up and check.", "In this %weather%? Up those stairs?", "...aye. In this %weather%, up those stairs. A dark lamp means a ship that doesn't come home. Fetch the rope. We go together."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"That noble's coach is stuck fast in the %route% mud.", "And paying nothing for the help, I'll wager.", "A whole %gold% to whoever frees it, he says.", "...for a %gold% I'd push his lordship himself through the mud. Grab the wheel, we're suddenly very loyal subjects."}, roles={"noble","citizen"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"A %companion% followed me the whole way from %zone%.", "Whose is it?", "Nobody's now. Half-starved, half-wild, wholly mine the moment it chose my fire.", "...you can't feed every stray on the road, friend.", "Can't feed every one. Can feed THIS one. That's how it always starts, and I've never once regretted it."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"What's the grandest %instance% you ever set foot in?", "The deep halls under %zone%. Ceilings you couldn't see the top of. We felt like ants in a god's house.", "Find anything?", "%item%, and a lot of dust, and a respect for the old builders I've never lost.", "...do the old places still call to you?", "Every %season%. But the knees said no, same as the dance. I send the young ones now and live it through their tales."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={road=1, wilderness=1} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged duos (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"That %herb% you pulled from the %zone% gully — worth anything?", "Dried and bundled? A fine %currency% from any alchemist who knows their trade.", "And from one who doesn't?", "Double. The ignorant always pay most. Don't tell them I said so."}, roles={"farmer","craftsman"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={wilderness=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Struck a vein of %ore% up the hill near pure.", "Keep your voice DOWN. The %city% levy-men have ears in every tavern.", "Let them hear. I earned that vein.", "You earned it. They'll tax it. That's the whole sad song of mining, friend. Now hush and haul it quiet."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"boastful","bitter"}, areas={rural=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"Sat that bank a whole %timeofday% for one %fish%.", "One? I'd have packed up by noon.", "That's why you've never tasted a catch like this. The river gives to the patient and the stubborn.", "...which are you?", "Both. Out here they're the same man."}, roles={"sailor","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={coast=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"What's that smell off your cookfire? The whole camp's drifting over.", "%food%, slow over the coals, with a pinch of %herb% my mother swore by.", "Share it round and I'll forgive you the last three cold nights.", "Sit, then. A good %food% on a bad %route% is the only sermon worth preaching out here."}, roles={"innkeeper","adventurer"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Your %companion% hasn't left your heel since %zone%.", "The little beast pulled me from a ditch the night the %weather% near took me. I owe it everything.", "It's a %critter%. It probably wanted the warmth.", "...maybe. But it stayed. That's more than most folk manage. I'll feed it first till the day I die."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"They're saying %rare%'s been seen in %zone% again.", "Same as last %season%. And the one before.", "You don't believe it?", "I believe in the LOOKING. Whether the beast is real or not, it's got three generations of us out walking the hills at dawn. That's a kind of magic too."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","dreamy"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"Noble's %gem% went missing, they say.", "And turned up round a certain urchin's neck, they ALSO say.", "Is no one telling the watch?", "...look at the child's face, then look at the noble's coffers, and ask me that again."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Twelve hours hauling %tradegood% and my back's done.", "Mine too. And the foreman's already eyeing tomorrow's ship.", "There's always another ship.", "Aye. And we're always the ones who carry it. Drink up. The dock pays in coin and aches, and we take both."}, roles={"sailor","citizen"}, moods={"weary","bitter"}, areas={coast=2, city=1} },
      { chain={"Knelt at the wayside shrine on the %route% today.", "Light? Earth Mother? Loa?", "Out there? I stopped asking which. Something listened. That was enough.", "...the road makes simpler believers of us all, doesn't it.", "It does. No temple walls to argue over. Just the sky and whatever's behind it."}, roles={"priest","adventurer"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"Won a %toy% at the %event% ring toss.", "Keeping it?", "Gave it to the first urchin I saw. Couldn't keep a thing that small against a face that happy.", "...you old softie.", "I contain multitudes. Now help me win another. There's more urchins where that one came from."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={city=2} },
      { chain={"Three days on the %route% to %zone% and not a soul but a goblin.", "Selling %consumable% at a robbery price, no doubt.", "Four times the %city% rate. I bought two.", "Of course you did. The road makes thieves of the goblins and fools of the rest of us. Welcome to travel."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"Wheel cracked on the %route% in the worst of the %weather%.", "Out here? Light help us. Got a spare?", "Got a spare, got two hands, got a foul temper. We'll manage.", "...you named the wheel, didn't you.", "I named the wheel. Don't judge me. A man needs someone to curse on a night like this."}, roles={"craftsman","adventurer"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged duos (shared / all factions)
      -- ============================================================
      -- Market & vendor duos
      { chain={"You're charging %currency% for ONE %gem%? My grandmother mined better in her sleep.", "Then wake your grandmother and undercut me, friend. Till then it's my stall and my price.", "...fine. But throw in a %herb% and we've a deal.", "A %herb%. The gall. ...done. Now move along before I change my mind."}, roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","gruff"}, areas={city=3} },
      { chain={"Caravan brought your %tradegood% in from %zone% yet?", "Two days late and half of it spoiled in the %weather%. I'm selling the rest cheap before it turns worse.", "Then I'll take the lot off you. Cheap suits me fine.", "...you vulture. Aye, take it. A loss shared is a loss halved, I suppose."}, roles={"vendor"}, moods={"weary","greedy"}, areas={city=2, coast=1} },
      { chain={"That %race% at the end stall is selling 'genuine %item%' again.", "The painted ones? He moved forty last %event%.", "Forty! And the watch does nothing?", "The watch bought three. Of COURSE they do nothing."}, roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","bitter"}, areas={city=3} },
      -- Guard & watch duos
      { chain={"Anything stir on the wall this %timeofday%?", "A drunk %class% tried to fight the gate. The gate won.", "It usually does. Log it and let him sleep it off.", "Already snoring in the stocks. Quietest prisoner we've had all %season%."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={city=3} },
      { chain={"They're saying %monster% tracks turned up on the %route% past the mile-stone.", "This close to the %city%? In daylight?", "That's why the captain's doubling the gate watch. Bring your %consumable% tonight, it'll be a long one.", "...I knew I should've taken the harbor posting."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"nervous","gruff"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"New lad asked me where the %instance% entrance was. Told him to mind his post.", "He's keen. Keen's better than the lazy ones.", "Keen gets you killed in %zone%. I'll take lazy and breathing.", "...you weren't always this grim, you know.", "Aye. Then I served a %season% in %zone%. Mind your post, lad."}, roles={"guard","soldier"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={city=2} },
      -- Innkeeper & traveler duos
      { chain={"Room for the night? The %weather% drove me clean off the %route%.", "Last one at the top, and a bowl of %food% if you want it. Pay what you can.", "I can't pay much. A %class% cleaned me out at dice two towns back.", "Then you'll wash the pots and tell me the tale of it. Fair trade for a dry bed, that."}, roles={"innkeeper","adventurer"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={road=3, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Bard's playing the ballad of %tale% again. Third time tonight.", "Aye, and look — the whole room's gone quiet for it again. Let him play.", "He only knows the one song.", "He plays the one song with his whole heart. That's rarer than a hundred songs done cold."}, roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"You set my hearthstone, poured my usual, AND remembered my %companion%'s name.", "It's the trade, friend. A good inn remembers you so the road doesn't have to.", "...I think I'll stay another %timeofday%.", "They always do. The stew sees to that."}, roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      -- Adventurer reminiscence duos (NPC veterans, not LFG)
      { chain={"You ever miss it? The %zone% days, the open %route%?", "Every %season%. Then it %weather%s and my old knee remembers why I quit.", "Ha. The knee's an honest counselor.", "Honest and loud. It's never once been wrong about a storm."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"That your old %item% on the mantel?", "Aye. Carried it from %zone% to the gates of %instance% and back. Doesn't glow anymore.", "Why keep it, then?", "Because I do. Some things you keep for the weight, not the worth."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { chain={"A young %class% asked me today how to get to %zone%.", "Did you tell them the safe road or the fast one?", "I told them the truth: there's no safe road to %zone%, only company worth dying beside.", "...that's the realest thing you've said since the war."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={road=2, city=1} },
      -- Soldier & war-camp duos
      { chain={"Quartermaster's short on %consumable% again before %zone%.", "He's short on everything but bad news.", "Then we share what we've got and make the rest up with spite.", "Spite I've got barrels of. Pass it down the line."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"wry","gruff"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"First muster tomorrow. They're marching us to %zone%.", "Scared?", "Sick with it.", "Good. The cocky ones get the rest of us killed. Stay scared, stay by me, and we'll see another %season%."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={battlefield=3, road=1} },
      -- Mage & priest duos
      { chain={"Your portal to %zone% dropped me in a %weather%-soaked bog. A BOG.", "It was within a league of the mark. That's well within tolerance.", "There is no tolerance for a bog!", "...I'll re-tune the anchor. Stop dripping on my reagents."}, roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={city=2} },
      { chain={"Enchanted the merchant's %item% with %enchant% like he asked.", "And he paid the proper fee?", "Half now, the rest 'when it sells.' We'll see the rest never.", "Mark his name. The Kirin Tor's patience is long, but the ledger is longer."}, roles={"mage"}, moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      { chain={"You've knelt at that altar since dawn, Sister.", "A %class% didn't come back from %zone%. I'm keeping the count the Light asked me to keep.", "...shall I bring you something? Bread, %drink%?", "Sit a while instead. The dead are lighter when they're mourned in company."}, roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={city=2, battlefield=1} },
      -- Craftsman duos
      { chain={"Ran clean out of %ore% halfway through the commission.", "The whole %city%'s short. The mines off %zone% flooded in the %weather%.", "Then I'll barter my %profession% for scraps and the noble can wait.", "Let him wait. Good steel won't be rushed, and he can't tell the difference anyway."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"You carved a %toy% for the innkeeper's girl?", "Took an evening. Cost me nothing.", "Soft of you.", "Bought me a %season% of free stew and a smile worth more than the stew. Who's soft now?"}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","wry"}, areas={rural=2, city=1} },
      -- Farmer & rural duos
      { chain={"Frost spared the %season% crop. Don't say it loud.", "Too late, you said it. Now we've jinxed the whole valley.", "...fetch the cider. If we're doomed we may as well be merry about it.", "Now THAT'S the wisest thing you've said since planting."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { chain={"Tax collector's riding the %route% this week, they say.", "Let him. He'll find empty cellars and emptier purses.", "Hide the seed %tradegood% deep. They took the neighbor's and he near starved.", "...quiet, then. We know nothing, we've got nothing, and the cellar stays shut."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","nervous"}, areas={rural=3} },
      -- Sailor & coast duos
      { chain={"Glass is dropping fast. There's weather in it, mark me.", "How long have we got?", "Till the next tide, no more. Lash the %tradegood% down and douse the galley fire.", "...you've that look again. The one from the night we lost the skiff.", "Aye. So move quick and pray I'm wrong. I'm rarely wrong, and I hate that most of all."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Caught a %fish% the size of the cabin boy this morning.", "Liar. You say that every haul.", "Come to the dock and weigh it before the vendor does!", "...alright, that IS a monster. Drinks are on you, then, since you're rich now."}, roles={"sailor","vendor"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"My boy's first voyage out of %zone% and I've not slept a wink.", "He's crewing under a good captain. The best on this coast.", "The best still answer to the sea, and the sea answers to no one.", "...come away from the dock, friend. Watching the horizon won't pull the sail any faster. Wait with me by the fire instead."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","kindly"}, areas={coast=3} },
      -- Noble & urchin duos
      { chain={"You there, urchin — mind my %mount% and there's a copper in it.", "A copper? I'd not cross the gutter for a copper, your lordship.", "...a silver, then, and not one word about the mud on my boots.", "Now that's a deal worth crossing for. Right this way, m'lord."}, roles={"noble","urchin"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"The little ones know every gap in the %city% walls, m'lady.", "Then I'll hire them. A hot meal buys sharper eyes than any patrol.", "...you'd make a fearsome spymaster.", "I'd make a fed one of every child in the lower quarter. That's the better title."}, roles={"noble","urchin"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      -- Drunkard & tavern duos
      { chain={"How long you been sat in this corner, friend?", "What %season% is it?", "...that long, eh.", "Bring me a %drink% and I'll tell you the tale of %boss%. Half of it's even true."}, roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      -- City-life & festival duos
      { chain={"The %event% banners are up across the whole quarter.", "Already? The %season%'s barely turned.", "The %city% never needs much excuse to hang a banner and sell %food%.", "...and I never need much excuse to buy it. Lead on."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={city=3} },
      { chain={"Watch the lamplighters race the dusk down the long street.", "Same every %timeofday%. I never tire of it.", "Forty years I've crossed this square and never once stopped to look.", "Then stop tonight. The %city%'s prettiest in that grey hour, and it won't wait for you."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={city=3} },
      { chain={"Is %gearscore% gearscore enough for %instance% on %difficulty%?", "More than. Bring %consumable% and you're set.", "Saving you a spot. Summon's up in %city%."}, roles={"adventurer"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A %race% just outbid me on %item% by %gold%.", "Ruthless. The auction house in %city% is a battlefield.", "I'll get the next one. Or I'll cry. Possibly both."}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"How do night elves get anywhere in this city? It's all bridges and trees.", "Slowly, and with great elegance.", "Mostly we just fall and call it 'shadowmelding'."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Got turned into a sheep for brawling in Dalaran again.", "The Kirin Tor warned you.", "Worth it. Baa."}, roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry"} },
      { chain={"Aldor or Scryers, which do you side with?", "Whichever's offering the better rewards this week.", "A diplomat, I see."}, moods={"wry","greedy"} },
      { chain={"Is it safe to walk the Booty Bay docks at night?", "Define 'safe.' Define 'walk.' Define 'night.'", "...I'll take a guard."}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { chain={"Do you ever just stop and appreciate how beautiful these cities are?", "Between the wars and the auction house? Rarely. But yeah, sometimes.", "Sometimes is enough."}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"New in the city. Any advice?", "Don't trust goblins, don't insult anyone's mother, and tip the bard.", "...and never split the loot in a crowded tavern."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Bartender, what's good tonight?", "The ale, the stew, and the company. In that order.", "I'll take all three and a story to go."}, roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"For the Alliance!", "For the Horde!", "For the love of- can we NOT do this in the bank line?"}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Move along, citizen.", "I live here.", "...Move along anyway. It's been that kind of shift."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Did you hear what happened in Theramore?", "Don't. Just... don't. Not today.", "Aye. Pour one out."}, moods={"solemn"} },
      { chain={"Why's everyone gathered in the square?", "Public hanging.", "...of a really bad street mime, but still, drama."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"First time in the big city. It's... a lot.", "You'll get used to it. Stick to the main roads and trust your gut.", "And never, ever follow a goblin into an alley."}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Gnomes and goblins should NOT be allowed to do engineering in the same city.", "Agreed. The last 'demonstration' took out a city block.", "In their defense, it was a very impressive city block."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Why are trolls always saying 'mon'?", "Why are humans always saying 'epic loot'?", "...fair point, mon."}, moods={"wry"} },
      { chain={"Is it just me or are there too many people summoning mounts INSIDE the bank?", "It's not just you.", "Someone's kodo is currently blocking the entire auction house."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Met someone in the tavern last night.", "Adventurer?", "Baker, actually. Real trade, steady hands, makes incredible bread. I'm smitten.", "Marry the baker."}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"How long have you been sitting in this tavern?", "What day is it?", "...that long, huh."}, roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Why is the line at the bank so long?", "Tax season.", "Even with a war on, there's taxes?", "ESPECIALLY with a war on."}, moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Who keeps dueling right outside the bank?", "Same two warriors every day.", "At this point it's less a rivalry and more a marriage."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Why does every tavern have that one drunk who challenges everyone to a duel?", "Tradition.", "He's undefeated because nobody takes him seriously enough to fight."}, roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"You ever just stand in the capital and watch everyone rush by?", "All the time. Everyone's the hero of their own story.", "And here we are, two faces in a thousand of them.", "Best seat in the house, if you ask me."}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"They're raising the bridge for a ship. We'll be stuck on this side for an hour.", "Tavern's right there.", "...I've never loved a delayed bridge more in my life."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Lost my whole coin purse to the auction house today.", "Buying or selling?", "Buying. I had a plan.", "You always have a plan. That's the problem."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Is the city always this loud?", "Only when it's awake. Come back before dawn, it's a different world.", "I'll take your word for it. I value sleep."}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Heard the King's holding court today.", "Good luck getting near the keep. Whole city turned out.", "I just want to deliver my cabbages.", "The cabbages will have to wait for the realm, friend."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"You're out late.", "Couldn't sleep. The city's quieter now. I like it.", "Aye. The night's the only time this place stops shouting.", "Then let's not waste it talking. Mind the view a while?"}, moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"What's that crowd by the docks?", "Sailor came back with a tale and a sea monster's tooth.", "Real tooth?", "Real enough for the price of his next three drinks."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"boastful"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { chain={"You from around here?", "Born three streets over. Never left. Never wanted to.", "Must be nice, having one place be home.", "It is. Stay a while. The city grows on you."}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Meet you by the city fountain in five.", "Which fountain? There's like four.", "The one where we always meet.", "...right. The one with the pigeon that hates me. Got it."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Is the city always this crowded at festival time?", "This is a quiet day.", "...I need to lie down.", "Tavern's right there, friend. Welcome to the capital."}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"You buying or selling at the auction house?", "Browsing.", "Nobody just 'browses' the auction house.", "...fine. Spending money I don't have on things I don't need. Happy?"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"How's business at the stall today?", "Slow. Everyone's saving coin for the festival.", "I'll buy something to break your streak.", "Bless you, that's why I keep the corner stall."}, roles={"vendor"}, moods={"weary","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Officer, someone stole my coin purse!", "Was it a goblin?", "...maybe?", "Then it's gone, friend. Light keep it. Want directions to the bank instead?"}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Did you HEAR what happened at the keep?", "No, what?!", "...I don't actually know, I was hoping you did.", "...we are terrible at gossip."}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Heard the dragons are stirring up north.", "They're always stirring. Scaly drama merchants, the lot of them.", "Say that louder. See if Alexstrasza's listening.", "...suddenly I have somewhere else to be."}, moods={"gossipy","wry"} },
      { chain={"Why's that paladin been kneeling in the Cathedral since dawn?", "Lost his whole company in the north. The Light's all he's got left.", "...I'll light a candle and leave him be.", "That's the kindest thing you can do."}, roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Think the war'll ever actually end?", "Wars end. Then somebody finds a new reason. Always do.", "Cheerful.", "I'm a realist with a drink in my hand. Same thing some nights."}, moods={"bitter","weary"} },
      { chain={"That orc and that human have been arm-wrestling for an hour.", "In neutral Booty Bay, no less.", "Goblin's taking bets on both.", "Goblin always wins, then. The only true neutral party."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { chain={"LFM %instance% %difficulty%, need a %role%. %gearscore%+ and bring %consumable%.", "Summon from %city%?", "Aye, soon as we've a %class% for the last slot.", "On my way. Don't pull %boss% without me, I mean it."}, roles={"adventurer"} },
      { chain={"Is it worth grinding %rep% all the way to exalted?", "Depends. The %mount% at the end is worth more than %gold% to the right buyer.", "Sold. I'll start the %profession% dailies this %timeofday%.", "Pace yourself. That rep broke better folk than us."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary"} },
      { chain={"Camped %zone% for %rare% three nights running.", "Still nothing?", "Nothing but %weather% and regret.", "It'll spawn the moment you log to sleep. They always do.", "...you're right and I hate it."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { chain={"Bard at %shop% is taking requests.", "Ask for the ballad of %tale%.", "Too sad for a %season% night, surely.", "That's exactly why. A good dirge and a warm pint — best %timeofday% you can buy.", "...go on then. Make us weep into the ale."}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A %race% %class% just walked in wielding %item%.", "The real one?", "Glows like a dropped star. Either it's real or it's the best forgery in %city%.", "Buy them a drink and find out. Subtly.", "There is nothing subtle about you."}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"How'd the %instance% run go?", "We wiped on %boss% six times, then a %class% dropped %spell% and it just... clicked.", "%difficulty%?", "%difficulty%. We were underleveled and overconfident.", "The two great traditions of this realm. Drinks on me."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"} },
      { chain={"Took %route% out to %zone% for the %event% festivities.", "Worth the trip?", "%weather% the whole way, but the lanterns at the end? Worth every copper.", "And the %gold% you spent on trinkets, no doubt.", "...the festival economy is a predator and I am its prey."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"road"} },
      -- == Coast & docks duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Tide's running hard out the channel. We sail on the turn or not at all.", "Then we sail. I've no patience for another night at anchor.", "Brave words from a man who heaved over the rail all last voyage."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Smell that wind shift? There's weather coming off the deep.", "Storm by dusk, I'd wager. Best double the moorings.", "Already done. I've not lost a boat yet and I don't aim to start.", "That's why I crew under you, old man."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"They're loading %tradegood% onto the foreign ship. Lot of it.", "And paying in %currency%, I hear. Somebody's getting rich off this port.", "Long as the coin trickles down to the docks, I'll haul whatever they like.", "It never trickles down. It pools at the top and we mop it."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"bitter","greedy"}, areas={coast=2} },
      { chain={"Caught a %fish% this morning the size of my forearm.", "Liar. You always say that.", "Come to the stall and see it before the vendor buys it off me!", "...alright, that IS a big fish. I owe you a drink."}, roles={"sailor","vendor"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Ship's three days overdue. My boy's aboard her.", "The fog's been thick past the cape. Slow sailing, not lost sailing.", "You don't know that.", "No. But I've waited on that same dock for my own. They came back. His will too."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","kindly"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Why's the lighthouse keeper never come down to the tavern?", "Says the lamp can't mind itself. Forty years he's said it.", "Lonely way to live.", "Or the most company a man can keep, watching every soul out there find their way home."}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Gulls are screaming inland. Mark me, that's a blow coming.", "You read birds now?", "I read forty years of getting it wrong until I got it right. Reef the sails."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={coast=3} },
      -- == Rural, farm & village duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Frost held off another night. The %season% crop might just make it.", "Don't count it till it's in the barn. Weather's a liar this time of year.", "You'd find a cloud in a clear sky, you would.", "Aye, and I've never lost a harvest to optimism."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","gruff"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { chain={"Wolf took two lambs out the south field last night.", "Two? It'll be back, then. They always come back for easy meat.", "I'll sit up with the dogs and a lantern.", "I'll sit with you. Bring the good ale, it'll be a long watch."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={rural=3, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"Market price for grain's dropped again. The city merchants are bleeding us.", "Same every year after a good harvest. Plenty makes us poor, somehow.", "There's a cruel joke in there.", "The joke's on whoever thought farming was a path to fortune."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { chain={"Old mare foaled before dawn. Both came through fine.", "That's the third this %season%. Good blood in that stock.", "Reckon the foal'll fetch a fine price come the fair.", "Don't sell her. I saw you name her already. You never sell the named ones."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { chain={"You hear the harvest festival's back on this year?", "After last %season%? Didn't think we'd have the heart for it.", "That's exactly why we need it. A village that can't dance is a village half-buried.", "...then I'll fetch the fiddle down from the loft."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"kindly","cheerful"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { chain={"Scarecrow's gone again. Third one this month.", "Crows or kids?", "Crows wouldn't take the hat. It's kids. Cheeky little urchins from the mill.", "Leave 'em be. A stolen hat's a small toll for a quiet field."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={rural=3} },
      -- == Battlefield & war-camp duos (expansion, faction-neutral) ==
      { chain={"Drums on the far ridge again. They don't mean to let us sleep.", "Let them drum. A man can fear in rhythm same as silence.", "...you always know the wrong thing to say to make me feel better.", "It's a gift. Now sharpen your blade and stop your shaking."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","cowardly"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"Quartermaster's short on arrows and shorter on patience.", "Tell him to be short on something useful, like the enemy.", "I'll pass that along. He'll have us both on latrine duty.", "Worth it. Somebody had to say it."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"First battle tomorrow. I won't lie, I'm scared sick.", "Good. The ones who aren't scared are the ones who get us all killed.", "That's meant to comfort me?", "It's meant to keep you alive. Stay scared, stay sharp, stay close to me."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"Healer's tent took three of mine through the night.", "Did they hold?", "Two did. The Light kept what it could.", "Then we carry the third, and we carry on. That's the whole of it out here."}, roles={"soldier","priest"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"Saw the captain crying behind the supply wagon last night.", "Say nothing. Not a word, to anyone.", "I wasn't going to. Makes me trust her more, truth be told.", "Aye. A leader who can't grieve can't lead. Let her keep her dark corner."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"They say we take the wall at dawn.", "They said that the last three dawns.", "One of these days they'll be right.", "Pray it's a day we're rested. Now eat. Cold rations beat fighting hungry."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","gruff"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      -- == Wilderness, wilds & hunting duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Tracks here are fresh. Something big came through at dusk.", "%monster%?", "Bigger. Don't make the fire too bright and keep the blade where you can reach it.", "...suddenly I miss the city walls something fierce."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { chain={"Listen. The whole forest's gone quiet.", "That's never good. Critters don't hush for nothing.", "Back to back. Whatever it is, it's close.", "If we live through this, I am never leaving a paved road again."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { chain={"Slept under the open sky in %zone% last night.", "Cold?", "Bitter. But the stars out there — no city lantern ever made anything so fine.", "Spoken like a man who's never woken with frost in his boots.", "...the boots were a problem, I'll grant you."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { chain={"Snare's empty again. Three nights, nothing.", "Beasts have moved on. We follow or we starve.", "Or we turn back for the village while we've still legs.", "...turning back. There's no shame in a warm hearth, whatever the bards sing."}, roles={"adventurer","farmer"}, moods={"weary","cowardly"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { chain={"Found %herb% growing thick by the spring up the gully.", "Worth a fortune dried and sold in %city%.", "If we can carry it out past whatever's been watching us since noon.", "...you felt it too, then. Pack quick. Quiet."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"greedy","nervous"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      -- == Road, caravan & traveler duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Caravan master says we push through the night to make the inn by dawn.", "Through the pass? After the talk of bandits?", "More guards than goods on this trip. We'll be fine.", "That's exactly what they said on the last caravan that didn't come back."}, roles={"adventurer","soldier"}, moods={"brave","cowardly"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"How far to the next inn, you reckon?", "Half a day if the bridge still stands. A full one if it's washed out again.", "And if it's washed out?", "Then we sleep in the cart and tell the children it's an adventure."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"Stranger on the ridge has been keeping pace with us an hour.", "Highwayman?", "Or another traveler nervous as we are. Hard to say on the road.", "Hail him friendly, hand on your blade. That's the road way."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"Best inn on this whole route is %shop%, no contest.", "For the beds or the ale?", "For the innkeeper. Remembers your name, your order, and your troubles. Rare gold, that.", "...now I'm homesick for a place I've not reached yet."}, roles={"adventurer","innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"Wheel's cracked. We're going nowhere till it's mended.", "Out here? In this %weather%?", "Out here. Gather wood, I'll find the spare. Could be worse.", "How, exactly, could this be worse?", "...don't tempt the road, friend. It listens."}, roles={"craftsman","adventurer"}, moods={"gruff","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"They say a noble's coach passed this way carrying a fortune in %gem%.", "And you're telling me on an open road because...?", "Because half the road's heard it too. Keep your eyes sharp tonight.", "Wonderful. Now I'll not sleep a wink."}, roles={"noble","adventurer"}, moods={"greedy","nervous"}, areas={road=3} },
      -- == Noble & urchin duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"You there, urchin — fetch my horse and there's a copper in it.", "A copper? I'd not cross the street for a copper, your lordship.", "...cheeky. A silver, then, and not a word about the mud on my boots.", "Now THAT'S a bargain. Right this way, m'lord."}, roles={"noble","urchin"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"My family's name has graced this realm for nine generations.", "And what's it graced lately besides the tax rolls?", "...I'll have you know I funded the new orphanage wing.", "Then your name's done one fine thing. Build a second wing and I'll even mean the bow."}, roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
      { chain={"Spare a coin for an orphan, kind sir?", "I've nothing on me, lad. Truly.", "Then spare a story instead. The ones with full purses never have time for those.", "...sit down, then. You've earned a tale and half my bread for the asking of it."}, roles={"urchin","adventurer"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"The little ones run the rooftops better than my guards run the streets.", "They know every gutter and gap in the city, m'lady.", "Then hire them. A coin and a hot meal buys sharper eyes than any patrol.", "...you'd make a fearsome spymaster. The urchins would adore you."}, roles={"noble","urchin"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={city=2} },
    },
    -- group discussions (many voices, rotating cast of 4-6)
    groups = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 5: tagged groups (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Festival games are on. What's each of you entering this %event%?", "The %fish%-catching contest. Haven't held a rod since boyhood, but the purse of %currency% is calling.", "The strongman lift. A tauron's the favorite, but I've been hauling %tradegood% on the docks all %season% — I fancy my odds.", "The footrace, the long one, out the gate and back. I run from my problems daily. Might as well get a medal for it.", "Nothing. I'm here for the %food% and the watching. Someone has to cheer, and someone has to lose gracefully — I'll do neither athletically.", "...the wisest entry of all is no entry and a full plate.", "Spoken like a true spectator. To the brave fools competing, and the wise fools eating.", "To both kinds of fool! Now budge up, the lifting's starting and I've %gold% riding on the tauron."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Bandits, beasts, and bad %weather% — what's the worst the %route% ever threw at you?", "A 'tax collector' crew that robbed me politely and handed me a receipt. I keep it. It's the strangest thing I own.", "%monster% out of the treeline at dusk. Lost a wagon of %tradegood% and very nearly more. Don't travel that stretch after dark.", "A flood that washed the bridge clean away. Stranded a %season%'s worth of us on the wrong bank, all sharing one inn and one nerve.", "...honestly? The loneliness. Three days without a soul. The bandits at least were COMPANY.", "There's the road truth nobody admits. The danger you can fight. The empty miles just wear you down.", "That's why we travel in company. Split the toll, share the watch, fill the silence. The %route%'s only cruel to the solitary.", "Then here's to company on the road. May your caravan be loud, your watch be doubled, and your receipts be few."}, roles={"adventurer","vendor"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"Animals know things we don't. Anyone's %companion% ever save them?", "Mine found the safe ford across the %zone% river when I'd have drowned us crossing where it looked calm.", "My old hound growled the whole night before the %monster% came. I didn't listen the first time. I listen now.", "A barn cat woke the whole household before the fire took hold. We lost the barn. We'd have lost everything.", "...my %companion% just refuses to enter the old mill. Won't say why. So I don't either. Some warnings you take on faith.", "We trust these beasts with our lives and repay them with scraps and a warm corner. Cheap at the price.", "Cheaper still when you count the lives they've pulled us out of. Feed yours first tonight, every one of you.", "To the %companion%s, then. Wiser than their masters and a great deal more loyal. May we deserve them someday."}, roles={"farmer","adventurer"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={rural=2, wilderness=1} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged groups (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Maddest coin you each ever earned — confession round, go.", "Guided a noble's hunt through %zone%. They shot at every %critter% and bagged nothing but my last nerve. Paid in %gold%, though.", "Carried a sealed crate down the %route% and asked no questions. Slept worse than I've ever slept. Spent it faster than I've ever spent.", "Posed as a %class% at a noble's ball to make the host look connected. Ate like a king, lied like a rug, left before the unmasking.", "Mucked out a stable of war-%mount%s after a campaign. No glory in it. But honest, and the beasts were better company than the nobles.", "...there's a moral in here and it's that the cleanest coin smells the worst, isn't it.", "Or that the dirtiest coin sleeps the worst. Either way — to the strange things we've done to eat.", "To eating. The realm's oldest and most persuasive argument. Drinks while we've still got the maddest %gold% in our purses."}, roles={"adventurer","citizen"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Who keeps the realm running, REALLY? Not the King. Settle it.", "The farmers. Starve the %city% one %season% and watch how fast the crowns and banners stop mattering.", "The smiths. Every blade, plough, nail, and hinge. Stop the forges and the whole realm seizes up like a rusted hinge itself.", "The innkeepers. Every soldier, merchant, and messenger needs a warm bed and a hot %food% or they don't make the next day.", "The urchins and the carters and the dockhands. The unseen ones. Pull us out and your grand realm is just nobles shouting in empty halls.", "...so it's all of us, then. The whole unsung scaffolding.", "Aye. The King wears the crown. WE hold up the floor he stands on.", "Then to the floor-holders. Long may we grumble, and longer may we hold. Pass the %drink% down the line."}, roles={"farmer","craftsman","innkeeper"}, moods={"gruff","wry"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Tell the fire the bravest thing you ever saw a COWARD do.", "A man who shook like a leaf the whole march still stood his ground when the line broke. Fear didn't stop him. It just rode along.", "A girl too scared to speak walked into a burning house for a %critter% that wasn't even hers. Came out singed and grinning.", "An old drunkard everyone wrote off carried two wounded off the %zone% field on a bad leg, then went straight back for a third.", "...my own brother. Terrified of everything. Volunteered for the watch the night the %monster% came, so a braver man could sleep.", "Brave's a strange word, isn't it. Turns out it's just being afraid and doing the thing regardless.", "The fearless ones were never brave. They just didn't understand the stakes. Give me a frightened soul who acts anyway.", "To the frightened, then. The truly brave. May we all be scared enough to know what courage costs, and do it anyhow."}, roles={"soldier","citizen"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={battlefield=1, city=1} },
      { chain={"What's the best gossip running the %city% right now? Don't hold back.", "The %shop% sold to a goblin who's 'modernizing.' Translation: a queue, a surcharge, and the soul ripped right out of it.", "A noble's %gem% went missing and turned up round an urchin's neck, and not a SOUL is willing to say how.", "The two warriors who duel outside the bank every dawn? Seen sharing a %drink% at dusk. Sworn enemies, my foot.", "The festival ball's guest list 'leaked,' and half the snubbed nobles are furious, and the catering staff are LOVING it.", "...we are terrible, gossiping people and I have never enjoyed anything more.", "It's not cruelty if it's true and we're smiling. It's just the %city% knowing itself.", "To the %city% knowing itself, then. Same fountain, same hour tomorrow. Bring fresh dirt."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged groups (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Veterans' corner, then — what title did each of you earn, and was it worth the cost?", "'%title%', out of %zone%. Cost me three friends and a finger. Worth? Ask the finger.", "%pvptitle%. Bled a whole %season% in the %bg% for it. Now it's just a word the young ones don't recognize.", "None. I held a supply line, fed an army, never once swung at a soul. No title for that. There never is.", "...and yet your line is why the rest of us LIVED to earn ours. The realm gives titles to the loud and owes its life to the quiet.", "Drink up, supply-man. You'll have no title from the King, but you've got one from us: the man who kept us breathing.", "...that's a finer title than mine. Truly.", "To the quiet ones, then. The realm forgets them. This fire never will."}, roles={"soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={city=1, battlefield=1} },
      { chain={"Settle it: greatest %mount% you've each ridden or seen?", "A storm-grey courser won off a %race% gambler in %city%. Fast as a cut rope and twice as mean.", "A %companion%-bred warhound the size of a pony. Carried my wounded brother off the %zone% field when no horse would.", "Saw a %class% ride something that wasn't natural at ALL through the gates once. Glowed. Didn't touch the ground. Still dream of it.", "Mine's a stubborn old mule that's never once thrown me. You can keep your glory-beasts. Loyalty outlasts speed.", "...the mule lover has a point none of us want to admit.", "The mule always gets you home. The glory-beast gets you a song and a grave.", "To the mules, then. And to the fools like me who'll still pick the glory-beast every time."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"The %event%'s on. What's everyone's favorite part of it, honestly?", "The %food%. I save my coin all %season% just to gorge for one glorious %timeofday%.", "The dancing. My knees curse me and I do that silly %emote% anyway. Once a year I'm young again.", "The lanterns. The whole %city% glowing soft, every window lit. I cry a little. I'm not ashamed.", "The quiet after. When the crowds thin and it's just the embers and the folk you love still lingering.", "...trust you to love the END of the party best.", "The end's when you find out who stayed. That's the part worth keeping.", "To the ones who stay till the embers, then. The %food%, the dance, the lanterns — and the lingering."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Around the war-camp fire — what gets each of you through the night before?", "I name them. Every soul I'm fighting to get home to. Out loud, soft, like a prayer. Keeps my feet pointed forward.", "I sharpen the blade till the edge could split %weather%. Busy hands don't shake.", "I write the letter home. The one I pray they never need to read. Then I tuck it away and hope.", "...I just listen to you lot. The naming, the sharpening, the writing. It's the only lullaby out here worth a damn.", "We're a sorry choir, aren't we. A namer, a sharpener, a letter-writer, and a man who can't sleep.", "Sorry choir or no, we sing each other through. That's the whole of soldiering nobody tells the recruits.", "Then sing on. Dawn comes for us all the same. Let's meet it at this fire, together, every one we can."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","brave"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"Dockside, then — worst thing the sea ever asked of you?", "To leave a man behind. The boat was swamping. One more aboard and we all drown. I still see his face on the swell.", "To wait. Three days becalmed, water gone, watching the horizon refuse to give us a breath of wind.", "To bury my own father to her. He went out in a squall when I was a boy. She never gave him back.", "...the sea takes, and takes, and we keep rowing out to her anyway. Why?", "Because she gives, too. A %fish% to feed the village. A horizon worth the ache. A home no land could match.", "Aye. She's cruel and she's kin, all at once. Light a lantern at the %event% and let it drift. That's the only answer there is.", "To the sea, then. May she be kind, and when she's not, may she be quick. Row on, lads."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={coast=3} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged groups (shared)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Round the fire — what's the finest %profession% there is, honestly?", "Smithing. Everything else needs a blade or a plough, and who do you think makes those?", "Cooking. Your fine blade's no use to a starving man. I keep the realm on its feet.", "Herbalism. I've walked %zone% to %zone% and never once gone hungry or unhealed. The land provides.", "Fishing. Quietest trade, oldest trade, and the only one that's also a rest.", "...you're all wrong, it's whichever one's fed YOU this %season%.", "Spoken like a man with no trade at all.", "Spoken like a man who buys from all of you and toasts the lot. To honest work, whatever its shape."}, roles={"craftsman","farmer","sailor"}, moods={"boastful","warm"}, areas={rural=2, city=1} },
      { chain={"The %season% turned hard this year. How's everyone faring with the %weather%?", "Lost half my late %herb% crop to the frost. The other half I'm guarding like a dragon's hoard.", "Roads to %zone% are mud to the axle. No caravan's getting through till it dries.", "We've %food% laid by and a tight roof. Could be worse. Was worse, the year the river came up.", "...the year the river came up. Don't. I still dream of bailing.", "Then let's not speak it into being. Tight roofs, full cellars, and good neighbors. That's how a hard %season% gets survived.", "Aye. And a fire like this one. Shuffle up, there's room. No soul freezes while the rest of us are warm."}, roles={"farmer","citizen"}, moods={"weary","kindly"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Best tale the bards tell these days — go.", "The ballad of %tale%. Gets the whole tavern weeping by the third verse, every time.", "Anything with %boss% in it. Half lies, all thunder. The children act it out in the square for a %season% after.", "The quiet ones. The tale of an unnamed %class% who saved a village and asked no song. Those are the true ones.", "...the true ones never make good ballads, though. No glory in 'and then they went quietly home.'", "Maybe that's the point. The best deeds outlive the loudest songs.", "Then here's to the unsung %class%es, and to the bards who at least TRY to remember them.", "To the bards. Lying beautifully in service of the truth since the first fire was lit."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"What small thing got you through the worst %season% of your life?", "A %companion% that wouldn't leave my side. Some nights its breathing was the only proof the world hadn't ended.", "A neighbor who left %food% on my step and never once knocked to be thanked.", "The %event%. I didn't want to go. They dragged me. I danced. I remembered I was alive.", "A single %toy% my lost boy carved. I hold it some nights. It holds me back, somehow.", "...we've all been carried by something small, haven't we.", "That's the secret nobody tells you. It's never the grand things that save you. It's the %food% on the step.", "To the small things, then. The %companion%, the neighbor, the dance, the carving. The whole quiet scaffolding of a life."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged groups (shared / all factions)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Settle it round the fire: best %food% in all of %city%?", "The meat pies off the cart by the bank. Don't ask what's in them. The not-asking is the secret.", "The %fish% stew down at the docks. Tastes of salt and home.", "Festival %food% during the %event%. Doesn't count year-round, but Light, when it's on...", "You're all wrong. Whatever the innkeeper sets in front of me after a long %route%. Hunger's the finest cook there is.", "...that's annoyingly wise for a man with gravy in his beard.", "Wisdom and gravy aren't enemies, friend. Pass the bread."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","wry"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Who's actually seen %rare% with their own eyes? No tavern tales.", "Once. In %zone%, in the %weather%, far off. Then it was gone. Half think I dreamed it.", "I tracked it a whole %season%. Found droppings, prints, a scared %critter% or two. Never the beast.", "My uncle swore he killed it. My uncle also swore he married a moon goddess.", "...the moon goddess I'd believe before the %rare%, honestly.", "That's the thing about %rare%. The proof is always one ridge further on.", "To the one ridge further on. May we never quite reach it. Keeps a man walking."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={wilderness=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Hardest thing you ever did in your %profession%, then?", "Forged a blade in one night for a soldier marching at dawn. He came back to thank me. Not all of them do.", "Hauled %tradegood% over the %zone% pass in a %weather% that killed two of the mules.", "Kept a tavern open the %season% the river flooded. Bailed all night, poured all day. Never closed once.", "Brought a %season%'s harvest in alone after the fever took my whole household. Just me and the scythe and the dark.", "...we don't talk enough about what the quiet trades cost, do we.", "No. We don't. Drinks on me. To the work nobody sings about.", "To the work nobody sings about."}, roles={"craftsman","farmer","innkeeper"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={rural=2, city=1} },
      { chain={"Quick — if a %class% handed you %gold% right now, what's the first thing you'd buy?", "A %mount%. Ride into %city% on a fine one and you never pay for a drink again.", "A %toy% for each of my children. They've gone without long enough.", "Passage on the next ship out of port. I've stared at the same %zone% horizon my whole life.", "Nothing. I'd bury it under the hearth and sleep better than I have in a %season%.", "...bury it? You'd waste a fortune on PEACE OF MIND?", "Peace of mind's the one thing none of you listed and the only thing worth the gold. Mark me on that.", "...hate that he's right. Pass the %drink%."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={city=2, coast=1} },
      { chain={"What's the worst the %weather% ever did to you all?", "Lightning split the old oak in my field and not one beast in the barn would settle for a %season% after.", "Snow shut the %route% so long we ate the seed grain. Hungry spring, that one.", "Squall off the cape took a whole skiff. We pulled two of the four lads out. I still hear the other two.", "...the calm's worse than any of it. The dead, glassy calm that goes on for days at sea.", "Aye. The storm at least lets you fight back. The calm just sits on your chest and waits.", "Light, what a cheerful fire this turned out to be. Somebody tell a lie about a %fish% they caught.", "Right — so it was the size of a longboat, see, and it WINKED at me..."}, roles={"farmer","sailor"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={coast=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Round the table: strangest thing you've sold or been sold in this %city%?", "A goblin sold me a map to buried treasure. The treasure was another map. I keep it. It's funny.", "I sold a noble a 'lucky %gem%.' It's a river pebble. He's won three duels since and swears by it.", "Bought a charm against %monster% attacks. We've no %monster% for fifty leagues. Sleep great, though.", "Sold a %toy% that's meant to whistle. It screams instead. Sold out by noon. The children adore it.", "...this whole market runs on lies we've agreed to enjoy, doesn't it.", "Always has. The honest stalls starve. The fun ones feast. Welcome to commerce, friend."}, roles={"vendor","citizen"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={city=3} },
      { chain={"They're calling up fighters for %zone% again. Who's going?", "My eldest signed this morning. Couldn't look at me when he did it.", "I went last %season%. I'd not send another soul, but I'll not stop one either. It's theirs to choose.", "The recruiters dress it up in banners and %drink%. Underneath it's the same cold ground it always was.", "...and yet someone has to stand on that ground, or there's no %city% left to come home to.", "That's the trap of it, isn't it. The cause is real even when the men selling it aren't.", "Then we send them off proud and we keep their stools warm. That's all the honesty we get to give.", "Their stools, and a candle each %timeofday% till they're back. Aye. To them."}, roles={"soldier","citizen"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Best inn on the whole %route%, then. Defend your answer.", "%shop%, no contest. The innkeeper remembers your name, your order, and your troubles.", "The one at the crossroads. Lumpy beds, but the %drink% flows till dawn and nobody asks your business.", "Any inn with a fire and a locked door after a %weather% like last night's. I've grown unfussy.", "...you've all forgotten the one that matters: the one closest when your legs give out.", "Ha! The nearest inn is always the finest inn. There's a road-truth for you.", "To the nearest inn. May it always have one room left and a pot still warm."}, roles={"adventurer","innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={road=3} },
      { chain={"What's the kindest thing a stranger ever did for you?", "A %class% paid my whole tavern tab and slipped out before I could thank them. Still don't know the face.", "A vendor gave my hungry boy a %food% 'for the road' and waved off the coin. Small thing. I never forgot.", "Got pulled from the surf off the coast by a sailor I'd never met. He just shrugged and rowed on.", "An old %race% woman shared her fire and her %drink% with me in a %weather% that would've killed me. Said nothing. Just made room.", "...the world's crueler in the telling than it is in the living, isn't it.", "Aye. For every villain in the tales there's ten strangers who just quietly made room.", "Then here's to the room-makers. The unsung lot. May we all be one when it counts."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Tell me true — does the war ever actually touch a quiet life like ours?", "Touched mine. Took a brother to %zone% and sent back a folded cloak.", "It's in the price of %tradegood% at every stall. We pay for it whether we march or not.", "It's in the empty stools and the young faces gone old. You don't need a blade to feel a war.", "...and yet the bread still bakes, the %season% still turns, the children still laugh in the square.", "That's not the war failing to touch us. That's us refusing to let it have everything.", "Refusing to let it have everything. Write that over the gate. To the small, stubborn, ordinary life.", "To the small life. Hardest thing in the world to keep, and worth every fight."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={city=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Settle it for me: which capital is the finest in all Azeroth?", "Ironforge. Warm stone, endless ale, and the Great Forge never goes cold.", "Stormwind. Spires like they're carved from morning light. Nothing finer.", "Darnassus, easily. You've clearly never lost an hour to moonlight on the ponds.", "Thunder Bluff. Open sky, clean wind, and not a single auctioneer screaming in your ear.", "Silvermoon. Ten thousand years of refinement, and it shows in every gilded arch.", "Undercity, if you've the stomach. Grim, yes, but the Forsaken made a home out of grief.", "You're all wrong. Booty Bay. No rules, great fishing, and the ale's only mostly poisoned.", "...of course the goblin lover says Booty Bay.", "It has a SUNSET over the SEA. What's your spire got? Pigeons.", "Every one of you is loyal to wherever your hearthstone's set. Admit it.", "Fair. Home's home. Mine just happens to be the prettiest."}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Anyone else feel the cities are quieter since the call-up north?", "Half the regulars from my tavern shipped to Icecrown. Place feels hollow.", "The recruiting officers are at every gate. Argent Crusade, mostly.", "My brother signed on. Said someone has to. I couldn't argue.", "Noble cause. Terrible odds. The Scourge doesn't tire and doesn't grieve.", "They say Fordring himself is leading the push. If anyone can, it's him.", "I just hope the ones who go come back. Most of them. Some of them.", "Light keep them. Earth Mother hold them. Whatever you pray to, pray it loud.", "...and keep their stools warm at the tavern. They'll want them back.", "That's the most hopeful thing anyone's said all week. I'll drink to it."}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"What's the strangest thing you've seen in a city square?", "A goblin auctioning 'genuine dragon eggs.' They were painted gourds. He made forty gold.", "A fully armored knight playing hopscotch on a chalk grid. Very seriously. On his way to war.", "Two bards turned a song into a duel. The crowd took sides. Beautiful chaos.", "A street preacher's been shouting about the end times for a week. The end times are taking their time.", "A stray dog adopted the entire city guard. They take turns feeding it. It eats better than I do.", "An apprentice mage misfired a portal and dropped straight into the sewers. We've all been there.", "A noble's carriage stuck in the market crowd, so he had to walk like the rest of us. The street rejoiced.", "A tauren gently lifting a lost gnome onto his shoulder so the little one could find his friends. Made my year.", "...this city is a circus with a war on the side, and I love every cobblestone of it.", "Couldn't have said it better. Same time tomorrow at the fountain?"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Settle a bar bet for us: hardest %boss% ever put down?", "%boss%, no contest. We threw ourselves at it for a whole %season%.", "Soft. Try it at %difficulty% with a pickup group and %consumable% running low.", "You're both wrong. The hard part was the trash before %boss%, not the boss.", "The hard part is always the %class% who stands in the fire. Every group has one.", "...we ARE the %class% who stands in the fire, aren't we.", "To standing in the fire. May we one day learn to step out of it.", "Drinks at %shop%. We've earned the wipe stories."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful","wry"} },
      { chain={"If you could own one thing in all Azeroth, what'd it be?", "%item%. I'd never set it down, not even to sleep.", "%mount%. Ride into %city% on that and you never pay for a drink again.", "Pfft. The title '%pvptitle%'. You can't buy what you bleed for.", "%gold% in the bank and a quiet cottage in %zone%. That's the dream.", "Exalted with every %rep% there is. Just to say I did it.", "...all of you chasing legends, and here's me just wanting a stall that sells out by %timeofday%.", "Honestly? That's the wisest answer at this table.", "To small dreams, then. They're the only ones that come true."}, moods={"dreamy","wry"} },
      { chain={"What's the worst luck you've had on a drop?", "Ran %instance% every week for a %season% and %boss% never once gave up %item%.", "Lost %item% to a %class% on a single dice roll. Off by one number.", "Sold a green for %gold%, then watched it resell for ten times that an hour later.", "Tracked %rare% across half of %zone%, dismounted to loot, and a passing %class% sniped it.", "...we are a table of the unluckiest souls in %city%, aren't we.", "And yet here we all are, still rolling. Still hoping.", "That's adventuring, friend. The Light gives, the dice take."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"bitter","weary"} },
      -- == Coast & docks groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Weather's turning. What's the worst you've all seen out on the water?", "A wall of black cloud off the cape that swallowed the sun whole. We rowed blind for an hour.", "Waterspout. Picked a skiff clean off the swell and set it down a hundred yards on, dry as you like.", "The calm. The dead, glassy calm that goes on for days till you'd sell your soul for a breeze.", "...the calm. Aye. That's the one that breaks men. The storm at least lets you fight back.", "I've buried friends to all of it. And still I'd not trade the deck for dry land.", "Spoken like every fool who's ever loved the sea. Drinks to the lot of us, then.", "To the sea. May she be kind, and when she's not, may she be quick."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Who runs this port, really? Not the harbormaster, I'll wager.", "The tide runs this port. Everything else just argues over the leavings.", "The goblins run it. Follow the coin, it always ends in a green pocket.", "The dockworkers run it. Stop hauling for one day and watch your great merchants weep.", "Pretty thought, but we'd starve before they would. Coin keeps longer than bread.", "...and there it is. We could own this harbor and we'll die haggling over a copper.", "Then haggle loud and haul proud, friend. It's the only kingdom we'll ever have."}, roles={"sailor","vendor"}, moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={coast=3} },
      { chain={"Festival of lanterns on the water tonight. You all coming down to the docks?", "Every year. Float a lantern for someone the sea took. Never miss it.", "I float one for my father. Went out in a squall when I was a boy and the water kept him.", "...mine's for the whole crew of the Gull. Good lads. Bad weather.", "It's the one night this rough port goes quiet and gentle. Like the sea's listening.", "Maybe she is. Light your wick, say your name, let it drift. That's the whole of grace, that is.", "Then let's go down together. Nobody should light a lantern alone."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={coast=3} },
      -- == Rural & harvest groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Harvest's nearly in. How'd your fields fare this %season%?", "Better than feared. The frost held off the one week it mattered.", "Mine drowned. Three weeks of %weather% turned the low field to a swamp.", "Then take from mine. I've more grain than barn this year, and a flooded neighbor's no neighbor at all.", "...I can't take charity, you know that.", "It's not charity, it's sense. Lean year for you's a lean market for me. We rise together out here or not at all.", "...then I'll repay you in lambs come spring, and not a word against it.", "Done. That's how a village outlasts a bad sky. Now somebody fetch the cider."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"kindly","weary"}, areas={rural=3} },
      { chain={"Wolves are bold this year. Anyone else losing stock?", "Two lambs and a calf. I've started bringing the dogs in close after dusk.", "It's the hard winter up in the hills driving them down. Hungry beasts, desperate beasts.", "I say we set a common watch. Take turns, share the lanterns, ring the low pastures.", "Brave talk from the man with the smallest flock.", "Brave talk from the man who'll be glad of my watch when it's his turn to sleep. Are you in or not?", "...aye. I'm in. Light help me, a village militia against wolves. The bards'll never sing it.", "Let them not. We keep our lambs. That's song enough."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={rural=3, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"They're saying a tax collector's riding the valley road this week.", "Let him ride. He'll find empty cellars and emptier purses, same as last year.", "Hide the good grain. The seed stock especially — they took my neighbor's and he near starved.", "That's the King's grain by law, you know. Talk like that gets a man's barn burned.", "The King's a long way off and the winter's right here. I'll feed my children before his ledger.", "...quietly, then. We say nothing, we know nothing, and the cellar door stays shut.", "Agreed. A village keeps its own counsel. Now drink up before someone mistakes us for honest men."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","nervous"}, areas={rural=3} },
      -- == Battlefield & war-camp groups (expansion, faction-neutral) ==
      { chain={"Eve of the assault. What's everyone do the night before?", "Sharpen the blade. Then sharpen it again. Keeps the hands from shaking.", "Write the letter home. The one you hope they never have to read.", "...I just sit with the fire and try to remember every face I'm fighting to get back to.", "I pray. Not for victory. Just that I don't run when the line breaks.", "You won't run. None of us will. We'll be too busy holding the man beside us up.", "That's the truth of it, isn't it. Nobody fights for the cause at dawn. You fight for the lot at this fire.", "Then to this fire, and the lot of us. May we all be sat round it again tomorrow night.", "...most of us. Let's not lie to each other on the last quiet hour. But to the fire, aye."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","brave"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      { chain={"What's the worst part of soldiering? Not the battles — the rest of it.", "The waiting. Battle's an hour; the waiting's a month, and it eats you slower.", "The food. I'd charge the enemy line for a hot meal that wasn't grey.", "The boots never drying. Trench foot's killed more of us than any blade.", "...the silence after. When the field's quiet and you start counting who's not at the fire.", "Aye. That's the one nobody warns the new recruits about. The arithmetic after.", "Cheerful lot tonight. Somebody tell a lie about a girl back home, quick, before we all weep.", "Right — so there I was, the most beautiful barmaid in three provinces, and she only had eyes for me...", "...there it is. Liar. Go on, though. We need the liars more than the priests out here."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={battlefield=3} },
      -- == Wilderness & road groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Round the fire, then — what's the wildest thing you've met out in the deep wilds?", "A stag white as snow that stood and watched me a full minute, then was just... gone. No sound.", "%rare%, if you'll believe it. Saw it once, never again. Half think I dreamed it.", "A whole ruined keep swallowed by the forest, doors still hung, table still set. No bones. Just left.", "...I don't camp near ruins. Ever. You can keep your set tables, friend.", "Coward.", "Wise coward. There's a difference, and the difference is still breathing.", "Fair. To the wise cowards, then — they outlive the brave ones and inherit the good stories."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","cowardly"}, areas={wilderness=3} },
      { chain={"Caravan's stopped for the night. Anyone know why we took the long road, not the pass?", "Bandits in the pass. Three caravans gone this %season%. The master's no fool.", "I heard it's worse than bandits. Something came down out of the high country.", "%monster%, they're saying. Whole hunting parties not coming back.", "...and we're sleeping in the open because of this? I'd sooner risk the bandits.", "Bandits you can pay. The other thing you can only run from, and it runs faster.", "So we keep the fires high, the watch doubled, and our mouths shut about it near the children.", "Aye. Loud fire, quiet talk, sharp eyes. We'll see %city% yet. Now who's got the first watch?"}, roles={"adventurer","soldier"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={road=2, wilderness=2} },
    },
  },

  alliance = {
    -- standalone one-liners (single speaker)
    lines = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged one-liners (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { "Westfall's farms stand empty and the Defias walk the roads bold as brass. Stormwind looks north to %zone% and starves its own back door. It breaks the heart.", roles={"farmer","citizen"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { "Redridge militia hold that border against %monster% raids with a handful of stout souls and a mountain of stubbornness. Somebody from the %city% ought to help.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={rural=2, wilderness=1} },
      { "A gnome 'optimized' my %item% and now it hums the Stormwind anthem and won't stop. Half genius, half hazard, all Tinker Town. A terrible, patriotic mistake.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Cathedral's taken in Westfall refugees, whole families on the steps, the Bishop turning none away. We'll MAKE room. That's the Alliance, or it's just a banner.", roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"kindly","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Every Brewfest I meet the dwarf who dragged me from a drift in %zone% by my collar. Same Ironforge corner, same silence, same bond. Some things you forge once.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Stormwind nobles are throwing a masque for the %event% and hired half the Trade District to cater it. A serving tray's the best disguise in the %city%.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A draenei sat with a frightened Westfall child on the Cathedral steps and just... hummed, soft, in her own tongue, till the little one slept. The Light has no language.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Ironforge Senate's been arguing the %tradegood% tariffs for three days straight. The dwarves can turn a coin debate into an epic saga. I've started bringing %food%.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged one-liners (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { "Earned the title '%title%' under the King's banner in %zone%. The Cathedral remembers my friends who didn't. I just remember to light the candle.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A draenei loosed a %spell% over the Stormwind harbor at dusk to bless the fleet for %zone%. The whole sky went gold. Even the dockhands stopped to stare.", roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Won a noble's %mount% at cards in the Blue Recluse. He bet more pride than he could cover. I ride to the docks in style and he walks. Stormwind justice.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Explorers' League sailed for %zone% after %item% again. Half come back, half of those come back changed. Light watch over the daft, brave dwarves.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A worgen knight holds the back of the Cathedral still as stone, mastering the beast where all can see. The Gilneans fight a war the rest of us never will.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Stormwind gryphons grounded by %weather% off the harbor. So the whole Alliance crowds the tram, and a gnome explains the engine to us mile by mile.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Selling Elwynn apples to every soldier marching to %zone%, first one free. A lad's last taste of home is worth more than the copper I'd make on it.", roles={"vendor","farmer"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "A dwarf, a gnome, and a night elf settled an old argument with a drinking contest in the Pig and Whistle. The night elf won. Nobody saw THAT coming.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged one-liners (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { "SI:7 had the Old Town rooftops crawling last night. Whatever they're hunting, the watch was told to look the other way and we all obliged.", roles={"guard","citizen"}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A gnome in Tinker Town swears their new %toy% runs on 'controlled' explosions. The word 'controlled' is doing a great deal of brave work there.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Watched the Stormwind Guard drill in the courtyard at dawn. Six peoples in one column, stepping as one. Say what you like — it's a fine sight.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"boastful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Cathedral took in a sick %race% child off the streets, no questions, no coin. That's the Light I signed on for. Not the sermons. That.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"kindly","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Dwarven District forge took a commission from a Darnassus Sentinel — elven steel, dwarven fire. The result's bound for %zone% and it's beautiful.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"boastful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A worgen kept their composure through the whole crowded Trade District, claws folded, breath even. The Gilneans fight a quiet war we never see.", moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Argent recruiters at the Stormwind gate ask for the brave, not the strong. Sent my nephew off to %zone% with that ringing in his ears.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Lost an afternoon in the Stormwind Library. A historian there can tell you the whole tale of %zone% and forget you exist by the second hour. Bliss.", roles={"mage","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The draenei vindicator blessed the new recruits' %item% before the march. Even the dwarves went quiet for it. The Light doesn't ask your race.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Ironforge gryphon master grounded the flights — %weather% off Dun Morogh too rough. So the tram it is, with half the Alliance and all their luggage.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Selling Elwynn apples and Westfall melons at the Stormwind gate — taste of the homeland for any soldier shipping to %zone%, first one's free.", roles={"vendor","farmer"}, moods={"kindly","cheerful"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "A night elf and a draenei argued ten thousand years of history versus the stars themselves over one %drink%. Loveliest argument I ever eavesdropped.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The King's tax on %tradegood% went up to fund the %zone% campaign. We grumble, we pay, we send our sons after the coin. That's the bargain.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Stormwind orphanage matron walked a line of children past the Cathedral, each clutching a %toy%. The whole square stepped aside and softened. Even the guards.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged one-liners (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      -- Stormwind life
      { "Trade District auctioneers are in fine voice this morning. One of them sold a %item% for more %gold% than my house is worth.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Cathedral bells rang for a fallen %class% out of %zone%. The whole of Stormwind went still for the length of them.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Old Town's rogues changed shift with the night watch again. Smoothest handover in the city, and neither side admits it.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Canal District smells of fresh bread and wet stone after the rain. I'd not trade a Stormwind morning for all the %gold% in Booty Bay.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A gnome set up an 'automatic %toy% dispenser' by the fountain. It dispensed, then exploded, then dispensed again. The children are thrilled.", moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The King's holding court in Stormwind Keep. Half the city turned out, and I just want to deliver my %tradegood% to the kitchens.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Mage Quarter portals to %zone% are down AGAIN. The line's out past the pond and a draenei's started a prayer circle to pass the time.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Ironforge & the dwarves
      { "The Great Forge never goes cold, and neither does a dwarf's welcome. Warm stone, warm ale, warm hearts — Ironforge has the lot.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Explorers' League just hauled a crate of %item% in from a dig in %zone%. Half of it's priceless. Half of it's rubble. They can't tell which yet.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "First snow in Dun Morogh and all of Ironforge smells of mulled %drink% and hot %ore%. Best %season% under the mountain.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A dwarf challenged me to drink him under the table. I'm a draenei. I weigh as much as his whole clan. He won anyway.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The tram to Stormwind broke down mid-tunnel again. Spent an hour underground with a gnome explaining the engineering. I understood none of it. Lovely fellow.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Darnassus, night elves, Teldrassil
      { "Sat by the Darnassus moonwell till the moonlight on the water stole a whole %timeofday% from me. Worth every minute.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Sentinel told me the leaves of Teldrassil never truly stop whispering. After a %season% in this city, I've started to hear them too.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"} },
      { "The owls of Darnassus hooted all night before the call-up. Omen or birds, the Sentinels marched at dawn regardless.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","nervous"} },
      { "Autumn leaves drifting off Teldrassil into the ponds. The druids say the tree dreams in %season%s. I believe them.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A night elf druid turned into a %critter% mid-conversation, wandered off, and came back an hour later as herself with no explanation. I love this city.", moods={"wry","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Exodar & draenei
      { "The crystals of the Exodar sing when the light hits them right. The draenei call it home now, and you can hear why.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Exodar still tilts where it crashed. An anchorite told me you get your sea legs eventually. I've been here a %season% and I still spill my %drink%.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "An anchorite blessed my %companion% on the Exodar steps for free. The dog's been suspiciously well-behaved since. Coincidence, surely.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Worgen & Gilneas
      { "A Gilnean told me of the home they lost behind the wall. Some nights you can hear the old country in how careful they are with everything.", moods={"solemn","kindly"} },
      { "The Gilneans keep their manners sharp as their claws. Bumped one in the market and got the most elegant apology of my life. From me. To him. Somehow.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Cross-Alliance unity & war
      { "Human, dwarf, gnome, elf, draenei, worgen — six peoples, one banner, and we STILL can't agree where to eat after the muster.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Word from %zone%: the Alliance line held another %timeofday%. Light keep our soldiers, and keep the recruiters honest about the odds.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={battlefield=1, city=1} },
      { "Stormwind recruiters at the gate again, promising glory in %zone%. I went last call-up. Glory's a word for folk who stayed home.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Stormwind Guard stopped a brawl between a dwarf and a night elf over whose ancestors were older. Both ancestors lost. The tavern won.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Vendors, craftsmen, daily Alliance trade
      { "Selling fresh-cut tulips from the Stormwind gardens — brighten any keep, three silver a bunch, and a free one for any %class% off to %zone%.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"cheerful","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Ironforge smiths want my %ore% at half what the gnomes offer. I'll sell to the gnomes and let the dwarves grumble. Old rivalry, good business.", roles={"vendor","craftsman"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Spent the morning enchanting a paladin's %item% with %enchant% before they shipped to %zone%. May it hold. May they hold.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Stormwind tailor stitched me a cloak so fine the nobles nod at me now. I'm a fishmonger. The cloak is doing heroic work.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Cathedral Square is quiet this morning. The Bishop's sermon must have run long again.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Anyone else stop to watch the Stormwind guards change shift at the Trade District gates? Best free show in the city.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The smell of fresh bread from the Trade District bakery is the only buff I need today.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Pickpockets in Old Town again. Keep a hand on your coin purse near the Slaughtered Lamb crowd, friends.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Sitting by the Stormwind canals watching the boats. Days like this make the wars feel far away.", moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Mage Quarter portals are down again. Whoever's on duty, the line is out to the fountain.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      "Just adopted a cat from the Cathedral district. Named it %npc%. It judges everyone.",
      { "Selling fresh-cut tulips from the Stormwind gardens! Brighten your keep, three silver a bunch.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A fine day for a stroll through the Dwarven District. The forges are warm and the ale is warmer.", moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Lost in the tram tunnels between Ironforge and Stormwind. Send a map. And a snack.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "They keep the Great Forge burning so bright you forget it's snowing in Dun Morogh.", roles={"craftsman"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Sat by the Darnassus ponds and lost an hour to the moonlight on the water. No regrets.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Sentinel told me the leaves of Teldrassil never truly stop whispering. I believe her.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"} },
      "The owls of Darnassus hooted all night. Either an omen or they're just owls. Probably owls.",
      { "The crystals of the Exodar sing when the light hits them right. The draenei call it home now.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      "The Exodar still tilts a little where it crashed. They say you get your sea legs eventually.",
      { "Anchorites at the Exodar bless travelers for free. Took the blessing, felt great, fell off a ramp anyway.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Made the full tour today: Stormwind to Ironforge by tram, Ironforge to Darnassus by boat. My feet are retired.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"} },
      { "A new adventurer asked me how to get to Stormwind from the night elf lands. Friend, clear your afternoon.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"} },
      "First snow in Dun Morogh and the whole of Ironforge smells like mulled cider. Best time of year.",
      { "Stormwind in spring, the gardens in full bloom. Even the guards crack a smile.", moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Autumn leaves drifting down off Teldrassil into the Darnassus ponds. Bittersweet and beautiful.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Mage Quarter at night is all blue light and quiet humming. Easy to forget there's a war on.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Old Town never really sleeps. The rogues just change shifts with the night watch.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Trade District at high noon is pure chaos. Auctioneers, beggars, nobles, and me, hopelessly lost.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Cathedral District is the only quiet corner of Stormwind. I go there just to hear myself think.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Two elves slow-dancing by the Darnassus moonwell while a bard played. The whole square went quiet.", moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      "An anchorite blessed my journey and meant it. You can tell when someone means it.",
      { "Anyone up for a scavenger hunt in Stormwind? First clue is 'Where the King's Shadow Lies.'", moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Forming a casual band at the Stormwind gates, bound for %instance%. No pressure, just good company.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Looking for a few brave souls at the Ironforge gates for a run to %instance%. Beards optional.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Standing at the Darnassus portal forever. Is ANYONE going to %zone% today?", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Stormwind fountain is NOT a wishing well, a swimming pool, OR a bath, and yet here we all are.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Stormwind's spires catch the morning light like they're made of it. Pride of the Alliance, and rightly so.", moods={"boastful","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Ironforge has stood since before the stories started. Let the surface squabble; the mountain endures.", moods={"solemn","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Found a bookshop tucked behind the Mage Quarter. Smells of dust and old magic. I may never leave.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Eyes open near Old Town tonight. Word is the thieves' guild is feeling ambitious. Aren't they always.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      "A %race% %class% rode into the Trade District on %mount% and the gnome children lost their minds. Can't blame them.",
      { "The %profession% trainer in Ironforge says she'll teach me to craft %item% one day. One VERY distant day.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Cathedral's blessing every soldier bound for %zone% this %timeofday%. The Light go with them, every one.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      "Some %level% %class% asked the way to %zone% in the Mage Quarter. Took the portal mage twenty minutes to stop laughing.",
      "Heard a Stormwind veteran earned '%pvptitle%' on the Wintergrasp wall. Bought him a pint at the Pig and Whistle and just listened.",
      "LFM %instance% %difficulty% forming at the Stormwind gates. Need a %role%, %gearscore%+, bring %consumable%.",
      { "Saw a Sentinel back from %zone% with %item% still wet from the fight. Darnassus turned out just to watch her pass.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn"} },
      "Hit revered with %rep% today. The Ironforge quartermaster finally smiled at me. First time in a %season%.",
      "%weather% over Dun Morogh this %timeofday%. The tram's running slow and the whole of Ironforge smells of wet beard.",
      { "A dwarf at the Stonefire Tavern swears he wrestled %rare% in the Hinterlands. Sober, he tells it shorter.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Alliance: Elwynn/Westfall farms & rural (expansion) ==
      { "Harvest's in early this year. The Elwynn fields came good and the granary's nearly full. The Light's been kind.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Westfall's dust gets in everything. In your bread, your boots, your teeth. A farmer's lot, and I'd not trade it.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Lost two sheep to the prowlers off the Elwynn treeline last night. Found one. The other's a wolf's supper now.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"gruff","bitter"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Goldshire's quiet of a morning before the adventurers wake. Just the smithy ringing and the smell of %food% from the inn.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "The Maclure and Saldean folk are sharing seed again after the gnolls burned the lower field. We mind our own out here in Westfall.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"kindly","weary"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Picked a basket of %herb% along the Elwynn creek for the Goldshire alchemist. Honest copper for an honest morning's stoop.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Rain's coming off the Redridge peaks. You learn to read the sky out here or you lose the hay to the wet.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "The Defias left these fields a graveyard of scarecrows. We're planting where we can and praying over the rest.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      -- == Alliance: dwarven highlands & wilderness (expansion) ==
      { "Up in the Dun Morogh snows the boars are fat and slow this %season%. A hunter's larder fills itself if you're patient.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"gruff","cheerful"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "Tracked a %monster% three valleys deep in the highlands and came back with nothing but cold feet and a good story.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "The Explorers' League pays fair coin for old dwarven relics dug out of the Loch. Muddy work, but the digs tell grand tales.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "Spotted %rare% prowling the ridgeline at dusk and gave it a very wide, very respectful berth. Some beasts you leave to the bards.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"cowardly","wry"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "Camped under the stars in Loch Modan with nothing but a fire and a flask of %drink%. The mountain air clears a tired head.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "The wolves in the Wetlands run in packs the size of a war-band. Keep your fire high and your back to the rock.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "Hunting %critter% along the Teldrassil boughs is half the joy of being kaldorei. The forest gives, if you ask it kindly.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","kindly"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      -- == Alliance: Menethil/Auberdine docks & coast (expansion) ==
      { "Menethil harbor's thick with gulls and gossip today. The boat from Auberdine came in late and everyone's a theory why.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Hauled in a net heavy with %fish% off the Wetlands shallows. The Menethil market'll pay well before the tide turns.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"cheerful","greedy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "The crossing to Darnassus is calm this %timeofday%, but I've seen these straits swallow stouter ships than ours. Mind the rails.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","solemn"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Auberdine smells of salt and starlight. The night elves built their docks where the sea kisses the old forest. Lovely posting.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Naga were sighted off the Darkshore reefs again. We sail in pairs now and keep the harpoons oiled. Cowards live to sail twice.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","cowardly"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Old salt down the Menethil docks swears he saw %rare% breach off the bow once. We humor him. He buys the rounds.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "%weather% rolling in off the Great Sea. The dockmaster's already lashing the crates. A wise sailor's ashore before it lands.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Mended my nets all afternoon on the Auberdine pier. Slow, salty work, but the gulls keep good company and ask no questions.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"coast"} },
      -- == Alliance: war front & battlefield (expansion) ==
      { "Marching north with the Seventh Legion at first light. Pray for steady hands and a quick spring, friends.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={battlefield=3, road=1} },
      { "The Scourge don't tire and they don't grieve. We hold the line in %zone% anyway, because someone has to.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "Lost three good lads taking that ridge in %zone%. The Light keep them. We dig in at dusk and do it again tomorrow.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "My hands won't stop shaking before the horn sounds. The sergeant says that's just sense. Cowards and corpses, he says, that's the choice.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","nervous"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "Field-priest blessed the whole company before the charge in %zone%. Hard to be afraid when the Light's at your shoulder.", roles={"priest","soldier"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "Held the wall against a wave of %monster% till the relief came. The lads sang the whole time. That's the Alliance, that is.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","boastful"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "Frostbite, hardtack, and a hundred miles of Scourge between us and home. Soldiering in the north is no song, whatever the bards claim.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","bitter"}, areas={battlefield=2, wilderness=1} },
      { "The siege engines rolled out at dawn, all gnomish gears and dwarven steel. Whatever we're hitting in %zone% won't be standing long.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"boastful","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      -- == Alliance: roads, caravans & flight paths (expansion) ==
      { "Took %route% out of Stormwind at dawn. Half asleep till the conductor's bell, then the whole tunnel lit up. Never gets old.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Caravan to Lakeshire's running guards now after the Redridge ambushes. Pay's good if you don't mind the worry.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"nervous","gruff"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Gryphon master at Sentinel Hill knows every flight path in the west by heart. Tell him where, he'll get you there, bless him.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Walked the Elwynn road from Goldshire to the Stormwind gates as the lamps came on. A grand quiet hour, that.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Mud to the axles on the Westfall road after the rains. Pushed the cart half a mile and cursed the whole way. Farmer's life.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"weary","gruff"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "The deer crossing the Elwynn road at dusk stopped the whole caravan. Even the gruff old teamster smiled at the fawns.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"road"} },
      -- == Alliance: nobles, urchins & city texture (expansion) ==
      { "Lady Whitford's garden party spilled into the Cathedral square again. Half of Stormwind's nobility, and not one of them on time.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"wry","gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "One does not simply walk into the Stormwind keep, darling. One is announced. There are forms. There is a queue. It is exhausting.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Father wants me wed to a Bronzebeard cousin for the trade alliance. I want to see %zone% before I see a marriage contract.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"bitter","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Snatched a hot roll off the bakery sill in the Trade District. Don't tell the guard. Don't tell my mum either, she's worse.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I run messages for the Old Town merchants, fastest legs in Stormwind. Pay me a copper and your note's there before the bells.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"cheerful","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Slept under the canal bridge again. Warm enough if you find the right arch. The lamplighter pretends he doesn't see me. Decent of him.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"weary","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A noble dropped a whole silver in the gutter and didn't even turn. To them it's nothing. To me it's a week of %food%.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"bitter","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Cathedral folk leave bread out for us street kids on feast days. Not charity, Mother Anveena says. Just the Light, doing what it does.", roles={"urchin","priest"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Alliance: craftsmen, drunkards, vendors, priests (expansion) ==
      { "Hammered out a set of horseshoes for the Goldshire stable and a blade for a lad bound north. The forge doesn't care who you are. Only the steel.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"gruff","warm"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "The Great Forge taught me everything I know. A dwarf's hands learn the metal before his head does, my da used to say.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Carved a whistle from highland pine for a farmer's lass. She paid me in apples. Best wage I've had all %season%.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Three pints in at the Stonefire and the room's gone lovely and warm. One more and I'll fight a %monster%. Two more and I'll fight the bar.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"boastful","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I only drink to forget the war, friend. Trouble is the ale's so good in Ironforge I keep forgetting to leave.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Genuine kaldorei moonwell water, blessed and bottled! Cures what ails you, or my name isn't... well. Buy a vial and don't ask my name.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I'll not drop the price a copper more. This is Ironforge steel, lad, not some surface tinker's tin. You pay for what lasts.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"gruff","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Said the rites over a fallen Sentinel today. Even in death the kaldorei are beautiful. Elune gather her gently.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A frightened recruit came to the Cathedral asking if the Light forgives a coward. I told him there are no cowards. Only the not-yet-brave.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"kindly","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Exodar's draenei have seen worlds end and still kept their faith. When my own falters, I think on that.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Alliance: guards, mages, innkeepers, gossip (expansion) ==
      { "Quiet shift on the Stormwind wall. Just me, the stars, and a gull that keeps trying to steal my supper. Cheeky beggar.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Logged a complaint about a duck in the canal 'behaving suspiciously.' This is the work that keeps the kingdom safe, citizens.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Portal to %zone% is up and stable for once. Step through quick before some apprentice sneezes and sends you to the Twisting Nether.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Spent the night decoding a Kirin Tor cipher by candlelight. The answer was 'turn the page over.' I have a headache and a degree.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Rooms upstairs, hot stew, and a fire that never dies. The Lion's Pride looks after its own. %drink%, friend?", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I've poured for kings and beggars at this bar and I'll tell you true: the beggars tip better and tell the finer stories.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "They say a noble's strongbox went missing from the Trade District vault. They say SI:7's already on it. They say a lot, don't they.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
    },
    -- two-person back-and-forth (speakers alternate A / B)
    duos = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 5: tagged duos (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"SI:7 posted a 'discreet inquiry' notice in Old Town.", "Discreet, and posted on a board. The irony's lost on nobody.", "What's it about?", "Missing %tradegood% off the Stormwind docks. 'Discreet' means they want it quiet AND they want everyone watching. Spies, eh. Mind your tongue near the harbor."}, roles={"guard","citizen"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Darnassus druids closed the moonwell grove to visitors.", "The leaves are turning early. They say Teldrassil's troubled.", "Troubled how?", "They won't say. But a Sentinel told me the tree DREAMS, and lately the dreams wake her. ...I've stopped asking questions I don't want answered."}, roles={"soldier","priest"}, moods={"dreamy","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"An Exodar anchorite's holding a blessing for the %zone% wounded.", "Free, as always?", "Free, as always. The draenei don't price the Light.", "...after all they lost, you'd think they'd hoard what comfort they have left.", "That's the wonder of them, isn't it. They lost a world and gave the Light away cheaper for it. Come. A blessing won't hurt either of us."}, roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Ironforge's hosting the %fish%-catching contest on the Loch this year.", "Dwarves fishing a frozen loch in this %weather%. Of course they are.", "Prize is a cask of the deep ale and a %currency% purse.", "...suddenly I'm a fisherman. Lend me a line and a very warm coat. For the Alliance, and the ale."}, roles={"sailor","citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A gnome's 'auto-angler' won the contest and they've disqualified it.", "Built a machine to fish FOR him? That's cheating.", "He argued it's 'engineering, not cheating.' The judges argued back with a net.", "...and now half of Tinker Town's protesting at the docks. Only in Stormwind does a fishing contest spark a philosophical riot. I love this city."}, roles={"craftsman","citizen"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged duos (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Westfall's gone to ruin since the harvest failed. You been out that way?", "Farms empty, Defias bold as brass on the roads. Broke my heart, what I saw.", "And Stormwind does nothing?", "Stormwind's looking north to %zone%. Westfall starves quiet at its back door. That's the cost of a war fought far away."}, roles={"farmer","citizen"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Redridge sent word — %monster% raids out of the hills again.", "Those folk have held that border alone for a generation.", "A handful of militia and a lot of stubbornness, aye.", "Then I'll ride out with my old blade and lend the stubbornness a hand. Somebody from the %city% ought to remember Redridge exists."}, roles={"soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={rural=2, wilderness=1} },
      { chain={"A gnome offered to 'optimize' my %item% with a gadget.", "Did you let him?", "It now does three things it never did and one I can't switch off.", "...that's Tinker Town for you. Half genius, half hazard, all enthusiasm. What's the thing you can't switch off?", "It hums the Stormwind anthem. Constantly. I've made a terrible, patriotic mistake."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Cathedral's taking Westfall refugees now.", "Whole families on the steps. The Bishop turned none away.", "Where will they all sleep?", "Wherever there's room, and we'll MAKE room. That's the Alliance, or it's just a word on a banner. Fetch blankets and spare %food%. We've work to do."}, roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"kindly","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"You served the northern campaign in %zone%, didn't you. With the dwarves.", "Shoulder to shoulder. A dwarf named Brann-something dragged me out of a drift by my collar.", "Ever find him after?", "Every Brewfest, same Ironforge tavern, same corner. We don't say much. We don't have to. Some bonds you forge once and they hold forever."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"The Stormwind nobles are throwing a masque for the %event%.", "And half the Trade District's been hired to cater it.", "Bet the kitchen hears better secrets than the ballroom.", "Always does. A serving tray's the best disguise in the %city% — nobody watches their tongue around the help. We'll know it all by the second course."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged duos (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"You marched in the last Stormwind muster to %zone%, didn't you.", "I did. Earned the title '%title%' and a scar I don't show in polite company.", "Was it worth it?", "Ask me at the Cathedral, where I light a candle for the lads who earned nothing but a name on a wall. ...no. But I'd go again. That's the curse of it."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A draenei vindicator loosed a %spell% over the Stormwind harbor at dusk.", "A blessing for the fleet bound to %zone%, I heard.", "The whole sky went gold. A child near me thought it was the Light made visible.", "...maybe it was. Draenei faith has a way of making the rest of us believe a little harder."}, roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Won this fine %mount% off a noble at cards in the Blue Recluse.", "A Stormwind noble lost a %mount% to YOU?", "He bet more than his purse and less than his pride could afford. I merely collected.", "...remind me never to deal you in. Drinks are on the mount-rich man, then."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Ironforge gryphons are grounded by %weather% again.", "Every %season% the same. The mountain keeps its own counsel.", "So we take the tram, packed in with half the Alliance.", "Aye, and a gnome will explain the whole engine to us the entire way. ...bring %food%. And patience. Mostly patience."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"That worgen warrior's been still as stone at the back of the Cathedral an hour.", "Mastering the beast. The Gilneans do it in plain sight and we never notice.", "Should the priests speak to him?", "They have. He asked only for a quiet corner and the Light's patience. Give him both. That's a war we'll never have to fight, and he fights it daily."}, roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Explorers' League is mounting an expedition to %zone%.", "After last time? Half of them came back, and half of THOSE came back wrong.", "They found %item%, though. Priceless, they say.", "...the League always finds the treasure. It's the coming home they keep losing the knack for. Light watch over the daft, brave fools."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Selling Elwynn apples to the soldiers shipping to %zone%, first one free.", "Soft of you. You'll go broke.", "A lad's last taste of home before a hard road? That's worth more than the copper.", "...give me a crate. I'll work the other gate. No soldier marches out of Stormwind hungry while we've apples to spare."}, roles={"vendor","farmer"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged duos (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"SI:7 had the Old Town roofs busy last night.", "I saw. The watch was told to go blind, so I went blind.", "What do you reckon they're hunting?", "In Old Town? Could be a spy, could be a debt. Either way it's above our pay and below our notice. Mind your post."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A gnome's selling a %toy% that runs on 'controlled explosions.'", "Controlled.", "His word. Not mine. He's only singed one eyebrow off so far.", "...only one? In Tinker Town that's practically a safety record. I'll take two."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Dwarven District forge is doing elven work now?", "A Sentinel commissioned a blade. Elven steel, dwarven fire. It's bound for %zone%.", "Bet the smith grumbled the whole way through.", "Grumbled, aye — then signed it like a masterwork. Old rivals make the finest collaborators when no one's watching."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"gruff","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"That worgen's been white-knuckled in the Trade District crowd a full hour.", "Hold steady, friend. The press of folk is hard on the Gilneans.", "Should we move him along?", "No. Stand near, say nothing, give him space to master it. That's a battle, what he's doing. We just don't see the field."}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"My nephew signed with the Argent at the gate this morning.", "What did they tell him?", "That they want the brave, not the strong. He's been standing taller since.", "...then he'll do fine in %zone%. It's the bravery that brings them home, not the muscle. Light keep him."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Found you in the Library again, lost in the %zone% histories.", "The historian here forgets I exist by the second hour. It's the most peace I get all %season%.", "You could just go home.", "Home doesn't have nine thousand pages on the fall of %zone%. Leave me to my dust, friend. Bring %food% if you love me."}, roles={"mage"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A draenei vindicator blessed the recruits' gear before the march.", "Even the dwarves went quiet.", "I've never seen the muster so still.", "The Light doesn't check your race at the door, friend. Human, dwarf, draenei — one blessing, one road, one hope they all come back."}, roles={"priest","soldier"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Gryphons are grounded — %weather%'s too rough off Dun Morogh.", "So it's the tram. With half the Alliance and all their luggage.", "I'll find us a corner.", "Bring your patience and your elbows. Ironforge to Stormwind underground at festival time is its own small war."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The King raised the %tradegood% tax for the %zone% campaign.", "We'll grumble. We'll pay. We always do.", "And send our sons after the very coin we paid.", "That's the bargain of it, isn't it. We fund the war and then we feed it our children. ...pour me another. I've talked myself grim."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged duos (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"How does a night elf get anywhere in Stormwind? It's all stairs and humans.", "Slowly. And with great dignity.", "I saw you fall off the bank steps this morning.", "...that was a tactical shadowmeld. Different thing entirely."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The tram to Ironforge stalled in the tunnel again.", "Gnome on board?", "Three of them. They've formed a committee about the fault.", "Then we'll be here till the %season% turns. Pull up a crate, I'll share my %food%."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Cathedral's full this %timeofday%. What's the occasion?", "Bells rang for a company lost out of %zone%. The whole district came to kneel.", "...I didn't know any of them.", "Doesn't matter. In Stormwind we grieve the Alliance's dead like our own. Come light a candle. They'll feel the warmth of strangers."}, roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A dwarf just challenged the whole Dwarven District tavern to a drinking contest.", "Again? He does this every %season%.", "He's a draenei this time. Twice the size of any of them.", "...and he'll still lose. Size means nothing against dwarven liver. Place your bets, friend."}, roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Darnassus moonwell's got a Sentinel standing watch all night again.", "There's talk of trouble up Teldrassil way.", "Always is. But I've never felt safer than under those leaves with the Sentinels on the boughs.", "Aye. Let the world rage. The night elves have kept this watch ten thousand years. One more %timeofday% won't break them."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Mage Quarter portal to %zone% is down. The line's enormous.", "A draenei's started a prayer circle near the front.", "Is it helping the portal?", "No. But the line's much calmer and someone's passing out %food%. Honestly the best the queue's ever been."}, roles={"mage","priest"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Explorers' League hauled a crate of %item% back from %zone%.", "Treasure?", "Could be priceless relics. Could be rubble. They're arguing about which as we speak.", "...so a normal day for the League, then.", "A normal day for the League. Someone's already set fire to a scroll to 'test its age.'"}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"First snow in Dun Morogh. All Ironforge smells of mulled %drink%.", "Best %season% under the mountain, no argument.", "The gnomes built a snow-machine that overshot and buried the bank entrance.", "...of course they did. Grab a shovel and a mug. This is the dwarven idea of a festival and I won't miss it."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A Gilnean held the door for me with the grandest little bow.", "They were a fine city once, behind that wall. The manners are all they carried out.", "It's almost sad, how careful they are with small things.", "When you've lost a whole country, a held door is a way of saying: this much, at least, I can still keep."}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"You shipping out to %zone% with the next muster?", "Aye. Recruiter made it sound like banners and glory.", "It's mud and waiting and cold %food%, mostly.", "...you went last call-up, didn't you.", "I did. So when the glory talk starts, find me. I'll tell you the true shape of it, and we'll both go anyway."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Stormwind tailor finished my cloak. The nobles are nodding at me now.", "You're a fishmonger.", "I'm a fishmonger in a VERY good cloak. Respect the craftsmanship.", "...alright, it is a fine cloak. Lend it me for the %event% and I'll respect it properly."}, roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Saw a night elf druid turn into a %critter% mid-sentence and wander off.", "Did they finish the sentence?", "No. Came back an hour later as herself, no explanation, finished a DIFFERENT sentence.", "...I've stopped questioning the druids. It's better for everyone's sanity. Mine especially."}, moods={"wry","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"An anchorite blessed my %companion% on the Exodar steps.", "And?", "The dog hasn't chewed a single boot since. A %season% of peace.", "...take MY dog to the Exodar. Take the whole kennel. Whatever they're doing, I need it."}, roles={"priest"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Six peoples under one banner and we still can't pick a tavern after muster.", "The dwarves want ale, the elves want quiet, the gnomes want to fix the tavern.", "And the draenei just want everyone to get along, which somehow makes it worse.", "...let's just eat at the gate fountain like always. United in mild disappointment. For the Alliance."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"The Lion's Pride Inn is packed tonight.", "It's the bard. He actually learned a second song.", "Two whole songs? Practically a symphony."}, roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"cheerful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Why is there a gnome statue in the middle of Stormwind?", "Knowledge, valor, and exceptionally good engineering, my friend.", "It's so we always look up to the little folk."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Anyone know why the Ironforge gryphons look so smug?", "They get to leave whenever they want. Wouldn't you be smug?"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Best enchanter in the city? Asking for my very plain weapon.", "Old elf in the Mage Quarter. Charges a fortune, glows like a star.", "Worth it. My sword now has a personality."}, roles={"mage","craftsman"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Did you see the lights over the Mage Quarter last night?", "Probably an apprentice's experiment.", "It spelled out a name. THAT'S not an experiment."}, roles={"mage"}, moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"First day with the city guard. Any tips?", "Stand up straight, learn the streets, and never chase a rogue into Old Town alone.", "Also the Mage Quarter sells the good coffee. You'll need it."}, roles={"guard"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"They say the King's planning another push north.", "Then Light help the lads who march. Icecrown takes more than it gives back.", "...I'll keep a candle lit in the Cathedral for them.", "We all will."}, roles={"soldier","priest"}, moods={"solemn","weary"} },
      { chain={"Teldrassil feels heavier lately, doesn't it?", "The Sentinels say the wilds are troubled. The leaves whisper louder.", "Or it's just the wind.", "...in ten thousand years, has it ever been 'just the wind' here?"}, moods={"nervous","solemn"} },
      { chain={"Did you catch that %race% %class% wielding %item% in the Trade District?", "Off %boss%, no less. %difficulty%.", "...and here's me still saving %gold% for a decent %profession% recipe."}, moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"%weather% over Dun Morogh again. The tram's crawling.", "Take %route% instead?", "In this %season%? I'd sooner wait. Pull up a stool at %shop% and we'll outlast it."}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Exalted with %rep% at last. The %mount% is mine.", "How long did THAT take?", "Most of a %season% and more repair %gold% than I'll ever admit to my spouse."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary"} },
      -- == Alliance: rural / Elwynn-Westfall duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Gnolls at the lower fence again last night.", "Aye, I heard the dogs. You drive them off?", "Pitchfork and a lantern. They don't like fire. Neither do I, but here we are.", "Farmer's courage. Light keep your hayricks dry."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"brave","weary"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { chain={"Saldean's pumpkins took a prize at the Goldshire fair, I hear.", "Biggest in Elwynn three years running. He's insufferable about it.", "I'd be insufferable too. Have you SEEN those pumpkins?"}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { chain={"You'd think after the Defias we'd get a quiet season in Westfall.", "Out here? Quiet just means the trouble hasn't found you yet.", "...cheerful as ever, neighbor.", "I farm dust and gnolls. Cheer's a town luxury."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={"rural"} },
      -- == Alliance: coast / docks duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Boat from Auberdine's three hours late.", "Naga, weather, or the captain found a tavern. Always one of the three.", "My coin's on the tavern.", "Wise coin. He found one last week too."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","gossipy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { chain={"Caught anything off the Menethil pier today?", "A boot, a crab, and three fine %fish%. The crab fought hardest.", "And the boot?", "The boot came quietly. I respect that in a boot."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { chain={"They say the Darkshore reefs are crawling with naga now.", "More every moon. We don't sail past the point after dark anymore.", "Cowardly?", "Alive. There's a difference, and I aim to keep enjoying it."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","cowardly"}, areas={"coast"} },
      -- == Alliance: war front / battlefield duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"First charge tomorrow. You scared?", "Witless with it. You?", "Same. The lads who say they aren't are lying or daft.", "Then we're the honest fools. Stand by me and we'll see the dawn."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { chain={"Hold the line, they said. As if the Scourge read the orders.", "We held it, didn't we?", "Aye. By the Light and stubbornness and not much else.", "That's most victories, in my experience."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { chain={"Field-priest's blessing the swords before the push on %zone%.", "Does it help?", "The steel? No. The lads? Every time.", "Then bless away, Father. We'll take all the courage we can carry."}, roles={"priest","soldier"}, moods={"solemn","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      -- == Alliance: wilderness / road duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Tracked that %monster% all the way up the Dun Morogh pass.", "And?", "And it tracked me right back. We came to a mutual understanding involving me leaving.", "Highland wisdom, that."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { chain={"The tram or the gryphon to Ironforge?", "Tram, every time. Warm, dry, and you can nap.", "Gryphon's faster.", "Gryphon's also forty minutes of clinging on and praying. I'll keep my nap."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={"road"} },
      { chain={"Caravan guard pay's gone up on the Lakeshire run.", "Because nobody sane takes it. Redridge is thick with gnolls.", "I'm not sane and I need the coin.", "Then I'll watch your back. Two fools live longer than one."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"brave","greedy"}, areas={"road"} },
      -- == Alliance: noble / urchin city duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Did you SEE what Lady Whitford wore to the Cathedral gala?", "Three layers of Silverpine silk in high summer. She nearly fainted in the receiving line.", "Beauty before breathing, darling. Always has been.", "And THAT is why I summer in Ironforge."}, roles={"noble"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Oi, hold your purse near the fountain, milord's not looking.", "You warning me or robbing me, kid?", "Warning. The robbing's the OTHER lad. I'm an honest urchin, me.", "...here's a copper for honesty, then. Now scram."}, roles={"urchin","noble"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Spare a coin for a cold kid, sir?", "Here. And take this bread, I've no stomach for it.", "Light bless you, milord, you're the kind one.", "Don't tell anyone. I've a reputation for being a miser to maintain."}, roles={"urchin","noble"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
    },
    -- group discussions (many voices, rotating cast of 4-6)
    groups = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 5: tagged groups (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"What's the most beautiful thing in any Alliance land? No cities — the WILD places.", "The moonlight on the Darnassus moonwells. I lost a whole %timeofday% to it once and counted it well spent.", "Dawn over Loch Modan from the dam. The whole valley gold and the %weather% rolling off the peaks.", "The Exodar crystals catching first light. A whole city singing soft, and you the only one awake to hear it.", "The Elwynn woods after rain. Nothing grand. Just green and quiet and home. That's enough for me.", "...we guard a lot of beauty, don't we. Easy to forget, with a war on.", "That's WHY we guard it. Not for the King. For the moonwells and the loch and the green after rain.", "To the wild places, then. The Alliance's truest treasure, and the realest reason to hold the line."}, roles={"citizen","soldier"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Stormwind's full of gnome contraptions lately. Each got a story?", "One 'optimized' my %item% and now it hums the anthem. Patriotic. Inescapable. I've made peace with it.", "An auto-angler that got banned from the %fish% contest and started a dockside protest. Tinker Town's still arguing.", "A self-heating teapot that heats EVERYTHING in a ten-foot radius. The inventor calls it 'ambient warmth.' We call it a fire hazard.", "A messenger-gadget that delivers your note and an unsolicited opinion about your handwriting. Rude. Effective. I use it daily.", "...do any of them actually work as intended?", "Define 'intended.' Define 'work.' Define... you know what, no. But they WORK, in the way only gnomish things do.", "To the gnomes, then. Half genius, half hazard, and the beating, sparking heart of Stormwind's chaos."}, roles={"craftsman","citizen"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged groups (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Westfall, Redridge, Duskwood — the border lands are bleeding. Who's seen it?", "Westfall's farms are dust and the Defias own the roads. I left with what I could carry and a grudge I'll never set down.", "Redridge holds, but barely. A few militia, a lot of nerve, and %monster% in the hills every %season%.", "Duskwood's worse. The dead don't stay down there. Honest folk barricade their doors by %timeofday% and pray for dawn.", "...and Stormwind looks north to %zone% the whole while, doesn't it.", "A realm that forgets its borders won't keep its heart long. We need to remind the %city% those folk exist.", "Then we tell their tale in every tavern till someone with a banner listens. The Alliance is the borderlands too, or it's nothing.", "Aye. To Westfall, Redridge, and Duskwood. The Alliance owes you a debt, and some of us mean to see it paid."}, roles={"farmer","soldier","citizen"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={rural=2, road=1} },
      { chain={"Brewfest's on. Best memory each of you has of it, then.", "Out-drinking a dwarf in his own Ironforge tavern. I lost, gloriously, and woke up an honorary member of his clan.", "Meeting the man who pulled me from a drift in %zone%, same corner, every year. We barely speak. It's everything.", "My first one. Fresh off the farm, eyes like saucers, a gnome handed me a %drink% that glowed and my whole world got bigger.", "Watching a night elf, a draenei, and a worgen attempt a dwarven drinking song. None knew the words. All committed entirely. Beautiful disaster.", "...it's the one festival where all six peoples just... relax together, isn't it.", "That's the magic of it. No banners, no muster, no %zone%. Just the Alliance being a family for one loud, golden week.", "To Brewfest, then. May the %drink% flow, the songs stay terrible, and the family stay whole one more year."}, roles={"citizen","soldier"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged groups (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Stormwind veterans' table — what'd the %zone% campaign cost each of you?", "A title and a limp. '%title%,' they call me. The limp doesn't have a fancier name.", "A brother. The Cathedral keeps his name carved with the rest. I keep his cloak folded by the door.", "My whole company, near enough. I came down that road with four of forty. I don't count it as surviving. I count it as being left.", "...and I never marched at all. I forged the blades you carried. I'll carry THAT weight to my grave — that I armed you and stayed safe.", "Don't. Without your steel none of the four come home. The Alliance is the smith AND the soldier, and the Light weighs them the same.", "...he's right, you know. To the man who armed us. We'd not be at this table to grieve without you.", "To all of it, then. The fallen, the four, the cloak, the forge. Light keep what %zone% left us. And keep what it took."}, roles={"soldier","craftsman"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"What's the most ALLIANCE thing each of you has ever witnessed?", "A dwarf carrying a wounded night elf two miles down the Dun Morogh road, grumbling the whole way, never once stopping.", "A gnome rebuilding a draenei refugee's exploded stove for free, then 'improving' it until it exploded again. The intent was pure.", "The whole Cathedral standing for a fallen %race% none of them knew, because the banner says we grieve our own.", "A worgen lifting a lost human child onto his shoulders so she could spot her mother in the Trade District crowd. Gentle as anything.", "...we're a quarrelsome, mismatched, beautiful mess of a banner, aren't we.", "Six peoples who keep CHOOSING each other. That's not weakness. That's the whole strength of the thing.", "To the mismatched banner. May we keep choosing. For the Alliance, and for the room we make."}, roles={"citizen","soldier"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged groups (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Round the table — what does the Alliance actually MEAN to each of you?", "It's the dwarf who pulled my cart from the ditch on the Dun Morogh road and wouldn't take a copper.", "It's six banners that could've stayed six and chose to be one instead. That choice, made fresh every %season%.", "It's the Cathedral taking in a sick %race% child with no questions. The Light over the law.", "It's my Gilnean neighbor, who lost a whole country and still holds my door.", "...it's a lot of strangers agreeing to make room, isn't it.", "Aye. That's the whole of it. Not the King, not the spires. The room we make for each other.", "To the room we make. May the table never run short of seats. For the Alliance."}, roles={"citizen","soldier"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The %zone% campaign's all anyone talks of. Who's lost someone to it?", "My nephew marched with the Argent last %timeofday%. I bless his blade in my mind every hour.", "Lost a brother there two musters back. The Cathedral keeps his name. I keep his cloak.", "My whole forge works for it now — blades, plate, nails. If I can't fight, I'll arm the ones who do.", "...and I just keep the gate inn warm for the ones who limp home. It never feels like enough.", "It's all enough. The blade, the blessing, the cloak, the warm bed. The Alliance is held up by ALL of it.", "Then we hold our corners and we wait. The smith, the priest, the innkeeper, the worried uncle.", "Together. Light bring them back down the Stormwind road to every one of us. To the ones in %zone%."}, roles={"craftsman","priest","innkeeper"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged groups (ALLIANCE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Settle it: which Alliance city is truly the finest?", "Stormwind. Spires carved from morning light, gardens in every district. Nothing finer.", "Ironforge. Warm stone, the Great Forge, and ale that never runs dry. Keep your spires.", "Darnassus. You've clearly never lost an hour to moonlight on the moonwells.", "The Exodar. Walls that SING, friends. The rest of you live in quiet rock.", "...and Gilneas, before the wall. We don't speak of it much. But it was finer than all of yours.", "There it is. Every one of us loyal to wherever our hearthstone's set.", "Aye. Home's home. Mine just happens to be the one that doesn't tilt when you spill your %drink%.", "...low blow, dwarf. The Exodar's tilt is CHARACTER."}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"How'd each of you end up in Stormwind, then?", "Marched here from %zone% after the call-up and just... never left. The canals got me.", "Came for the Explorers' League. Stayed for a gnome who fixes my %toy% and never charges right.", "Fled here behind the Gilnean refugees. They made room for me. I make room for them now.", "Born three streets from the Cathedral. Never wanted any other sky but Stormwind's.", "...funny. Five different roads, one city, one table.", "That's the Alliance for you. A bunch of strangers who decided to make room. Pass the %food%.", "To making room. May the table always be one seat too long."}, roles={"citizen","adventurer"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The recruiters are at the gate again. Talk me out of signing, somebody.", "Can't. I signed last %season%. Came back with a limp and no regrets I'll admit to sober.", "Don't go for the banners. They lie. Go because someone you love sleeps safer for it. That's the only true reason.", "Or don't go at all. There's no shame in keeping the home fires that the soldiers march to defend.", "...the Light doesn't keep score on who held a blade. Only on who held something dear.", "Then hold SOMETHING dear, all of you, and let that pick your road, not the recruiter's drum.", "Wise. Now drink up. Whoever marches and whoever stays, tonight we're all just folk at a fire."}, roles={"soldier","citizen"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Strangest thing each of you has seen in a Stormwind square?", "A gnome's %toy% dispenser that exploded, dispensed, then exploded again. The children formed a fan club.", "A fully armored paladin playing hopscotch. Dead serious. On his way to %zone%, apparently.", "A night elf druid dozing as a %critter% in the fountain. The guards left a little sign: 'do not feed the druid.'", "A draenei anchorite blessing a line of pets one by one. Took all %timeofday%. Worth it. The dogs glowed.", "...this city is a circus with a Cathedral in the middle, and I adore every cobble.", "Couldn't have said it better. Same fountain tomorrow?", "Same fountain. Bring %food% for the druid. Sign or no sign."}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Word's grim out of %zone%. How's everyone holding up?", "My boy's with the muster there. I bake his favorite %food% every %timeofday% like he might walk in. He won't yet. But I bake it.", "I lost my company there a war ago. I light a candle in the Cathedral and I keep walking. It's all you can do.", "The League's sending relics and supplies up the line. It's not a blade, but it's hands doing something.", "...I just keep the tavern open. Warm fire, full pot, a place for the ones who do come home.", "And that's no small thing. A soldier needs a hearth to march toward as much as a cause.", "Then we each hold our corner — the bread, the candle, the supplies, the fire — and we wait, together.", "Together. For the Alliance, aye, but mostly for them. Light bring them home to their warm pots."}, roles={"citizen","priest","innkeeper"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Which corner of Stormwind is the best to just sit and waste an afternoon?", "The canals, no contest. Watch the boats, feed the gulls, forget the war exists.", "Cathedral Square. Quietest spot in the whole city. I go there to think.", "The Trade District, if you like chaos. Best people-watching in the Alliance.", "Old Town, if you don't mind the company. The rooftops at dusk are something else.", "The Dwarven District. Warm forge, cold ale, and a dwarf who'll tell you his whole life story.", "...you've all forgotten the gardens in the Mage Quarter in spring.", "Light, you're right. The gardens. Lost a whole afternoon there last week.", "That's the secret, isn't it. This city's full of corners worth losing an afternoon to."}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"LFM %instance% %difficulty%, summon's at the Stormwind gates.", "Need what?", "A %role% and a %class% who knows the fight against %boss%.", "%gearscore% and I've got %consumable% for the whole run.", "Invite's up. Mind the Cathedral bells, we move when they toll."}, roles={"adventurer"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Worth grinding %rep% out of Ironforge?", "The %mount% alone is worth more than %gold%, aye.", "And the %profession% recipes you can't get anywhere else.", "Then I'll run the dailies till my gryphon knows the way by heart.", "It will. Mine flies to the quartermaster without me even asking."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"That %race% %class% by the fountain — is that really %item%?", "Glows like Teldrassil at moonrise. Has to be.", "Earned it off %boss%, I heard. %difficulty%, no deaths.", "...I need to sit down. Some people just live a different life.", "Buy them a drink at the Lion's Pride. Greatness rubs off, they say.", "Nothing's ever rubbed off on you but ale stains.", "And I wear them with pride."}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Best corner of the Alliance to watch %weather% roll in?", "The Stormwind canals. Rain on the water, lamps coming on one by one.", "The high terraces of Darnassus. You're above the clouds half the time.", "Ironforge — you don't watch the weather, you escape it by the Great Forge.", "The Exodar crystals catch storm-light like nothing else in the world.", "...all of you, romantics, the lot of you.", "It's a %season% evening and there's a war on. Let us have the small beauties.", "Fair. To small beauties, then. And to surviving long enough to notice them."}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Alliance: rural / farming-life groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"How's the Elwynn harvest looking this year, neighbors?", "Wheat came good. The rains held off just long enough.", "Westfall's a dust-bowl, as ever. We trade you grain for your courage out here.", "Lost half my orchard to the gnolls, but the apples that lived are sweet.", "Goldshire mill's grinding day and night to keep up. Good problem to have.", "...you all remember when the Defias had us hiding in our cellars?", "Hard to forget. Makes a full granary taste sweeter, doesn't it.", "To the harvest, then. And to never going hungry under a Defias winter again.", "Light keep the fields green. Pass the cider, I've earned it."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"rural"} },
      -- == Alliance: coast / dockside groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"What's the worst crossing you've sailed out of Menethil?", "The Darnassus run in a winter gale. Lost the mainsail and most of my supper.", "Auberdine in naga season. They came up the anchor chain. The ANCHOR CHAIN.", "Booty Bay way, when the goblins 'forgot' to mention the reef.", "Any crossing with a green captain. Give me a storm over a fool at the wheel.", "...you're all braver than me. I haul nets from the pier and sleep ashore.", "Smartest of the lot, then. The sea takes the bold first.", "Aye. To the ones it took. And to dry boots and a full net.", "Drinks at the Menethil tavern. First round on the naga survivor."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={"coast"} },
      -- == Alliance: war front / battlefield groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"How does a body keep its nerve before a charge?", "Prayer. The field-priest's words, and the Light at my back.", "I think of home. Elwynn in spring. Gives me something to march toward.", "Honestly? I'm terrified every time. I just march scared.", "That's the truest answer of the lot, lad. We all march scared.", "The veterans don't, surely?", "The veterans are the ones who learned to march scared and live. There's no other kind.", "...then we're all in good company. Stand fast when the horn sounds.", "For the Alliance. And for getting home to tell it badly over ale."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","cowardly"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      -- == Alliance: road / caravan groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Best way west out of Stormwind, then? Settle it for me.", "%route%, no argument. Warm, fast, and you wake up in Ironforge.", "Gryphon if you're in a hurry and don't mind your stomach in your boots.", "On foot through Elwynn if you've the time. Prettiest road in the kingdom.", "Caravan if you've goods to haul — but pay for guards past Westfall.", "...the urchin networks know shortcuts none of you do, by the way.", "The street kids? Truly?", "Pay one a copper and they'll walk you to a gate you never knew existed. Best guides in the city.", "Light, the things you learn on the road. To shortcuts and short coppers, friends."}, roles={"adventurer","urchin"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"road"} },
    },
  },

  horde = {
    -- standalone one-liners (single speaker)
    lines = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged one-liners (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { "Barrens caravans are hit hard this %season% — centaur from the dust, quilboar from the thorns. For the right %currency% a goblin will haul %tradegood% through anything.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { "Sen'jin sent word the murlocs are bold on the coast again. The Darkspear hold that shore with a few hunters and the loa at their backs. The Horde should stand with them.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={coast=2, rural=1} },
      { "A goblin 'upgraded' my %item% and now it shouts a discount slogan mid-swing. Only in the Horde would a weapon try to sell you something. I've decided it's a feature.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Brill grows Tirisfal grain for Durotar though the Forsaken can't eat a bite of it. To labor for a hunger you'll never feel again — leave them an honor at the totem.", roles={"farmer","priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={rural=2, city=1} },
      { "Every %event% I meet the tauren who carried me a mile in %zone% when my leg gave out. Same Thunder Bluff rise, same silence, same shared %drink%. No peace undoes that bond.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Bilgewater cartel's 'sponsoring' the %event% — their logo on every banner, a surcharge in every %food%. But the fireworks are grand. Take their party, count your coin after.", roles={"citizen","vendor"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "An orc warrior knelt to let a Darkspear child press a tiny loa-charm into his hand before the march to %zone%. Took it like a holy relic. In the Horde, every blessing counts.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Thunder Bluff's elders debated the %season% hunt-rites for a full %timeofday% and never once raised a voice. The tauren argue like the wind — patient, and it gets where it's going.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged one-liners (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { "Earned the title '%title%' in %zone% under the warchief's banner. I leave an offering at the totem each %timeofday% for the ones who earned only the soil.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A shaman cracked the dusk sky with a %spell% to bless the warriors for %zone%. A young troll dropped to his knees. The elements answer the Horde in plain sight.", roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Won a fine %mount% off a drunk goblin who bet his whole caravan. I robbed a fool, not a merchant. There's a difference, and I sleep fine on it.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Forsaken stands at the Undercity gate watching the living hurry past. Says they like remembering what wanting looked like. Bravest grief I ever saw.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Selling Mulgore cornbread to every warrior marching to %zone%, first piece free. The Earth Mother would frown if I charged a soul for his last taste of home.", roles={"vendor","farmer"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Wind-riders grounded by %weather% off the Barrens, so it's the long %route% on foot — and a goblin hawking %consumable% at robbery prices every mile of it.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "A blood elf granted that the loa were 'a valid framework' and the troll laughed for an hour. Two who couldn't differ more, finding the one thread. That's the Horde.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Bilgewater goblin's 'genuine %mount% whistle' summons an angry Barrens %critter% instead. Sells out daily. In the Horde, even the swindles have a sense of humor.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged one-liners (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { "An orc shaman called the rains early to save the Durotar crops. The elements don't serve the Horde — they CHOOSE us, and that's a debt we honor.", roles={"priest","farmer"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "The Kor'kron drilled in the Valley of Strength at dawn — orc, troll, tauren, and Forsaken stepping as one column. The Horde is no rabble. Mark it.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"boastful","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A tauren elder told the young ones the tale of %tale% by the totem fire till the stars came out. The Horde remembers through its storytellers.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","kindly"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "A Forsaken apothecary saved a whole Durotar village from the fever with a %consumable% no living healer could brew. We don't ask their methods. We just live.", roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "A blood elf magister mended a goblin's exploded %toy% with a flick of the wrist and didn't even break conversation. Sin'dorei make it look like nothing.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A troll showed me the loa-marks carved above his door — one for each spirit that's carried his family. The Darkspear never walk %zone% alone, he said.", roles={"citizen","priest"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"} },
      { "Bilgewater goblin set up a 'war-surplus' stall hawking dented %item% off the %zone% front. Grim trade, but a warrior on a budget doesn't argue.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Orgrimmar's recruiters promise plunder and glory in %zone%. The old veterans by the gate say nothing and drink. Listen to the silence, young blood.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The wind-riders are grounded — %weather% off the Barrens too fierce. So it's the long %route% on foot, sharing the road with half of Durotar.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Selling Mulgore cornbread and spiced Durotar %drink% by the Orgrimmar gate — fuel for any warrior bound to %zone%, and the first cup's on me.", roles={"vendor","farmer"}, moods={"kindly","cheerful"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "A tauren and an orc argued the old way versus the new over a shared %drink% and parted as brothers. The Horde fights itself only to forge itself.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gruff","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "An orphan matron of the Horde led her little ones through the Drag, each clutching a carved %toy%. Even the goblins stopped hawking to let them pass.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Darkspear witch doctor read the spilled %drink% and told me a storm was coming to %zone%. Three days later, %weather%. I've stopped doubting the loa.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","dreamy"} },
      { "The Forsaken keep the Royal Quarter cold and quiet by choice. 'The dead were never fond of crowds,' the warden told me, and almost smiled.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged one-liners (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      -- Orgrimmar life
      { "The Valley of Strength is loud as a war drum this %timeofday%. Auctioneers, recruiters, and a goblin selling 'genuine %item%' over the top of both.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Orgrimmar's smiths have the forges roaring. You can hear the hammer-song from the Drag, and it sounds like the Horde itself breathing.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"boastful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Kor'kron doubled the gate watch after word came down the %route% from %zone%. Warchief's orders. We don't ask twice.", roles={"guard","soldier"}, moods={"gruff","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A young orc asked me the road to %zone% to prove himself. I gave him a blade and the truth: glory's heavier than it looks, pup.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","gruff"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "The Drag never sleeps. Trolls, goblins, and the smell of %food% off a dozen carts. I'd not live anywhere else in Orgrimmar.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Goblin in the Valley of Honor sold me a 'discount' %mount%. It bolted at the first %weather% and I've not seen it since. Lesson learned.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","bitter"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Thunder Bluff & the tauren
      { "Open sky, clean wind, and not one auctioneer screaming in my ear. Thunder Bluff is the only capital that lets a soul breathe.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "An elder on the high rise blessed the %season%'s hunt and thanked the Earth Mother for every %critter% taken. The tauren waste nothing, least of all gratitude.", roles={"priest","farmer"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"} },
      { "The wind off the mesa carried %weather% in by dusk, just as the totem-readers said. The tauren have never once been wrong about the sky.", moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "A tauren gently lifted a lost goblin onto his shoulder so the little one could spot his caravan. Made my whole %season%.", moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Undercity & the Forsaken
      { "Undercity's grim, aye, but the Forsaken built a home out of grief, and there's a stubborn beauty in that no spire can match.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "An apothecary offered me a vial of something green for my cough. I declined. In the Undercity you learn which %profession% to trust, and it's none of them.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Forsaken told me they still remember the taste of bread they can no longer eat. They keep a %food% on the sill anyway. For the memory.", moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Royal Quarter echoes when it's empty. The Forsaken like it that way. The dead were never fond of crowds, they say.", moods={"wry","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Silvermoon & the blood elves
      { "Ten thousand years of refinement and it shows in every gilded arch of Silvermoon. The blood elves lost much, but never their eye for beauty.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A magister in Silvermoon enchanted my %item% with %enchant% and made it look effortless. Showoffs, the lot of them. Magnificent showoffs.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Sunfury spires catch the dawn and the whole of Silvermoon burns gold for a moment. Even an old %profession% like me stops to watch.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Blood elves still feel the thirst, deep down. You'll see one pause, breathe, master it, and carry on lovely as ever. Quiet courage, that.", moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Trolls & Darkspear
      { "A Darkspear told me the loa watch over the Echo Isles still. He spoke of %zone% like it was a living thing that remembered his name.", moods={"dreamy","solemn"} },
      { "Why do the trolls always say 'mon'? Why do you always say 'epic %item%'? We've all got our songs, friend.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A troll witch doctor brewed me a %drink% for the road that tasted of swamp and victory. Walked thirty leagues on it. Don't ask what's in it.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","brave"}, areas={road=1, wilderness=1} },
      -- Goblins & trade
      { "Goblin set up a 'Bilgewater bargain bin' by the bank. Everything's half off and twice as likely to explode. Business is booming.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A goblin sold me a map to buried %gold% in %zone%. The %gold% was another map. I respect the hustle. I want my coin back, but I respect it.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={road=1, city=1} },
      -- Cross-Horde unity & war
      { "Orc, troll, tauren, Forsaken, elf, goblin — six peoples bound by blood and grit. We argue like a family because we ARE one.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"warm","gruff"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { "Word from %zone%: the line held another %timeofday%. Lok'tar. Spare a thought for the warriors who won't see the next %season%.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={battlefield=1, city=1} },
      { "Recruiters in the Valley of Honor promise glory in %zone%. I marched last call-up. Glory's a word the ones who stayed home use.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Kor'kron broke up a brawl between an orc and a troll over an old grudge from before either was born. Some quarrels the Horde just inherits.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- Daily Horde trade & craft
      { "Selling cured %fish% off the Bilgewater docks — keeps a %season% in the salt, fills a warrior's pack, two coppers and don't haggle.", roles={"vendor","sailor"}, moods={"gruff","greedy"}, areas={coast=1, city=1} },
      { "Forged a blade in Orgrimmar steel for a warrior bound to %zone%. He'll carry it into the teeth of it. May my work hold where he can't.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"solemn","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "An orc shaman called the wind to dry the %tradegood% on the racks before the %weather% hit. The elements answer the Horde. We don't forget the gift.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { "Valley of Strength is roaring today. Half the Horde came to gawk at the new recruits.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Drag smells of leather and smoke and something I'd rather not name. Home sweet home.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Down in the Cleft of Shadow the warlocks are at it again. Whole tunnel reeks of brimstone.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Garrosh's banners are everywhere now. The old guard mutters, but quietly.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"gruff","bitter"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Zeppelin to the Undercity is late again. Goblin pilot says it's 'weather.' There is no weather up there.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Valley of Honor forges never sleep. Neither do the smiths, apparently.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Grommash Hold is busy. When the Warchief calls a meeting, the whole city listens at the door.", moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The wind on the rises of Thunder Bluff carries the smell of sage and open plains. Peace, finally.", moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Watched the sun set over Mulgore from the highest rise. The tauren were right to settle here.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Spirit Rise is quiet today. Even the totems seem to be listening for something.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","dreamy"} },
      { "The Apothecarium's fumes are thick today. The Forsaken are brewing something that bubbles green.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Undercity's canals run with things best left unexamined. The Forsaken call it 'ambiance.'", moods={"wry","bitter"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Forsaken bard played a dirge in the Trade Quarter. Saddest thing I've heard. Tipped him double.", moods={"solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Royal Quarter is colder than the grave. Fitting, given the tenants.", moods={"bitter","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Dark Rangers patrol the upper ring tonight. The Banshee Queen takes no chances.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Silvermoon City gleams red and gold even at midnight. The blood elves spare no expense on beauty.", moods={"dreamy","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Royal Exchange is bustling. Blood elves haggle like it's an art form, because to them it is.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Magisters arguing in Murder Row again. Yes, that's really what the street is called.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A sin'dorei tailor offered to fix my robes. Now I'm too well-dressed to fight anything.", roles={"craftsman","vendor"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Someone's lost a pet hawkstrider near the bank. Answers to 'Sparkles.' Reward offered, dignity not included.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A Forsaken and a human stood at the same grave in Duskwood. Some losses don't pick a side.", moods={"solemn"} },
      { "Took the zeppelin from Orgrimmar to the Undercity. Goblin pilot did a loop 'for fun.' I did not have fun.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","nervous"} },
      { "Spent the afternoon in Silvermoon just looking at the architecture. Felt underdressed the entire time.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Thunder Bluff at dawn, Undercity at dusk. The Horde lands have a beauty the maps never capture.", moods={"dreamy"} },
      { "Summer heat in Orgrimmar is no joke. Even the orcs are seeking shade in the Drag today.", moods={"weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Thunder over Thunder Bluff. On the nose, I know, but the tauren love it.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "The Cleft of Shadow gives me the creeps and I'm a warlock. That's saying something.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Valley of Wisdom is where the old shaman gather. Walk soft and listen; they've earned their silence.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Pools of Vision in Thunder Bluff reflect the sky so clearly you forget which way is up.", moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "My hawkstrider knocked over a fruit cart in Silvermoon. The vendor charged me for 'street theater.'", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Trying to park my kodo by the Orgrimmar bank. Got a ticket. From a goblin. With a straight face.", moods={"wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Say what you will about Orgrimmar, but watching the sun rise over those iron walls stirs something in the blood.", moods={"boastful","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Thunder Bluff doesn't conquer; it abides. There's a strength in that the warmongers never understand.", moods={"solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Silvermoon rebuilt itself from ruin into the most beautiful city on Azeroth. Spite never looked so elegant.", moods={"boastful","bitter"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Undercity is a tomb that learned to live. Grim, yes. But the Forsaken made a home where there was only grief.", moods={"solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Word from Orgrimmar: the Warchief's recruiting for a march north. The old veterans sharpen their axes and say nothing.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Gathering a war-band at the Orgrimmar gates for a strike on %instance%. Bring steel and a strong stomach.", roles={"soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"brave"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Anyone at the Thunder Bluff rise want to ride out to %zone%? The plains are calling and the city's too loud.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"rural"} },
      "A %race% %class% rode through the Valley of Strength on %mount% with %item% strapped to their back. Even the grunts stopped to %emote%.",
      { "Word from the front: someone put %boss% in the dirt at %difficulty% and lived to brag about it in the Drag.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"boastful"}, areas={battlefield=2, city=1} },
      "LFM %instance% %difficulty% mustering at the Orgrimmar gates. Need a %role%, %gearscore%+, and bring your own %consumable%.",
      { "The %profession% master in the Valley of Honor wants %gold% just to teach me %item%. The Earth Mother gives; the trainers most certainly take.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"gruff","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      "Hit exalted with %rep% this %timeofday%. The quartermaster handed over the %mount% like it was nothing. Lok'tar earned, mon.",
      "Some %level% %class% wandered into the Cleft of Shadow asking for directions to %zone%. The warlocks just... smiled. Poor fool.",
      "A Forsaken hunter dragged %rare% back from %zone% to mount on the wall. The Apothecarium offered to 'preserve' it. She declined, wisely.",
      { "%weather% over the Barrens on %route% this %timeofday%. The wind riders are grounded and the caravan masters are furious.", moods={"weary"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { "Heard a veteran in Grommash Hold carries the title '%pvptitle%'. Earned it the only way the Horde respects — in blood.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"boastful","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Bard in the Undercity sang of %tale% till the whole Trade Quarter went still. Even the Forsaken remembered how to mourn.", moods={"solemn","dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Horde: Mulgore plains & rural (expansion) ==
      { "The kodo herds are moving down to the low pastures for the %season%. A tauren's heart goes quiet watching them pass.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Bloodhoof Village smells of woodsmoke and roasting %food% tonight. The whole tribe gathers when the hunt comes home full.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "We take only what the plains offer and give thanks for all of it. The Earth Mother feeds those who do not grasp.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Gathered %herb% along the Golden Plains for the village healer. The grass parts for you if you walk it with respect.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Quilboar raided the totems at the edge of the field again. We mend them, we sing over them, we stand the watch. Mulgore is ours.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"gruff","brave"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "A young tauren brought down his first kodo this week. The elders sang for him. The plains gain a hunter; the boy gains a name.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "The wind through the Mulgore grass sounds like the breathing of something vast and asleep. The Earth Mother, the elders say.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Durotar's red dirt grows little but spite and cactus, but a hardy people made a home of it. That is the orcish way.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"gruff","boastful"}, areas={"rural"} },
      -- == Horde: the Barrens & wilderness (expansion) ==
      { "Tracked a %monster% across the Barrens for two days. The Crossroads bounty's good, but the heat near broke me.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","gruff"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "The Barrens at night is alive with hyena-laughter and worse. A wise hunter keeps the fire high and the spear closer.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","brave"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "Saw %rare% prowling the Stonetalon pass and let it pass right back. Some kills aren't worth the funeral, mon.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"cowardly","wry"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "The plainstriders out past the Crossroads make fine eating and finer hunting. Bring an axe and a strong stomach for the heat.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"gruff","cheerful"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "Camped in the Stonetalon wilds with the loa watching from the dark. A troll's never truly alone out here. Comforting, mostly.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "Hunting %critter% along the Durotar coast scrub for the cookpot. Lean pickings, but a grunt learns to make do, mon.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { "The centaur war-bands roam the deep Barrens still. We hunt in pairs out there now. Even a brave orc respects a centaur lance.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"brave","nervous"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      -- == Horde: Ratchet/Bilgewater/Echo Isles coast (expansion) ==
      { "Ratchet docks never close, mon. Goblins trading, sailors swearing, and somebody always trying to sell you a 'genuine' map.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","gossipy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Hauled a net of fat %fish% out of the Echo Isles shallows. The trolls there share the catch and the fire freely. Good harbor, that.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"warm","cheerful"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "The Bilgewater goblins will sail you anywhere for the right coin and sink you for a better offer. We watch our backs and our cargo.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Sea spray off the Echo Isles at dawn, drums on the wind, the loa close in the mist. A troll's soul rests easy by this water.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Naga came up the Ratchet pilings last night. We fought them off, but I'll not sail the bay alone for a %season%, I tell you true.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","cowardly"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "%weather% rolling in off the bay. The goblin harbormaster's screaming about his cargo. Let the surface-folk panic; the tide always wins.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { "Mended my raft on the Durotar shore all afternoon, mon. Slow work, salt in every cut, but the sea asks patience and gives fish.", roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","warm"}, areas={"coast"} },
      -- == Horde: war front & battlefield (expansion) ==
      { "We march on %zone% at the Warchief's word. Sharpen your axe, grunt, and let the enemy hear the drums before they see the steel.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","boastful"}, areas={battlefield=3, road=1} },
      { "Held the ridge in %zone% against a wave of %monster% till the reinforcements came. The Horde does not break. The Horde digs in.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "Buried three of my war-band beneath the cairns at %zone% today. We sing them to the ancestors and we fight on. Lok'tar ogar.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "My hands shake before the horn, and any orc who says his don't is lying to you. The trick is charging anyway, mon.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "The witch doctor painted the war-band with the loa's marks before the charge on %zone%. Hard to fear death with the spirits at your back.", roles={"priest","soldier"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "Frost, hunger, and a hundred Scourge between us and Orgrimmar. The bards make soldiering north sound grand. The bards have never bled north.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","bitter"}, areas={battlefield=2, wilderness=1} },
      { "Watched the demolishers roll out at dawn, all goblin powder and orcish iron. Whatever fortress we're cracking in %zone% won't stand the day.", roles={"soldier"}, moods={"boastful","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { "Sin'dorei battle-mages lit the whole front line crimson before the charge. Say what you will of the blood elves; they fight beautiful.", roles={"soldier","mage"}, moods={"boastful","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      -- == Horde: roads, caravans & flight paths (expansion) ==
      { "Took the Barrens road to the Crossroads with the caravan. Two days of dust, one quilboar scare, and a wind rider that wouldn't fly. Typical.", roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "The wind rider master at Razor Hill knows every roost from here to Thunder Bluff. Tell him where, mon, he'll point your beak the right way.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"warm"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Walked the Durotar road from Razor Hill to the Orgrimmar gates under the red dusk. A hard land, but a beautiful one to a Horde eye.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","weary"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Caravan to the Crossroads runs armed grunts now after the centaur raids. The pay's good if the dust and the worry don't get you first.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"gruff","nervous"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "Zeppelin tower's busy this %timeofday%. Half of Durotar's lining up for the Undercity run and the goblin's selling them all 'priority' tickets.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry","gossipy"}, areas={"road"} },
      { "The kodo caravan stopped dead while a herd of %critter% crossed the Barrens track. Even the gruff old teamster waited. The plains keep their own time.", roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={"road"} },
      -- == Horde: nobles, urchins & city texture (expansion) ==
      { "Lord Solanar's salon in Silvermoon was simply EVERYONE this evening. The magisters, the rangers, two very dull diplomats. Divine, darling.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "One does not merely enter Silvermoon society, darling. One is invited, vetted, and judged. I, naturally, sailed through. As one does.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "My family held a seat among the chieftains before the Cataclysm scattered us. Now I drink in the Drag and pretend it suits me.", roles={"noble"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Snatched a skewer off the Drag vendor's grill and ran. He threw a cleaver. Missed by a mile, mon. Slow arm, good aim with the curses.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I run messages across Orgrimmar faster than any wind rider, mon. Copper a note, and I know every shortcut through the Drag the guards don't.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"cheerful","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Sleep in the warm by the Valley of Honor forges, me. The smiths pretend not to see, and a forge-warm night beats a Durotar cold one.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"weary","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "A blood elf dropped a gold coin in Murder Row and didn't stoop. To them it's dust. To me it's a moon of %food%, mon. I stooped fast.", roles={"urchin"}, moods={"bitter","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The Earthen Ring leaves food at the Cleft of Shadow steps for us street-folk on the feast days. The elements provide, the old shaman says.", roles={"urchin","priest"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Horde: craftsmen, drunkards, vendors, priests (expansion) ==
      { "Beat a war-axe into shape in the Valley of Honor today, and a plow-blade for a Mulgore farmer. Steel doesn't care who swings it. Only that it's true.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"gruff","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "An orc learns the forge before he learns his letters, and rightly so. My hammer's said more true things than my mouth ever has.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"gruff","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Carved a totem of Mulgore oak for a young shaman. He paid me in dried meat and thanks. Best wage a craftsman can ask, that.", roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "Three horns of grog at the Drag and the whole world's gone warm and loud. One more and I'll wrestle a %monster%, mon. Two more and I'll lose.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"boastful","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I drink to forget the war, friend. Trouble is the Orgrimmar grog's strong enough I keep forgetting my own name too. Small mercies.", roles={"drunkard"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Genuine troll voodoo charms, mon! Wards off curses, bad luck, AND tax collectors. Two silver, and don't ask which loa I borrowed it from.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I'll not drop the price, mon. This be Sen'jin craftwork, not goblin tin. You pay for the loa's blessing woven in, or you pay nothing and leave.", roles={"vendor"}, moods={"gruff","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Sang the spirit-walk over a fallen brave today and led his soul gentle to the ancestors. The Earth Mother gathers her children home.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { "A trembling young grunt asked the witch doctor if the loa forgive a coward. Dere be no cowards, I told him. Only da brave who not found it yet.", roles={"priest"}, moods={"kindly","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "The shadow holds no fear for the Forsaken. We have already died once. What is left to frighten the dead?", roles={"priest"}, moods={"bitter","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Horde: guards, mages, innkeepers, gossip (expansion) ==
      { "Quiet watch on the Orgrimmar wall this %timeofday%. Just me, the red stars, and a scorpid trying to climb the rampart. Persistent little beast.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Hauled in a goblin for 'unlicensed explosive enthusiasm' near the bank. He argued it was ART. The Warchief's law disagreed.", roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Portal to %zone% is stable for once, mon. Step through fast before some apprentice in the Cleft of Shadow miscounts and opens a rift to who-knows-where.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Studied a Reliquary cipher in Silvermoon by candlelight all night. The secret was written backward. The Sin'dorei do love their riddles.", roles={"mage"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "Hot stew, strong grog, and a fire that never dies, mon. The inn looks after the Horde's own. Pull up a stool; first %drink%'s on the house tonight.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"warm","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "I've poured for warlords and beggars across this bar, mon, and I'll tell you true: the beggars tip in stories, and the stories are worth more.", roles={"innkeeper"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { "They say a Kor'kron officer went missing on the road to the Crossroads. They say the Warchief's not pleased. They say a great deal in the Drag, mon.", roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
    },
    -- two-person back-and-forth (speakers alternate A / B)
    duos = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 5: tagged duos (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"The shaman's holding a calling-of-the-elements at the totem this %timeofday%.", "For the %zone% campaign?", "For the rains, first. Durotar's cracked dry and the crops are failing.", "...then I'll kneel with the rest. A Horde that won't ask the elements humbly doesn't deserve the rain they send. Come, leave your boots at the ring."}, roles={"priest","farmer"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { chain={"A Forsaken just told the grimmest joke I've ever heard and I can't stop laughing.", "They've a gift for it. When you've nothing left to lose, nothing's off the table.", "Is it healthy, laughing at death like that?", "For them? It's the healthiest thing they've got. Better to mock the grave than weep in it. Buy them a %drink% they can't taste and laugh along."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The witch doctor read the bones and named a winner for the %fish% contest.", "Did he name himself?", "He named a goblin nobody's heard of. Then the goblin won. By a LOT.", "...remind me to never bet against a Darkspear with the bones out. The loa see the river before the fish do."}, roles={"adventurer","vendor"}, moods={"nervous","wry"}, areas={coast=1, city=1} },
      { chain={"A blood elf and an orc are arguing about magic in the Drag again.", "The elf calls it discipline, the orc calls it a crutch.", "And it'll come to blows?", "It'll come to a shared %drink% and a draw, same as always. The Horde argues hard and forgives harder. Pull up a crate, this round's a good one."}, roles={"mage","soldier"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Orgrimmar's hosting the strongman trials for the %event%.", "A tauron favorite, no doubt.", "Till an orc matriarch twice his age stepped up and out-lifted the lot of them.", "...of course she did. Never bet against an old Horde woman with something to prove. Put my %gold% on the grandmother."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"cheerful","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged duos (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"The Barrens caravans are getting hit hard this %season%.", "Centaur out of the dust, quilboar from the thornbrush. Every %route% a gamble.", "And the goblins still run them?", "For the right %currency%, a goblin would haul %tradegood% through a dragon's gullet. Brave or greedy — out here they're the same word."}, roles={"vendor","sailor"}, moods={"greedy","wry"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Sen'jin village sent word — the murlocs are bold on the coast again.", "The Darkspear have held that shore a long time. They'll hold it yet.", "A few hunters and the loa at their backs, aye.", "Then I'll take my axe down to the water and stand with them. The Horde doesn't let the Darkspear hold the tide alone."}, roles={"soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"brave","gruff"}, areas={coast=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"A goblin 'upgraded' my %item% with a Bilgewater gadget.", "And?", "It hits harder, sparks when it shouldn't, and occasionally shouts a discount slogan mid-swing.", "...only in the Horde would a weapon try to sell you something. Does it work?", "Frighteningly well. The shouting's even unnerved a foe or two. I've decided it's a feature."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Brill's sending Tirisfal grain down to Durotar.", "The Forsaken feeding the living? There's a thing.", "They can't eat it. They grow it anyway, for the Horde that took them in.", "...that's the most the dead can give, isn't it. To labor for a hunger they'll never feel again. Leave them an honor at the totem tonight."}, roles={"farmer","priest"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={rural=2, city=1} },
      { chain={"You marched the northern campaign in %zone%. With the tauren.", "Shoulder to shoulder. A tauren twice my size carried me a mile when my leg gave out, and never once complained.", "Ever see him after?", "Every %event%, same Thunder Bluff rise, same silence over a shared %drink%. We don't need words. We bled the same ground. That's a bond no peace undoes."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"warm","weary"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"The Bilgewater cartel's 'sponsoring' the %event% this year.", "Translation: banners with their logo on every stall.", "And a surcharge hidden in every %food%, no doubt.", "No doubt. But the fireworks are spectacular and the %drink% flows free till midnight. Take the goblins' coin AND their party. Just count your own afterward."}, roles={"citizen","vendor"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged duos (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"You marched with the last Orgrimmar muster to %zone%.", "Earned the title '%title%' and a debt to the dead I'll never finish paying.", "Was it worth it?", "Ask me at the totem, where I leave an offering for the ones who earned only a place in the soil. ...no. But the Horde called. I went. I'd go again."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"An orc shaman loosed a %spell% over the Valley of Strength at dusk.", "Calling the elements to bless the warriors bound for %zone%.", "The whole sky cracked with light. A young troll near me dropped to his knees.", "...the elements answering in plain sight will do that. We forget, in the loud city, that the Horde walks WITH the world, not over it."}, roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Won this %mount% off a goblin who bet his whole caravan.", "A GOBLIN gambled badly? I don't believe it.", "He didn't gamble badly. He gambled drunk. Different beast entirely.", "...ha. Then you robbed a fool, not a merchant. Drinks on the mount-rich orc, and don't let him near the dice again."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The wind-riders are grounded — %weather%'s too fierce off the Barrens.", "So it's the long %route% on foot, then. With half of Durotar.", "And a goblin selling %consumable% at four times the gate price the whole way.", "...of course. The Horde marches, the goblin profits. Pack your patience and your coin, friend. It'll be a long road."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"A Forsaken keeps standing at the Undercity gate watching the living come and go.", "Lonely post.", "I asked once. They said they like remembering what hurry looked like. What WANTING looked like.", "...that's the saddest and the bravest thing. To stand at the edge of a life you've lost and not turn bitter. The Forsaken are stronger than we know."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Selling Mulgore cornbread to every warrior bound for %zone%, first piece free.", "You'll go broke feeding an army, tauren.", "A warrior's last taste of the plains before a hard road? The Earth Mother would frown if I charged for that.", "...give me a basket. I'll work the Drag gate. No one marches out of Orgrimmar hungry while there's bread to share."}, roles={"vendor","farmer"}, moods={"kindly","warm"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"A blood elf and a troll were arguing magic against the loa half the %timeofday%.", "Did it come to blows?", "Came to a shared %drink% and a grudging respect. The elf admitted the loa were 'a valid framework.' The troll laughed for an hour.", "...that's the Horde, isn't it. Two who couldn't be more different, finding the one thread that holds. Pass me a cup, I want in on the next round."}, roles={"mage","citizen"}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged duos (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"The shaman called the rains early. Saved the whole Durotar crop.", "The elements actually answered the call?", "Like kin. They don't serve us — they choose us. That's a debt, not a tool.", "...then we leave an offering at the totem tonight. A Horde that forgets its debts deserves the drought."}, roles={"priest","farmer"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Watched the Kor'kron drill at dawn.", "Orc, troll, tauren, Forsaken — all in one column, all in step.", "Some still call us a rabble.", "Let them. A rabble doesn't move like that. Let our enemies keep underestimating us right up until %zone%."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"boastful","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A Forsaken apothecary cured the whole village's fever.", "With what?", "A %consumable% no living healer could brew. I didn't ask the ingredients.", "Wise. In the Undercity, the cure and the curse share a shelf. Be grateful and don't read the label."}, roles={"priest","citizen"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { chain={"A blood elf just fixed a goblin's exploded %toy% mid-sentence.", "Didn't even look down, did they.", "Flick of the wrist, kept right on talking. Showoffs.", "Ten thousand years of magic in their blood, friend. To them it IS nothing. Respect it and try not to be jealous."}, roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A troll showed me the loa-marks carved above his door.", "One for each spirit watching his line?", "Said the Darkspear never walk %zone% alone. Felt it in how he said it.", "...I used to think the trolls' faith was strange. Now I think it might be the least lonely way to live there is."}, roles={"citizen","priest"}, moods={"dreamy","solemn"} },
      { chain={"Goblin's running a 'war-surplus' stall — dented %item% off the %zone% front.", "Grim, selling what the fallen dropped.", "A warrior on a budget doesn't have the luxury of grim. He buys the dent and lives.", "...fair. Pick me out a sturdy one, then. And say a word for whoever carried it last."}, roles={"vendor","soldier"}, moods={"greedy","solemn"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Recruiters are promising plunder and glory in %zone%.", "Look at the old veterans by the gate. Watch what they do when the glory-talk starts.", "...they just drink. They don't say anything.", "That silence IS what they're saying. Listen to it harder than the recruiter's drum, young blood."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"bitter","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A tauren and an orc were arguing the old way against the new.", "Should we step in?", "No — watch. See? Shared a %drink%, clasped arms, walked off as brothers.", "The Horde only ever fights itself to sharpen itself. That's the difference between a quarrel and a feud."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"gruff","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A witch doctor read my spilled %drink% and called a storm over %zone%.", "And?", "Three days on, %weather% rolled in just as he said.", "...leave the man an offering and stop spilling your %drink% where he can read it. Some futures you don't want told."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"nervous","dreamy"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged duos (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Why's a goblin selling 'genuine %item%' in the Valley of Strength again?", "Moved forty last %event%. Painted scrap, every one.", "And the Kor'kron allow it?", "The Kor'kron bought three. Of course they allow it."}, roles={"vendor"}, moods={"wry","bitter"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"You hear the drums from the smiths' quarter?", "Day and night since the call-up. They're forging for %zone%.", "Sounds like the city's heart beating.", "It IS the city's heart, friend. As long as the Orgrimmar forges sing, the Horde stands. Now mind the sparks."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"boastful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A young orc just marched off to %zone% to prove himself.", "They all do, that age. Glory-blind, the lot.", "Should we have stopped him?", "You can't. You can only sharpen his blade, tell him the truth, and hope the truth reaches him before the enemy does."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"gruff","solemn"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Why's it so QUIET up here on Thunder Bluff?", "No auctioneers. No portals. Just wind and totems and sky.", "...I don't know what to do with this much peace.", "Sit. Breathe. The tauren learned long ago that a still soul hunts truer. Try it a %timeofday%."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"An elder blessed the whole hunt before they rode out.", "Thanked the Earth Mother for every %critter% they'd take, before they took one.", "Strange, thanking your supper in advance.", "Not strange. Right. The tauren waste nothing — not the meat, not the gratitude. We could learn from them."}, roles={"priest","farmer"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { chain={"An apothecary in the Undercity offered me a green vial for my cough.", "Did you drink it?", "Do I look dead to you?", "...give it a %season%. In the Undercity that's not always a yes or a no."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A Forsaken keeps a %food% on the windowsill. They can't even eat.", "It's for the memory. They remember the taste, though the hunger's long gone.", "...that's the saddest thing I've heard all %season%.", "Or the bravest. To keep a small joy you can no longer have, just so you don't forget you once did. That's the Forsaken."}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Silvermoon magisters make it look so EASY.", "Ten thousand years of practice will do that. Watch one enchant a %item% with %enchant% — it's like breathing to them.", "Showoffs.", "Magnificent showoffs. Lost their Sunwell, kept their swagger. You have to respect it a little."}, roles={"mage"}, moods={"wry","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Saw a blood elf stop mid-step, breathe slow, then carry on.", "The thirst. They all feel it, deep down. They just master it where you can see.", "...I never noticed before.", "That's the point. Quiet courage. The hardest battles are the ones fought behind a calm face."}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Why do the trolls always say 'mon'?", "Why do YOU always say 'epic %item%' and 'for the Horde'?", "...that's different.", "It's not, mon. We've all got our songs. Sit, share a %drink%, learn a few of mine."}, moods={"wry","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Goblin sold me a map to buried %gold% in %zone%.", "Let me guess. The treasure was another map.", "...the treasure was another map.", "It's always another map. Frame it. You paid for a lesson, not a fortune, and that's the goblin way."}, roles={"adventurer","vendor"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={road=1, city=1} },
      { chain={"You shipping out to %zone% with the muster?", "Aye. Recruiter sang of glory and plunder.", "It's cold ground and colder %food%, mostly.", "...you've been, then.", "Twice. So when the glory-song starts to fade out there, find me at the fire. I'll remind you what we're really holding the line for."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"An orc and a troll are brawling by the bank over some ancient grudge.", "From before either of them was born, no doubt.", "Should the Kor'kron stop it?", "They will, then make the two of them haul water together till they're friends. The Horde mends its quarrels with sweat, not speeches."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"wry","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A shaman called the wind to dry our %tradegood% before the %weather% hit.", "The elements actually answered?", "Like an old friend. The Horde doesn't take that gift for granted.", "...remind me to leave an offering at the totem. I'd no idea the racks were saved by spirits."}, roles={"priest","farmer"}, moods={"solemn","warm"}, areas={city=1, rural=1} },
      { chain={"Why does every orc in Orgrimmar look like they could bench-press a kodo?", "Because most of us can.", "The kodos volunteer. It's a status thing."}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"How do you not fall off Thunder Bluff? It's all cliffs and rope bridges.", "We don't look down. The Earth Mother handles the rest."}, moods={"wry"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { chain={"Does it ever bother you that the Undercity used to be Lordaeron's crown jewel?", "Every single day. That's rather the point."}, moods={"bitter"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Everything in Silvermoon is so perfect it's almost unsettling.", "Ten thousand years of refinement, darling. Try to keep up."}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Warchief's banners went up overnight. All of them.", "Garrosh doesn't do subtle.", "...think the old guard will say anything?", "Quietly. Always quietly. That's how you keep your head."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"gossipy","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"A shaman told me the elements are angry lately.", "Aye. The earth's been restless under Orgrimmar for weeks.", "Omen?", "Or the forges. Hard to say. The old ones say omen. I'd listen to the old ones."}, roles={"priest"}, moods={"solemn","nervous"} },
      { chain={"Caught a Forsaken laughing in the Apothecarium today.", "Now THAT'S unsettling. What was so funny?", "Didn't ask. Some questions you don't want answered in the Undercity.", "Wise. Very wise."}, moods={"wry","nervous"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"That %race% %class% in the Valley of Strength is carrying %item%.", "Off %boss%, at %difficulty%. Earned it in blood.", "...and I'm still hauling ore for %gold% a stack. The Earth Mother tests us all differently."}, roles={"craftsman"}, moods={"weary","gossipy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"%weather% grounded the wind riders again.", "So we take %route%?", "In this %season%? We drink at %shop% till it clears, mon. The Barrens isn't going anywhere."}, moods={"weary","wry"}, areas={rural=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Hit exalted with %rep% this %timeofday%.", "The %mount%?", "Mine at last. And every %profession% pattern they were hoarding. Lok'tar, it was worth the grind."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"boastful"} },
      -- == Horde: Mulgore / rural duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Quilboar took the eastern totems again last night.", "Aye, the watch-fires were down by dawn. You stand the line?", "Spear and a war-cry. They don't like a tauren who won't run. Neither do I.", "The plains remember the brave. Walk easy, kinsman."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"brave","solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { chain={"The young one brought down his first kodo this moon.", "Did the elders sing for him?", "All night. He's got a name now and a tremble in his hands he'll grow out of.", "We all had that tremble once. The plains make hunters slow and sure."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      { chain={"You'd think after the centaur we'd get a quiet season in Mulgore.", "Quiet just means the trouble's grazing elsewhere, kinsman.", "...you sound like a Durotar orc.", "I married one. It rubs off. Pass the smoked plainstrider."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"wry","weary"}, areas={"rural"} },
      -- == Horde: coast / docks duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Boat from the Echo Isles is three hours late, mon.", "Naga, weather, or the captain found the Ratchet grog. Always one of the three.", "My coin's on the grog.", "Wise coin. He found it last tide too, mon."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","gossipy"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { chain={"Catch anything off the Ratchet pier, mon?", "A boot, a crab, and four fat %fish%. The crab fought the hardest.", "And the boot?", "The boot came quiet. I respect a quiet boot, me."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"coast"} },
      { chain={"They say the naga are thick off the Durotar reefs now.", "More every moon, mon. We don't sail past the point after dark.", "Cowardly?", "Breathing. Dere's a difference, and I aim to keep doing it."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"nervous","cowardly"}, areas={"coast"} },
      -- == Horde: war front / battlefield duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"First charge on %zone% at dawn. You afraid, grunt?", "Witless with it. You?", "Same. The ones who say they aren't are liars or fools.", "Then we're the honest fools. Stand at my shoulder, and we'll feast tonight or with the ancestors."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"cowardly","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { chain={"Hold the line, the warlord said. As if the Scourge take orders.", "We held it, didn't we?", "By the elements and orcish stubbornness and little else.", "That's most victories the Horde ever won, kinsman."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      { chain={"The witch doctor's marking the war-band before the push on %zone%.", "Does the voodoo help, mon?", "The marks? Who can say. The courage they put in da lads? Every time.", "Then mark away, doctah. We carry all da spirit we can hold into that fight."}, roles={"priest","soldier"}, moods={"solemn","brave"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      -- == Horde: wilderness / road duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Tracked that %monster% clear across the Barrens, mon.", "And?", "And it tracked me back. We came to an understanding involving me leaving very fast.", "Hunter's wisdom, dat. Live to track another day."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={"wilderness"} },
      { chain={"Wind rider or the road to the Crossroads?", "Road, every time. The wind riders buck in the Barrens heat.", "Road's two days of dust and quilboar, though.", "Two days I'll walk over forty minutes of clinging to a screaming beast. Keep your sky, mon."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"wry","cowardly"}, areas={"road"} },
      { chain={"Caravan grunt's pay went up on the Crossroads run.", "Because no sane orc takes it. The Barrens crawl with centaur.", "I'm not sane and I need the coin, mon.", "Then I watch your back. Two fools last longer than one in the Barrens."}, roles={"guard"}, moods={"brave","greedy"}, areas={"road"} },
      -- == Horde: noble / urchin city duos (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Did you SEE what Lady Sunwhisper wore to the magisters' gala?", "Three layers of enchanted silk in high summer. She nearly swooned in the receiving line, darling.", "Beauty before breathing. Silvermoon's eternal motto.", "And THAT, darling, is why I summer in cool Thunder Bluff with the savages."}, roles={"noble"}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Oi, mind your purse near the Drag fountain, your lordship, the guards ain't looking.", "You warning me or robbing me, kid?", "Warning, mon. The robbing's the OTHER kid. I'm an honest little thief, me.", "...here's a copper for the honesty, then. Now vanish."}, roles={"urchin","noble"}, moods={"wry","greedy"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Spare a coin for a cold kid, your grace?", "Here. And take this skewer, mon, I've no stomach for it tonight.", "The loa bless you, lordling, you're the kind one.", "Tell no one. I've a reputation as a Silvermoon miser to protect."}, roles={"urchin","noble"}, moods={"kindly","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
    },
    -- group discussions (many voices, rotating cast of 4-6)
    groups = {
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 5: tagged groups (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Most beautiful place in the Horde's lands? The WILD ones, not the cities.", "Mulgore at dawn. The whole plain gold, the wind in the grass, and not a single thing to fear. Peace you can taste.", "The Echo Isles when the loa-fires burn low and the water glows. The Darkspear say the spirits dance there. I believe it.", "Sunset over the Barrens, of all places. Harsh land, but the sky bleeds colors no painter could mix. Beauty out of hardship — very Horde.", "The quiet of Tirisfal at %timeofday%. Grim, grey, still. The Forsaken find it restful. After a while, so did I.", "...even the dead among us have a place that's beautiful to them. That says something.", "It says we're more than the war. We're the plains and the isles and the grey quiet too.", "Then we hold the line for THOSE, not the warchief's banner. To Mulgore, the Isles, the Barrens sky. Lok'tar."}, roles={"citizen","soldier"}, moods={"dreamy","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"The Forsaken have the darkest humor in the Horde. Best one you've each heard?", "An apothecary offered me 'a free sample, no refunds, no survivors.' Then winked. I think it was a joke. I'm fairly sure.", "One told me they're 'dying to retire.' Took me a moment. Then I couldn't breathe for laughing.", "A gravedigger in Brill said business was 'looking up' and gestured at the whole of us living folk. Grim. Fair. Funny.", "...is it strange that their jokes are the ones that stick with me longest?", "Not strange. When you've stared death down and come back wrong, you've EARNED the right to laugh at it.", "And they share the laugh freely. That's the Forsaken gift — they make the grave a little less frightening for the rest of us.", "To the Forsaken, then. The grimmest jokes and the bravest hearts. Buy them a %drink% they can't taste. They'll appreciate the gesture."}, roles={"citizen"}, moods={"wry","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 4: tagged groups (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"The Barrens, Sen'jin, the thornlands — the Horde's frontier is bleeding. Who's been out there?", "Ran a Barrens caravan that lost two wagons to centaur before the first water-stop. The dust doesn't forgive.", "Sen'jin holds against the murlocs, but the Darkspear are stretched thin. A few hunters and a lot of loa.", "The quilboar are organized this %season%. That's new, and it's worse. They hit the %route% like they planned it.", "...and Orgrimmar drums for %zone% the whole while, doesn't it. The far war pulling eyes off the near one.", "A Horde that forgets its own frontier won't hold its heart long. We owe the borderlands more than a banner.", "Then we carry the tale to every cookfire in the Drag till the warchief's ear bends. Strength shared, frontier included.", "Lok'tar. To the Barrens runners and the Sen'jin hunters. The Horde stands with you, or it doesn't deserve to stand."}, roles={"vendor","soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"bitter","brave"}, areas={road=2, rural=1} },
      { chain={"The harvest %event%'s on. Best memory each of you carries from it?", "Out-eating a tauron at the Mulgore feast. I lost, magnificently, and was adopted by his whole family on the spot.", "Meeting the tauren who carried me out of %zone%, same rise, every year. We barely speak. It's the loudest silence I know.", "My first one, fresh from the thornlands — a goblin handed me a %drink% that sparked and the whole world cracked open bigger.", "Watching an orc, a Forsaken, and a blood elf attempt a Darkspear drum-chant. None knew the rhythm. All committed entirely. Glorious noise.", "...it's the one festival where the whole Horde just breathes together, isn't it. No muster, no front.", "That's the heart of it. Six peoples, one fire, no %zone% on anyone's mind for one golden %timeofday%.", "To the harvest feast, then. May the %food% never run short, the drums stay terrible, and the family stay whole. Lok'tar ogar."}, roles={"citizen","soldier"}, moods={"cheerful","warm"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 3: tagged groups (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Round the totem — what did the %zone% campaign take from each of you?", "A title and a debt. '%title%,' the young ones call me. The debt to the dead has no name and never empties.", "My whole warband but two. I came off that field and the Earth Mother asked me to keep breathing. Hardest order I ever followed.", "My son. I forge a blade each dawn anyway, as if there were still someone to come home and claim it. Maybe there is. Maybe it's just the forge keeping me upright.", "...and I never marched. I ran supplies. Lived safe while you bled. I carry that.", "Carry it lighter. Without your runs we'd have starved before the first charge. The Horde is the runner AND the warrior. Strength is shared or it's nothing.", "...he speaks true. To the one who fed us. No title from the warchief, but a place at this fire forever.", "To all of it. The fallen, the two, the son, the supply road. Lok'tar ogar. We carry each other or we carry nothing."}, roles={"soldier","craftsman"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Most HORDE thing each of you has ever seen — go.", "A tauren lifting a lost goblin onto his shoulder to find his caravan, gentle as if the little schemer were his own calf.", "An orc and a troll settling a blood-grudge by hauling water together till they were too tired to hate. Brothers by sundown.", "A Forsaken apothecary curing a Durotar village no living healer could save, asking nothing, fading back into the dark.", "A blood elf magister mending an orphan's exploded %toy% mid-sentence, like ten thousand years of magic were nothing beside one child's tears.", "...the cast-out, the proud, the dead, and the ancient — all of us, somehow, one banner.", "That's the strength they never understand. Not the axe. The CHOOSING. Lok'tar ogar.", "Lok'tar. Pass the %drink%. To the strangers who became kin, and the Horde that took us all in."}, roles={"citizen","soldier"}, moods={"warm","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH 2: tagged groups (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Round the totem fire — what does the Horde mean to each of you, truly?", "Strength. Not the axe-arm kind. The kind where a tauron lifts your lost child to his shoulder without being asked.", "Belonging. I woke up Forsaken with nowhere to go, and this was the only banner that didn't flinch from me.", "The elements. An orc shaman calls the rain and Durotar lives. We are KIN to the world here, not its master.", "The loa. The Darkspear taught me you never walk %zone% alone. There's always a spirit at your shoulder.", "...five answers, one fire, one family.", "That's the Horde. Forged from the cast-out and the proud alike. Lok'tar ogar.", "Lok'tar. Pass the %drink%. To the strength that's really just refusing to abandon each other."}, roles={"soldier","priest","citizen"}, moods={"warm","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Grim news off %zone%. Who here's lost someone to the front?", "My son marched last %timeofday%. I forge a blade each dawn so there's something for him to come home to.", "Lost my whole warband a war past. I leave an offering at the totem and I keep breathing. The Earth Mother asks no more.", "The Bilgewater crews run medicine and %tradegood% up the line now. Coin and conscience, finally pulling the same way.", "...and I keep the Drag's cookfire lit. A warrior needs a warm pot to march toward as much as a warchief's cause.", "All of it is strength. The blade, the offering, the supply run, the fire. None of it is small.", "Then we each hold our corner and we wait, together. The smith, the mourner, the runner, the cook.", "Together. Lok'tar ogar — but more than that, Earth Mother and loa both, bring them home to their warm pots."}, roles={"craftsman","priest","sailor"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- ============================================================
      -- == EXPANSION BATCH: tagged groups (HORDE)
      -- ============================================================
      { chain={"Settle it: which Horde city stands tallest?", "Orgrimmar. The forges never cool, the walls never bend. The heart of the Horde, and you know it.", "Thunder Bluff. Open sky, clean wind, and a peace your iron city's never tasted, orc.", "Undercity. Grim? Aye. But we made a home of the grave itself. Beat that.", "Silvermoon. Ten thousand years of beauty against your mud huts and your tombs. Please.", "Bilgewater spits on all of you. Best harbor, best deals, and the only city that turns a profit on the others' wars.", "...of course the goblin counts coin while the rest of us count glory.", "Glory doesn't fill a coffer, friend. But you're all loyal to wherever your hearthstone sits, admit it.", "Aye. Home's home. Mine just happens to have the best forges, the cleanest sky, OR the cleverest accountants, depending who's asking."}, moods={"boastful","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"How did each of you come to call the Horde home?", "Born under the Orgrimmar walls. Marched for it before I could grow a proper tusk. Never questioned it.", "Fled to Thunder Bluff after my village burned. The tauren took me in, fed me, asked nothing. So I gave everything.", "I... woke up Forsaken. The Horde was the only banner that didn't run from what I'd become.", "Silvermoon joined and so did I. We needed somewhere to belong after the Sunwell fell. We found it here.", "...six different roads, one fire, one family.", "That's the Horde. Not blood — though there's plenty of that. Belonging. Strength shared.", "Lok'tar ogar. Pass the %drink%, and let's drink to the strangers who became kin."}, roles={"soldier","citizen"}, moods={"warm","gruff"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Recruiters are in the Valley of Honor again. Talk some sense into me.", "Can't. I marched last %season%. Came back with scars I'll show and stories I won't.", "Don't go for the warchief's banners. Go because the ones at your fire sleep safer for it. That's the only honest reason.", "Or stay and tend the home the warriors march to defend. The Earth Mother keeps no score on who held a blade.", "...glory's heavy, young one. Heavier than any axe. Be sure you can carry it before you reach for it.", "Then reach for something REAL to fight for, and let that pick your road, not the recruiter's drum.", "Wise words. Now drink, all of you. Marcher or hearth-keeper, tonight we're just Horde at a fire."}, roles={"soldier","citizen"}, moods={"solemn","weary"}, areas={city=1, road=1} },
      { chain={"Strangest thing you've each seen in a Horde city square?", "A goblin's 'bargain bin' that exploded, restocked itself, and exploded again. Sold out in an hour.", "A tauren gently lifting a lost goblin onto his shoulder to find his caravan. I nearly wept into my %food%.", "A troll witch doctor reading fortunes in spilled %drink%. Told mine. It's come half true, which is the troubling half.", "A Forsaken juggling their own detached hand for tips. Grim. Effective. The children loved it.", "...our cities are strange and wonderful and a little bit on fire at all times, aren't they.", "Always. The Horde never does anything by halves. Same square tomorrow?", "Same square. Bring coin for the goblin and a strong stomach for the Forsaken."}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"News is grim out of %zone%. How's everyone bearing it?", "My son's with the muster there. I forge a blade each %timeofday% and tell myself it's for him to come home to.", "Lost my whole warband there, a war past. I leave an offering at the totem and I keep breathing. It's the tauren way.", "The Bilgewater crews are running %tradegood% and medicine up the line. Coin AND conscience, for once aligned.", "...I keep the cookfire lit in the Drag. A warrior needs a warm pot to march toward as much as a cause.", "And that's no small thing. Strength isn't only in the swinging arm. It's in the ones who keep the fire.", "Then we each hold our corner — the blade, the offering, the supplies, the fire — and we wait. Together.", "Together. Lok'tar ogar — but mostly, Earth Mother, bring them home to their warm pots."}, roles={"craftsman","priest","sailor"}, moods={"solemn","kindly"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Which Horde city actually feels like home to you?", "Orgrimmar. Iron walls, hot forges, and the sunrise over the gates. Nothing like it.", "Thunder Bluff. Open sky, clean wind, totems humming. The plains heal you.", "Silvermoon, obviously. Beauty rebuilt from ash. We earned every gilded arch.", "The Undercity. I know, I know. But the Forsaken made a home out of nothing. That means something.", "Sen'jin and the echoes of the islands, for me. The drums still call us, mon.", "...the orc and the tauren are about to argue forges versus plains again, aren't they?", "We always do. And we always end up drinking together after.", "That's the Horde, isn't it. Different blood, same fire.", "Lok'tar. To home, whatever shape it takes."}, moods={"warm","boastful"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"War-band's short for %instance% %difficulty%.", "Short what?", "A %role% and a %class% who won't bolt when %boss% enrages.", "%gearscore% here, and I've %consumable% enough for the lot of you.", "Then strap in. We ride from the Orgrimmar gates at %timeofday%. Lok'tar."}, roles={"soldier","adventurer"}, moods={"brave"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Is %rep% worth the grind, honestly?", "The %mount% at exalted is worth more than %gold% to a Silvermoon collector, so aye.", "And the %profession% patterns. You'll not find %item% taught anywhere else.", "Then it's settled. Dailies at dawn till the quartermaster knows my name.", "He'll know it. He knew mine before I knew the way back to Orgrimmar."}, roles={"adventurer"}, moods={"weary"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"That %race% %class% in the Drag is carrying %item%, I swear it.", "Off %boss%? At %difficulty%?", "Glows like Silvermoon at midnight. Has to be real.", "Or the best forgery a goblin ever sold. Half the Drag is forgeries.", "...only one way to know. Buy them a drink and ask.", "In the Drag? You buy a stranger a drink, you wake up missing a kidney, mon.", "...fair. We admire from a safe distance, then."}, moods={"gossipy","wry"}, areas={"city"} },
      { chain={"Best place in the Horde to watch %weather% come in?", "The high rises of Thunder Bluff. You're up in it before it ever touches the plain.", "The Orgrimmar walls at %timeofday%. Iron and storm-light, nothing finer.", "The spires of Silvermoon. Even a downpour looks like a painting from up there.", "...the Undercity. No weather at all. That IS the appeal, for some of us.", "Leave it to the Forsaken to call 'no sky' a feature.", "We made peace with the dark a long time ago. You'd be surprised how restful it is.", "To each their own horizon, then. Drinks in the Valley of Honor after?", "Lok'tar. First round's on the one who said Undercity."}, moods={"dreamy"}, areas={"city"} },
      -- == Horde: Mulgore / plains-life groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"How fared the hunt this %season%, kinsmen?", "The kodo herds came down fat. The cookfires of Bloodhoof burned bright all moon.", "The quilboar tested our totems twice, but the plains are still ours.", "My young one took his first kill. The elders sang till dawn.", "The Earth Mother was generous. We gave thanks and took only our share.", "...you all sound like the elders now, you know.", "Good. Someone must, when the elders walk the long path home.", "To the herds, then, and the grass, and the breathing of the Earth Mother beneath us.", "An'she keep the cookfires warm. Pass the smoked plainstrider, kinsman."}, roles={"farmer"}, moods={"warm","solemn"}, areas={"rural"} },
      -- == Horde: coast / dockside groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Worst crossing you ever sailed out of Ratchet, mon?", "The Echo Isles run in a bay-gale. Lost the sail and most of me supper.", "Durotar reefs in naga season. They came up the anchor chain, mon. The CHAIN.", "Any goblin captain who 'forgets' to mention the reef for a cheaper fare.", "Give me a storm over a goblin at the wheel any tide of the year.", "...you're all braver than me. I haul nets from the pier and sleep on dry sand.", "Smartest of the lot, then. The sea takes the bold first, mon.", "Aye. To the ones it took. And to dry feet and a full net.", "Grog at the Ratchet tavern. First round on the naga survivor, mon."}, roles={"sailor"}, moods={"weary","brave"}, areas={"coast"} },
      -- == Horde: war front / battlefield groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"How does a Horde warrior keep his nerve before the horn, kinsmen?", "The witch doctor's marks, and the loa close at my back.", "I think of Mulgore. The grass, the herds. Something worth marching home to.", "Honestly? I'm terrified every charge. I just charge terrified.", "That's the truest answer here, grunt. We all charge terrified.", "The veterans don't, surely?", "The veterans are the ones who learned to charge terrified and live. There's no other kind, mon.", "...then we ride in fine company. Stand fast when the drums sound.", "Lok'tar ogar. And here's to surviving to tell it badly over grog."}, roles={"soldier"}, moods={"brave","cowardly"}, areas={"battlefield"} },
      -- == Horde: road / caravan groups (expansion) ==
      { chain={"Fastest way north out of Orgrimmar, then? Settle it, kinsmen.", "Zeppelin to the Undercity, no argument. Up and over and done.", "Wind rider if you trust the beast not to buck in the Barrens heat.", "On foot through Durotar if you've the time. The red dusk is something to see.", "Caravan if you've cargo — but pay for grunts past the Crossroads.", "...the Drag urchins know shortcuts none of you do, mon, by the way.", "The street kids? Truly?", "Pay one a copper and they'll walk you to a gate you never knew Orgrimmar had. Best guides in the city.", "The things you learn on the road. To shortcuts and short coppers, kinsmen."}, roles={"adventurer","urchin"}, moods={"wry","cheerful"}, areas={"road"} },
    },
  },

}
